  2,148,"Ena woodani mo kala ba≈ã≈ãe …óe o fewtata e mun.Adondiree e mo∆¥∆¥ereeji,nokku kala ka laati-…óon,Allah artiray on,on denndaangal. Pellete,Allah ko hattan…óo e dow kala huunde"
