  2,150,"Nokku kala ka yaltir…óaa, fewtinir yeeso maa ngon ba≈ã≈ãe Suudu Hormorteendu ndun, nokku kala ka ngon…óon, fewtiniree geece mon …óen ba≈ã≈ãe mayru fii wata wonan yim…ìe …ìen hujja e hoore mo'on - so wanaa …ìen too√±u…ìe e ma…ì…ìe. Wata non on hulu…ìe, Hulee Lam, fii no Mi Timminira neema Am On e mo'on, belajo'o on feeway"
