  2,168,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe! √ëaamee yoga e ko woni ka leydi ko dagii ko laa…ìi, wata on jokku juri=taabe seytaane …óin : Pellet, ko o ga√±o mo'on fee√±u…óo"
