  2,173,"Anndee ko O Harminani on, ko jii…ìe, e ∆¥ii∆¥am, e teewu kose, e [huunde hirsiraande] daginiraande ko woori Allah. Kala on du√±aa…óo [e √±aamugol …óum] hara wanaa …ìew…óo wanaa jaggitu…óo, bakkatu fawaaki mo. Pellet Allah ko Ya'fotoo…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  2,174,"Pellet …ìen suu…óoo…ìe ko Allah Jippini kon e Deftere nden, hi…ìe soodira …óum cogguwel fam…óungel. ∆Åen …óon alaa wa…óude ka deedi ma…ì…ìe si wanaa yiite ngen; Allah Yeewtidtaa …ìe √±alnde darngal, O La…ì…ìi≈ãtaa …ìe, hino woodani …ìe lepte muusu…óe"
