  2,180,"Farlaama e mo'on:si maayde nden arii e mo'on,si o accii jawle: wasiyanagol jibin…ìe mo …ìen,e …ìadondiraa…ìe …ìen no mo∆¥∆¥iri.Ko hannduyee e dow gom…óu…ìe …ìen"
