  2,182,"On mo huli oo√±aare immorde e wasiyii…óo maa bakkaatu o mo∆¥∆¥ini hakkunde ma…ì…ìe,bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Pellet Alla ko Yawtanoowo Yurmotoo…óo"
  2,183,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ìe, koorka kan farlaama e mo'on wano ka farliranoo e …ìen adinoo…ìe on, …ìelajo'o laato…óon gom…óu…ìe"
  2,184,"√ëal…ói limtaa…ói. Kala e mo'on laatii…óo nawnu…óo maa e hoore-jahal: ko limtugol √±al…ói goo. No fawii …ìen ha…ótan…ìe ka, √±ammingol …ìilii…óo. Kala on gattu…óo mo∆¥∆¥ere …óum no mo∆¥∆¥ani mo. Ko nde hooroton …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde on, si wonii hi…óon nganndi"
  2,185,"Lewru koorka ndun, ndu Alqur'aanaare nden jippinaa e mu'un, ko ndu peewal wonannde yim…ìe …ìen e …ìangannduyeeji immorde e peewal e serndugol. On e mo'on seedii…óo lewru ndun, yo o hooru ndu. On taw…óo no nawni maa himo e hoore-jahal, ko limtugol e √±al…ói goo. Alla no Faandanii on neweende O Faandanaaki on sa…óteende; e fii yo on timmin limoore nden e no mawniniro Alla kon ko O Fewni on, belajo'o on jaarnay Mo"
  2,186,"Si jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen lamndike lan fii Am, hary Min: Ko Mi ∆Åa…óii…óo. Mi…óo Jaabina toraare torotoo…óo si o torike Lam. Yo …ìe nooto Lam, e yo …ìe gom…óinam, belajo'o …ìe feeway"
  2,187,"Daginanaama on jemma koorka kan yiidugol e rew…ìe mon …ìen. Ko …ìe koltu mo'on ko on koltu ma…ì…ìe. Alla Anndii wonde on laatinoke ja≈ãfotoo…ìe ko*e-mon,O Ja…ìani on tuubuubuyee O Ya'fii on.Jooni non,soccondiree e ma…ì…ìe …óa…ì…ìon ko Alla Winndani on.√ëaamee yaron haa gaarawol danewol ngol …ìa≈ãngirana on …ìalewol ngol ka peeral, refti timminiron koorka kan jemma. Wata on soccondir e ma…ì…ìe hara ko on ufnii…ìe ka juulir…óe.∆äum ko keeri Allah, wata on …ìa…óto …ói.Ko wano nii Allaahu On ∆Åa≈ãnginira≈ãta yim…ìe …ìen aayeeje Makko …óen,belajo'o …ìe wona gom…óu…ìe"
  2,188,"Wata on √±aamir jawle mon …óen hakkundeeji mo'on e hoore mehre, werloron …óe e √±aawoo…ìe …ìen fii yo fedde goo √±aamira e jawle yim…ìe …ìen bakkaatu, hara hi…óon nganndi"
  2,189,"Hi…ìe naamno-maa fii daror…óe lebbi, wi'u: \"∆äin ko waqa≈ãtinanay…ói yim…ìe e fii hajju\".Dewal ngal wonaali nde ngarda≈ãton cuu…ói …óin immorde ka …ìabbe majji, si ko woni dewal ngal: ko on gom…óu…óo.Ngardanee cuu…ói …óin ka dame majji.Hulon Allah,belajo'o on malete"
  2,190,"Ha…ìee fii laawol Alla ngol …ìen ha…ìoo…ìe on, wata on jaggitu. Pellet, Alla yi…óaa jaggitoo…ìe …ìen"
  2,191,"waree…ìe nokku kala ka taw…óon …ìe, yaltinee…ìe nokku ka …ìe yaltiniri on: ko geddi …óin …ìuri mawnude e dii ha…ìugol ngol. Wata on ha…ìu…ìe ka Misiide Horma≈ãteere haa …ìe ha…ìa on e mayre. Si …ìe ha…ìii on ha…ìee …ìe. Ko wano nii woni njo…ìdi heefer…ìe …ìen"
  2,192,"Si …ìe ha…óitike, pellet, Alla ko O Hafroowo Huu…ìu…óo-yumeende"
  2,193,"Ha…ìee …ìe haa nokku ka laatotaako fitina, diina kan laatanoo Alla. Si …ìe ha…óitike, haray jaggitere alanaa si wanaa …ìen too√±oo…ìe"
  2,194,"Si …ìe ha…ìii on e lewru horma≈ãteeru, ha…ìee …ìe e lewru horma≈ãteeru, horminaa…ói …óin ko yottondirtee …óum. On mo jaggiti e mo'on jaggitee e dow makko yeru kon ko o jaggiti e dow moo…óon. Hulee Alla anndon pellet Alla no wonndi …ìen gom…óu…ìe"
  2,195,"Wi≈ãtee e fii laawol Alla, wata on bugor juu…óe mon …óen faade e halakuyee. Mo∆¥∆¥inee, pellet Alla no Yi…ói mo∆¥∆¥inay…ìe …ìen"
  2,196,"Timminiree hajju ngun e 'omra on fii Alla. Si on sakkaama: fawike on ittugol kon ko newii e kirse, wata on femmbu ko'e mon …óen haa kirse …óen yottoo nokku majje. On taw…óo e mo'on ko √±aw…óo maa lorra no ka hoore makko, ko soktorgol: koorka, maa sadaqa maa dammol. Si on wonii e hoolaare, on mo dakmitori 'omra on haa ka hajju: fawike mo ittugol kon ko newii e kirse. Mo he…ìaali, ko hoorugol bal…óe tati ka hajju e jee…ói…ói si on ruttike; …óen ko sappo timmu…óe. Ko ja≈ãtaa koo, ko fii on taw…óo …ìeynguure mun nden laataaki ho…óu…ìe ka Misiide horma≈ãte. Hulee Alla, anndon pellet Alla ko sa…ótu…óo lepte"
  2,197,"Hajju ngun:ko lebbi anndaa…ói. Mo anniyike e nder majji hajju,renndugol alaa,wanaa faasoqingol wanaa kadi yeddondiro ka hajju.Kala ku gollug…óon e mo∆¥∆¥ere, Allah no Anndi …óum.Yoo…ìee,ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e njoo…ìa,ko gom…óal. Hulee Lam yo joomiraa…ìe haqqillaaji"
  2,198,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde …óa…ì…ìoton arsike immorde e Joomi mo'on. Si on iwtii 'Aarafaat, Ja≈ãtee innde Alla ka nokku horminannde. Ja≈ãtoron Mo wano O fewniri on non, hari on laatinoke ado muu…óum ko on jeyaa…ìe e majju…ìe"
  2,199,"Refti yahron ka yim…ìe …ìen yahri …óon, Insinano…óon Alla. Pellet Alla ko Yaafotoo…óo Huu…ìu…óo-yurmeende"
  2,200,"Si on gaynii dewe hajju mon ngun, ja≈ãtoree innde Alla wano ja≈ãtorton baabiraa…ìe mo'on, maa ko …ìuri …óum tii…óude. No e yim…ìe …ìen wi'oo…ìe: \"Joomi amen Rokku men ka aduna\", alanaa mo ka laakara ge…ìal-mo∆¥∆¥al"
  2,201,"No e ma…ì…ìe wi'oo…ìe: Joomi amen, okku min moyyere aduna e laakara, ndanndaa min lebte jayngol"
  2,202,"∆Åen …óon, no woodani …ìe ge…ìal-mo∆¥∆¥al e kon ko …ìe faggitii. Alla ko Yaawu…óo hasboore"
  2,203,"Ja≈ãtee Innde Alla e √±al…ói limtaa…ói. On yaccin…óo e nder bal…óe …ói…ói, bakkaatu fawaaki mo; on ne…ìtin…óo kadi, bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Wonannde on gom…óu…óo. Hulee Alla, nganndon pellet ko ka Makko moo…ìindiroyte-…óon"
  2,204,"No e yim…ìe …ìen on mo konngol mun no haawne ka nguurdam aduna, himo seedi≈ãtina Alla kon ko woni e ndeer …ìernde makko, hara non ko ka≈ãko …ìuri sa…ótude wennje"
  2,205,"Si o huccitii, o yaha ka leydi fii o bonnu e mayri, o halka gese e ge√±√±i. Alla Yi…óaa bononda"
  2,206,"Si o wi'anaama: \"Hulu Alla\", mawni≈ãtinaare he…ìa mo sabu bakkaatu. Jahannama yonii mo, e nge bonii nda…ó…óudi"
  2,207,"No e yim…ìe …ìen: on mo no soo…ótira wo≈ãkii mun kin …óa…ì…ìugol yarluyee Alla. Alla ko Hilnotoo…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen"
  2,208,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ìe, naatiree e lislaamu ka denndanngal, wata on jokku juri seytaane …óin. On ko ga√±o moo…óon …ìa≈ãngu…óo"
  2,209,"Si on oo√±ike …ìaawo koo ko ari on e …ìa≈ãngannduyeeji, nganndee pellet, Alla ko Foolu…óo √ëee√±u…óo"
  2,210,"Taw si …ìee no sabbii: si wanaa nde Allaahu On Arda≈ãta …ìe e ndeer ni…ìe duule wondude e Maalaa'ika en; fiyaaku gasinee. Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde fiyakuuji …óin"
  2,211,"Naamno ge…óal…ìe Israa'iila en:ko jelu woni ko Men Rokki …ìe e maandeeji …ìa≈ãngu…ói! Kala wa…ótitu…óo neema Alla on …ìaawo on arude mo, pellet, Alla ko Tii…óu…óo lepte"
  2,212,"Nguurdam aduna …óam cu…óinanaama …ìeya heefer…ìe, hi…ìe jalkita …ìen gom…óim…ìe. ∆Åen gom…óu…ìe wonoyay dow ma…ì…ìe √±alnde darngal. Alla no Arsikira on Mo O Muuyi, ko aldaa e hasboore"
  2,213,"Yim…ìe …ìen laatino mofte goote. Allaahu On Nuli Annabaa…ìe …ìen, wewlinoo…ìe e jeertinoo…ìe, O Jippindini e ma…ì…ìe Deftere nden hoore goonga, fii yo o √±aawu hakkunde yim…ìe …ìen kon ko …ìe luuondiri e muu…óum. Luutondiraali e muu…óum, si wanaa …ìen rokkaa…ìe nde, …ìaawo kon ko ari …ìe e …ìa≈ãngannduyeeji; ka bewre hakkunde ma…ì…ìe. Allah Fewniri du≈ãyee Makko …ìen gom…óim…ìe e kon ko …ìe luutondiri e muu…óum, immorde e goonga. Alla No Fewna on Mo O Muuyi, faade e laawol focciingol"
  2,214,"Kaa on sikku on naatay aljanna hara araali on sugu kon ko arunoo …ìen wulii…ìe on? He…ìiino …ìen sa…ótteende e lorra, …ìe dillinaa haa Nulaa…óo wi'i, e …ìen gom…óindim…ìe e makko: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ballal Alla ngal?\", hey, pellte ballal Alla ngal …ìa…ótiingal"
  2,215,"∆Åe ngaray naamnaade ma ko hon…óum …ìe sakkotoo, wi'u: \"Si won ko sakki…óon e mo∆¥∆¥ere, ko fii jibin…ìe on, e …ìadondiraa…ìe …ìen, e wondu…ìe …ìen, e …ìilii…ìe …ìen, e setee…ìe …ìen. kalako gollu…óon e mo∆¥∆¥ere, pellet Alla ko Anndu…óo …óum"
  2,216,"Hare nden farlaama e mo'on; nden non ko a√±aande e mo'on,no tijjaa ka a√±oton huunde hara ko nde mo∆¥∆¥ere mon, no tijjaa kadi ka yi…óoton huunde hara ko nde bone mon. Ko Alla No Anndi onon on nganndaa"
  2,217,"Hi…ìe naamno maa fii lewru horma≈ãte ndun, ha…ìugol e mayru, maaku: \"Ha…ìugol e mayru ko mawnu-…óum. Ko sakkagol e laawol Alla ngol e yeddugol Mo e Misiide hormorde nden e yaltingol yim…ìe mayre …ìen e mayre, …ìuri mawnude ka Alla. Ko shirku on kadi …ìuri mawnude dii wargol ngol; …ìe seerataa hi…ìe ha…ìa on haa …ìe rutta on e diina mon, si …ìe haa…ótanii. Kala e mo'on yaltondir…óo e diina mu'un, o maayi ko o keefeero: …ìen …óon, golle ma…ì…ìe …óen bonii aduna e laakara; ko …ìen ngoni yim…ìe yiite, …ìen ko luttoo…ìe ton"
  2,218,"Pellet, …ìen gom…óim…ìe e …ìen feru…ìe ha…ìiri fii laawol Alla, …ìen …óon no jortii Yurmeende Alla; Alla ko Ya'fotoo…óo Huu…ìu…óo-yurmeende"
  2,219,"Hi…ìe naamno-maa fi sanngara e karte, maaku: \"No e …óin …ói…ói bakkaatu maw…óo e nafawoy wonannde yim…ìe …ìen, ko bakkaatu majji on non …ìuri mawnude e dii nafawoy majji on\". Hi…ìe naamno-maa kadi hol ko …ìe sakkotoo? Maaku: \"yaafuya=Ko fawi e haaju\". Ko wano nii Alla ∆Åa≈ãnginira≈ãta on Aayeeje …óen, belajo'o on miijitoto"
  2,220,"Fii aduna on e laakara on, hi…ìe naamno-maa fii wondu…ìe …ìen, maaku: \"Ko mo∆¥∆¥agol e ma…ì…ìe …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude\". Si on jillondirii e ma…ì…ìe, ko musi…ó…ìe mo'on. Alla no Anndi on mo∆¥∆¥inoowo e on bonnoowo. Si Alla muuyuno, O ∆Åi…ótinanayno on. Pellet Alla ko Foolu…óo √ëee√±u…óo"
  2,221,"Wata on resu …ìen rew…ìe shirkay…ìe haa …ìe gom…óina: Mi Woondii ko kor…óo gom…óin…óo …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude debbo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on. Wata on resin …ìen wor…ìe shirkoo…ìe haa …ìe gom…óina: Mi Woondii ko maccu…óo gom…óin…óo …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude dimo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on.∆Åen …óon hi…ìe nodda faade e yiite, Alla No Noddude e Aljanna e haforanal, e du≈ãyee Makko. Himo ∆Åa≈ãngina Aayeeje Makko …óen wonannde yim…ìe …ìen, belajo'o …ìe wa'ajitoto"
  2,222,"Hi…ìe naam-no maa fii fiilordu, maaku: ∆äum ko nefinii …óum; luncitee rew…ìe …ìen fewndo fiilordu, wata on …ìa…óto …ìe haa …ìe laa…ìa. Si …ìe laa…ìii, ngaree e ma…ì…ìe nokku ka Alla Yamiri on …óon. Pellet Alla No Yi…ói tuubaya…ìe …ìen Himo Yi…ói kadi …ìen la…ì…ìinotoo…ìe"
  2,223,"Rew…ìe mon …ìen ko gese mo'on. Ngardee e ngesa mon mbam nokku kala ka faalira…óon, ngardinanee wo≈ãkiiji mon …óin. Hulle Alla, nganndon ko on kawroo…ìe e Makko. Weltin gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  2,224,"Wata on wa…óu Alla heedo fii ngoondooje mon …óen; nde …óiggoton, gom…óon hulon mo∆¥∆¥inon hakkunde yim…ìe …ìen. Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,225,"Alla Nanngitirtaa on gardambi=bolle mehre ka ngoondooje mo'on, kono Himo Nanngitira on kon ko …ìer…óe mon …óen faggitii. Alla ko Hafroowo Mu√±√±ii…óo"
  2,226,"No woodani …ìen woondiroo…ìe suddii…ìe mun …ìen: habbitagol lebbi nayi. Si …ìe ruttike, pellet Alla ko Haforoowo Huu…ìu…óo-yurmeende"
  2,227,"Si …ìe fellitii ceergal ngal, pellet Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,228,"Seeraa…ìe …ìen yo habbi≈ãtin ko'e ma…ì…ìe …óen laa…ìe tati; daga≈ãtaako …ìe suu…óugol kon ko Alla Tagi ka ndeer renngaaji ma…ì…ìe, si wonii hi…ìe gom…óim…ìe Alla e √±alaande sakkitiinde. Ko moodi…ì…ìe ma…ì…ìe jojjidi ruttugol …ìe e …óum, si hawrii hi…ìe faalaa weldital. No woodani …ìen [rew…ìe] yeru kon ko fawii…ìe, no mo∆¥∆¥iri. No woodani wor…ìe …ìen: …ìural e dow ma…ì…ìe. Alla ko Foolu…óo √ëee√±u…óo"
  2,229,"Ceergal, ko laa…ìi …ói…ó: ko jogitorgol no mo∆¥∆¥iri maa accitira no mo∆¥∆¥iri. Daga≈ãtaako on ∆¥ettitugol huunde e kon ko rokku-…óon …ìe, si wanaa hara …ìe hulii [kam…ìe …ói…óo] nde …ìe nii…ìnataa keeri Alla …óin. Si on hulii ro≈ãkude √±ii…ìnude keeri Alla …óin, goopi alanaa …ìe e kon ko debbo on soktori. ∆äin ko keeri Alla, wata on jaggitu-…ói. kala jaggitu…óo keeri Alla …óin, ko …ìen ngoni too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  2,230,"Si o seerii mo, on [debbo] dagita≈ãtaako mo …ìaawo …óu'um, haa o resindira e gorko goo. Si on [gorko] seerii mo, goopi fawaaki …ìe nde …ìe ruttondira, si …ìe fellitii √±ii…ìnugol keeri Alla …óin.∆äin ko keeri Allah, Himo ∆Åa≈ãnginana …ói …ìen yim…ìe nganndu…ìe"
  2,231,"Si on seerii rew…ìe …ìen, laje ma…ì…ìe …óen yottike: jogitoree-…ìe no mo∆¥∆¥iri maa accitoron …ìe no mo∆¥∆¥iri. Wata on jogitor …ìe lorrugol nde jaggitoton. Kala wa…óu…óo …óum, gom…óii o too√±ii hoore-makko. Wata on jogitor Aayeeje Alla …óen jalnori. Annditee neemaaji Alla …ói O Neemini e mo'on, e ko O Jippini e mo'on immorde e Deftere e √ëee√±al; Himo Wa'ajora …óum. Hulle Alla, nganndon pellet Alla ko Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  2,232,"Si on seerii rew…ìe …ìen, laje ma…ì…ìe …óen yottike, wata on laagu …ìe nde moodi…ì…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen resata …ìe; si …ìe welondirii hakkunde ma…ì…ìe no mo∆¥∆¥iri. ∆äum no waajoree on taw…óo e mo'on no gom…óini Alla e √ëalaande Sakkitiinde. Ko ja≈ãtana…óon koo …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde on, …ìuri laa…ìaande. Alla No Anndi onon on nganndaa"
  2,233,"Jibim…ìe …ìen yo muynin …ìi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen duu…ìi …ói…ói timmu…ói; wonannde on faandii…óo timminde muyninngol ngol.No fawii jibinanaa…óo on, √±ammingol holitinira [rew…ìe] …ìen no mo∆¥∆¥iri. Wo≈ãkii woo fawaaka si wanaa ko ki waawata. Wata jibin…óo on lorrire sabu …ìi…ó…óo makko on, wanaa jibinanaa…óo on kadi lorrirtee sabu …ìi…ó…óo makko on; no fawii ronoowo on yeru …óum. Si …ìe faandike entude e hoore yarlondiral hakkunde ma…ì…ìe e diisondiral, bakkaatu fawaaki …ìe. Si on faandike …óa…ì…ìude muyninanoowo on …ìi…ó…ìe mon …ìen, bakkaatu fawaakii on, si on jonnirii kon ko …ìen [muyninoo…ìe] hanndi e mo∆¥∆¥ere.Hulee Alla, nganndon ko O Reenu…óo kala ko golloton"
  2,234,"∆Åen maayoo…ìe e mo'on …ìe acca suddii…ìe: yo …ìen habbi≈ãtin ko'e ma…ì…ìe lebbi nayi e bal…óe sappo. Si …ìe yottike laje ma…ì…ìe …óen, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko …ìe wa…óani ko'e ma…ì…ìe no mo∆¥∆¥iri. Alla Ko Humpitii…óo kon ko golloton"
  2,235,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko wee…ìitoton, e sabboyde suddii…ìe …ìen, maa suu…óu…óon …óum ka wo≈ãkiiji mo'on. Alla No Anndi aray ka annditon fii ma…ì…ìe, ko woni tun, wata on fodondir e ma…ì…ìe [desal] e gunndoo: si wanaa nde wowloton ko≈ãngol mo∆¥∆¥ol, wata on fellitu humugol dewgal ngal haa lajal edda ngal yottoo. Ngande pellet Alla No Anndi ko woni e wo≈ãkiiji mo'on, Re≈ãtee e Makko, nganndon pellet Alla Ko Haforoowo Mu√±√±ii…óo"
  2,236,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on si on seerii suddii…ìe …ìen ado on renndude e ma…ì…ìe maa ja≈ãtanagol …ìe te≈ãe, dakmitee …ìe:no fawii galo on yeru makko, no fawii kadi baydoolo on yeru makko.Dakmitirgol …ìe no mo∆¥∆¥iri.Hannduyee fawii…óo mo∆¥im…ìe …ìen"
  2,237,"Si on seerii suddii…ìe …ìen ado on meemude …ìe, tawa on ja≈ãtanike …ìe te≈ãe: ko feccere kon ko ja≈ãti-…óon, si wanaa hara …ìe ya'afi maa on mo dewgal woni e juu…óe mu'un ya'afii. Ko nde ya'afoto…óon …ìurata …ìa…ótinnde gom…óal. Wata on yejjitu …ìural ngal hakkunde mo'on. pellet Alla ko Reenu…óo kala ko golloton"
  2,238,"Reenee e jul…óe …óen, e julde hakkundeere nden. Darano…óon Alla ko o to∆¥∆¥inii…ìe"
  2,239,"Si on hulii, juulee ko on seppay…ìe maa wa…ó…óii…ìe. Si on hoolike, ja≈ãtee Innde Alla nden wano O Anndiniri on kon ko on nganndaano"
  2,240,"∆Åen maayoo…ìe e mo'on …ìe acca suddii…ìe: ko wasiyanagol suddii…ìe …ìen dakmitor…óum haa hitaande nden timma, ko aldaa e yalti≈ãgol …ìe. Si …ìe yaltii, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko …ìe wa…óani ko'e ma…ì…ìe e mo∆¥∆¥ere. Alla ko Foolu…óo √ëee√±u…óo"
  2,241,"No woodani …ìen seeraa…ìe: dakamitorgol no mo∆¥∆¥iri. ko goongofawii…óo gom…óu…ìe …ìen"
  2,242,"Ko wano nii Alla ∆Åa≈ãnginira≈ãta on Aayeeje Makko …óen, belajo'o on haqqilay"
  2,243,"E a tinaali …ìen njaltunoo…ìe e galleeji mu'un, kam…ìe ko …ìe guluuje, ka reenagol e maayde, Allaahu On Daalani …ìe: \"Maayee\", refti O Wuurniti …ìe? Pellet Alla ko Jom ∆Åural e dow yim…ìe …ìen, ko woni tun, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen njaanataa [Alla]"
  2,244,"Ha…ìee fii laawol Alla Ngol, nagndon pellet Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,245,"Ko hombo woni on √±awloowo Alla √±amaande mo∆¥∆¥ere, O Sowitana mo nde cowalle …óuu…óu…óe? Alla No ∆Åi…óttina Himo Ya√±√±a, ko faade ka Makko ruttete-…óon"
  2,246,"E a tinaali ngun mbatu …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'ila, …ìaawo Muusaa, tuma nde …ìe wi'annoo Annabaajo ma…ì…ìe on: \"Imminan men lam…óo, men ha…ìa fii laawol Alla Ngol?\" O maaki: \"Hara on tijjaaki si hare nden farlaama e mo'on nde ro≈ãkoton ha…ìude?\" …ìe mbi'i: \"Ko ha…óata men ha…ìugol e fii laawol Alla Ngol, gom…óii men njaltinaama e galleeji amen e …ìi…ó…ìe amen?\" Nde hare nden farlanoo e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe hucciti, si wanaa see…óaa…ìe e ma…ì…ìe. Alla Ko Anndu…óo too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  2,247,"Annabaajo ma…ì…ìe on maakani …ìe:\"Alla Imminanii on Taaluuta laam…óo\". ∆Åe mbi'i:\"Hol no laamu laatora≈ãta mo e hoore amen,ko menen …ìuri mo haandude e laamu,o rokkaaka yaajeende jawdi?\" O maaki:\"Alla Su…ìike mo e dow mo'on,O ∆Åeydi mo yaajeende ka ganndal e ka …ìanndu\". Alla No Rokka Laamu Makko Ngun on Mo O Muuyi,Alla ko Yaaju…óo […ìural] Anndu…óo"
  2,248,"Annabaajo ma…ì…ìe on maakani …ìe: \"Nganndee Maande Alla nden, ko nde Arkawal ngal arata on; dee∆¥ere no e ndeer maggal, immorde ka Joomi mo'on, e ko heddinoo ko aalo Muusaa e aalo Haaruuna en acci, hara Malaa'ika en no ronndii ngal. Pellet no e koo ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo, Maande wonannde on; si o laatike gom…óim…ìe"
  2,249,"Nde Taaluuta yaltidunoo e konu ngun, o maaki: \"Alla No Jarribora on caangol: kala yar…óo e maggol o jeyaaka e am, kala mo me…óaali ngol ko on …óon jeyaa e am, si wanaa on √±e…óir…óo junngo mun √±e…óannde\". ∆Åe yari e caangol ngol si wanaa see…óaa…ìe e ma…ì…ìe. Nde o lummbunoo ngol, ka≈ãko e …ìen gom…óim…ìe wondu…ìe e makko, …ìen mbi'i: \"Feere alanaa en e Jaaluuta e konu mun ngun\". ∆Åen fellitu…ìe hawray e Alla …ìen mbi'i: \"Heewii ka fedde tokosere fooliri fedde …óuu…óunde, du≈ãayee Alla\". Pellet Alla No Wondi e mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìen"
  2,250,"Nde …ìe fee√±annoo Jaaluuta e konu mun ngun, …ìe mbi'i: \"Joomi amen, Rufu mu√±al e dow amen, Tabi≈ãtinaa teppe amen, Faabo-…óaa men e …ìee heefer…ìe"
  2,251,"∆Åe fooliri…ìe Du≈ãayee Alla: Daawuuda wari Jaaluuta, Alla Rokki mo Laamu e Annabaaku, O Anndini mo kon ko O Muuyi. Si wanaano Ko Alla Du√±irnoo yim…ìe …ìen yoga e dow yoga, leydi ndin bonayno. Kono Alla Ko Jom ∆Åural e dow winndere nden"
  2,252,"∆äen ko Aayeeje Alla, Me…óen Ja≈ãnga …óe e dow maa…óa wondude e Goonga, Pellet ko a jeyaa…óo e Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  2,253,"∆Åen Nulaa…ìe, Men ∆Åurnii yoga ma…ì…ìe e dow yoga : No e ma…ì…ìe yeewtidu…ìe e Alla, O ∆Åa≈ãti darjaaji yoga e ma…ì…ìe; Men Rokki Iisaa, …ìi…ó…óo Maryama on, …ìanngannduyeeji Men semmbiniri mo fittaandu laa…ìundu ndun. Si Alla Muuyuno, wom…ìe …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe …ìen wartindirtaano …ìaawo nde …ìanngannduyeeji …óin ari maab…ìe. Kono …ìe luutondiri: no e ma…ì…ìe …ìen gom…óim…ìe, no e ma…ì…ìe …ìen yeddu…ìe. Si Alla Muuyuno, …ìe wartindirtaano, kono Alla no wa…óa kon ko O Yi…ói"
  2,254,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ìe, sakkee e kon ko Men Arsiki on adii √±alaande arde; nde ngeyngu alaa e mayre, wanaa sehilaaku, wanaa tefoore. Ko heefer…ìe …ìen woni too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  2,255,"Alla, alaa reweteezo si wanaa kanko, Wuur…óo √ëii…ìu…óo. ≈äo≈ãre nanngataa Mo, wanaa kadi …óoyngol. ko Kanko Jeyi huunde ko woni ka kammuuli e huunde ko woni ka leydi. Ko hommbo woni on tefoowo ka Makko si wanaa e du≈ãayee Makko? Himo anndi ko woni yeeso ma…ì…ìe, e ko woni …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åe hu…ìindotaako huunde e Anndal Makko ngal si wanaa ko O Muuyi. Jullere Makko nden no yaaji …ìuri kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Reenugol …ói aaninaa Mo. Ko Kano woni Toowu…óo Maw…óo On. @Corrected"
  2,256,"Doolugol alaa ka diina. Gom…óii peewal ngal …ìanngii immorde e majjere nden. Kala yeddu…óo …óuu…óa bewreeru ndun o gom…óini Alla, haray o jogitike …ìoggi finnde hoolaare …óin, firtagol alanaa …ói. Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,257,"Alla Ko Gi…óo gom…óim…ìe …ìen: Himo yaltina …ìe e ni…ìe, O na…ìa …ìe e ndaygu. ∆Åeya yeddu…ìe, yi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe ko …óuu…óa bewreeji …óin: Hi…ói yaltina …ìe e ndaygu na…ìa …ìe e ni…ìe. ∆Åen ko yim…ìe yiite, luttoo…ìe e magge"
  2,258,"E a yi'aali on wennju…óo Ibraahiima e fii Jey…óo mo On, fii Alla no Ye…ói mo laamu, nde Ibraahiima maakunoo: \"Jey…óo lam on, ko On Wuurnata Wara\". [Wennju…óo on] wi'i: \"Min kadi mi…óo wuurna wara\". Ibraahiima maaki: \"Pellet Alla no Addira naange ngen fu…ónaange, addir nge hiirnaange\".Yeddu…óo on mugaa. Alla fewnataa yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  2,259,"Wolla ko hono oon birtii…óo wuro yeewngo ngo maadi mum e mbildi mum yirbi o wi*i hono Alla wuurtaninta …óum caggal maayde mum? Alla wari mbo o lelii duu…ìi teemedere O ummini mbo O daali hono foti √±ii…ì…óa o wi*i √±alawma maa feccere √±alawma, O daali alah a duumiima …óo duu…ìi teemedere ∆¥eew √±aamdu ma e njaram ma waylaaki ndaaru mbabba ma ba, ngam min mba…ó ma maande wonande yim…ìe, ∆¥eew ∆¥i*e nomin cardata…óe refti Min muurda…óe teew, nde …óuum fee√±i mbo o wi*i mi anndi Alla na hattani kala huunde…ì…ó∆¥∆¥√±j"
  2,260,"Nde Ibraahiima maaki joom am hollam na nguurtanirta maay…ìe, O daali mate a goon…óinaani? o maaki ohonkay kono ko haa …ìernde am dee∆¥a , O daali nanngu colli nay tappu…ói faade e ma refti mba…óa e kala tulde feccere e colli he refti noddu…ói …ói ngara e ma ho…ói njaha anndu Alla ko pooloowo mbo fooletaake ko O √±ee√±o"
