  2,277,…ìeen goon…óin…ìe ngolli ko mo∆¥∆¥i o darni juulde o tottiri askal woodanii…ìe jobdi mum en ummaade ko joomi mum en kulol alanaa…ìe …ìe ngonah sunatoo…ìe
  2,278,Eehey mon goon…óin…ìe kulee Alla accon ko heddii ko e riba si on ngonii goon…óu…ìe
  2,279,Si on mba…óaani …óuum kolliree hare ummorde e Alla e nelaa…óo MakkoJJJ…ìJ
  2,280,"Si tawii o wonii e satteende yo o mu√±ane haa e yaajeende,nde cakkorton …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e mon si on ngonii anndu…ìe"
  2,281,Kulee √±alngu ngu nduttete…óon ka Alla refti yo…ìee kala fittaandu ko ndu faggitii ko kam…ìe …ìe too√±etaake
  2,282,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ìe si on √±amlandiri nyamaande faade happu dottaa…óo mbinndee nde, yo nuun…óu…óo winndu hakkunde mon, woto binndoowo sala winndude yo o winndu no Alla anndiniri mbo, yo o winndu yo mbo hakke woni dow mum winndu yo o hul joomiiko woto o ustu heen hay huunde, si wonii mbo hakke woni e dow mum ko …óaay…óo wolla loh…óo wollo o waawah fidde, yo keedo makko fidir nuun…óal, ceednee seede en …ói…óo e wor…ìe mon, si wor…ìe …ói…óo ngalah ko gorko e rew…ìe …ói…óo …ìe mbelete …óon e seedeeli ngam si gooto e ma…ì…ìe yrdditi go…ó…óo o siftirina mbo, woto seedeeli cala si…ìe noddaama, wote kaaste winndude ko fam…ói maa ko heewi faade e happu mum, ko …óuum …ìuri nuun…óude ka Alla …ìuri fooccaade wonande seede …ìuri kadi …ìadaade waasde mon sikkitaade, si wonah kommersaagu ngonaangu ngu yiilaton hakkunde mon, ndeen noon bakkaat alah e mon nde mbaasaton …óum winndude, ceetnee si on yeeyandiri woto binndoowo e seede lore, si on wa…óii …óuum pellet …óuum ko faasikaagal e mon, kulee Alla O anndina on Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde"
  2,283,"Si on ngonii e …óatngal on ke…ìaani binndoowo tottirre jukunnde tamaande, si on koolandirii, oon tottaa…óo hoolaare yo tottit hoolaare nde, yo o hul Alla joom makko, wotee cuu…óe seedanfaagu kala cuu…óo ngu pellet oon …ìernde makko ko bakkadinnde, Alla na anndi ko ngollaton ko"
  2,284,"Woodanii Alla ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi si on …ìannginii ko e pittaali mon wolla on cuu…ói ma Alla haasbu mon sabu mum, O yaafoo mbo O wela O lepta mbo wela, Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde"
  2,285,"Nulaa…óo goon…óanii ko jippinaa ko e Makko ummade e Joom Makko, e goonin…ìe …ìe fof …ìe goon…óanii Alla e malaykaaji Makko e defte makko e Nulaa…ìe makko, min ceerndatah hay gooto e Nulaa…ìe makko, …ìe wii min nanii min …óoftiima hafran amen Joomi amen ko Mah woni ruttorde"
  2,286,"Alla fawatah fittaandu kondu hattanaani,woodanii ndu kondu faggii, fawiima e dow mayru kondu faggitii,Joomi amen woto nanngir min ko min njjiti ko wollo ko min ngoopi ko,woto A faw e amen tampere hono no ndoondirna…óa …ìeen adii…ìe amen,Joomi amen woto faw min komin kattanaani,yaafa amin cuura bakkatuuJi amen nJurma…óa min ko Aan woni keeda amin wollu min e dow yim…ìe heeferee…ìe …ìe"
  3,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  3,2,"Alla: rewetee…óo woo alaa si wanaa Ka≈ãko. Ko O Wuur…óo, √ëii…ìu…óo"
  3,3,"O Jippinirii Deftere nden dow maa…óa e goonga, goonginnde ko adii nde, O Jippini Tawreeta e Linnjiila"
