  17,71,"√ëannde Men noddiroyta kala yim…ìe yeesoojo ma…ì…ìe on,kala on jonnitiroyaa…óo deftere makko nden ka √±aamo makko …ìen …óon …ìe janngay deftere ma…ì…ìe nden …ìe too√±irtaake hay yeru gaarayol hun tamaro"
