  18,18,"Hi…óa sikka …ìe ko …ìe finu…ìe, hara kam…ìe ko …ìe …óaanii…ìe, Me…óen waylitira …ìe senngo √±aamo e senngo nano, rawaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun no fonti kay…óe mun …óen ka dammbugal, si a ∆¥ellitike e ma…ì…ìe a huccitayno e ma…ì…ìe dogaa a heewayno kulol immorde e ma…ì…ìe"
  18,19,"Ko nii Men immintiniri …ìe fii yo …ìe lanndondir hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, wi'oowo wi'i immorde e ma…ì…ìe: \"No foti hewde ko √±ii…ìu…óon?\" ∆Åe wi'i: \"Men √±ii…ìii √±allal maa go…ó…óun e √±allal.\" ∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko Joomi mon woni Anndu…óo emmbere ko √±ii…ìu…óon, nulee go…ó…óo e mon wonndude e …óii kaaki=ceede mon …óoo ka saare, yo o ndaaru ko hommbo e ma…ì…ìe …ìuri laa…ìude √±aamitee, yo o addan on √±aametee immorde e on …óon, yo o molto wata gooto so'u fii mon"
  18,20,"Pellet, kam…ìe si …ìe ∆¥ellitike e mon …ìe rajmay on, maa…óun …ìe rutta on e laawol ma…ì…ìe ngol, ontuma hara on maletaake poomaa"
  18,21,"Ko nii Men yaltiniri fii ma…ì…ìe, fii yo …ìe anndu pellet, Fodoore Alla nden ko nde Goonga, Pellet, Darngal ngal sikke alaa e maggal. Tuma nde …ìe poo…óondiraynoo hakkunde ma…ì…ìe fiyaake ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe wi'i: \"Mahee e hoore ma…ì…ìe maadi, ko Joomi ma…ì…ìe woni Anndu…óo fii Ma…ì…ìe.\" ∆Åen foolu…ìe e fiyaake mu'un wi'i: \"Men jogitoto e dow ma…ì…ìe Juulirde"
  18,22,"Aray …ìe wi'a: \"Ko …ìe tato naya…ìo ma…ì…ìe ko rawaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun.\" ∆Åe wi'a kadi: \"Ko …ìe njowo njeega…ìo ma…ì…ìe ko rawaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun ko fampaangol ka ni…ìe.\" ∆Åe wi'a kadi: \"Ko …ìe njee…ói…óo njeetata…ìo ma…ì…ìe ko rawaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun.\" Maaku: \"Ko Joomi an woni Anndu…óo limoore ma…ì…ìe, anndaa …ìe si wanaa see…óaa…ìe.\" Wata a wennju fii ma…ì…ìe si wanaa yewtere fee√±unde, wata a lanndo fii ma…ì…ìe hay e gooto e ma…ì…ìe"
  18,23,"Wata a wi'an huunde: \"Min mi wa…óay …óun janngo"
  18,24,"Si wanaa si Alla Muuyii, janto Joomi maa…óa si a yejjitii, maaku: \"No tijjaa nde Joomi an Fewnan mi ko …ìuri …ìadaade immorde e …óun Peewal"
  18,25,"∆Åe √±ii…ìi ka fammeere ma…ì…ìe duu…ìi teeme…ó…óe tati, …ìe …ìeydi jeenay"
  18,26,"Maaku: \"Ko Alla woni Anndu…óo emmbere ko …ìe √±ii…ìi, ko Kanko heeranii ko wirnii kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi kaawes ko yi'iri wa Makko e ko naniri, alanaa …ìe gaanin Makko gi…óo, O kafidaa ka √ëaawoore Makko hay e gooto"
  18,27,"Janngu ko wahayinaa e maa…óa kon immorde e Deftere Joomi maa nden, alaa wattitoowo Daaluyeeji=konngudi Makko …óin, a he…ìataa gaanin Makko fattorde"
  18,28,"Tabintin wonkii maa…óa kin wonndude e …ìen noddoo…ìe Joomi ma…ì…ìe ka bimmbi e ka kiikii…óe hi…ìe faandii Jaati Makko Kin, wata gite maa …óe yawtu gaayi ma…ì…ìe hara hi…óa faandii cu…óaari ngurdan aduna, wota a …óofto on mo Men welsindini …ìernde mun gaayi jantagol Men o jokki belee…óe makko fiyaake makko on woni halkaare"
  18,29,"Maaku Goonga kan immorde ka Joomi mon, mono faalaa yo o gom…óin mono faalaa yo o yeddu, Menen Men heblanii too√±oo…ìe …ìen Yiite no hunnditi …ìe …óen…óe magge …óen si …ìe …óa…ì…ìii faabo, …ìe faaboree ndiyan wa'u…óan wa sila taynaa…óo …óan ju…óa geece …óen, bonii njaram bonii werde"
  18,30,"Pellet, …ìen gom…óin…ìe …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin, Menen Men yeebataa njoddi kala mo∆¥∆¥in…óo golle"
  18,31,"∆Åen …óon no woodani …ìe Aljannaaji √±ii…ìal can…ói no ila ley ma…ì…ìe, hi…ìe cu…óiree ton immorde e jawe kan≈ãe …ìe …ìornoo conci haaki…óu…ói …óewlu…ói e jalbu…ói ko …ìe so…ì…ìindii…ìe=tuugiibe ton e hoore julle, mo∆¥∆¥ii mbarjaari mo∆¥∆¥ii kadi fowtorde"
  18,32,"fiyan …ìe misal,wor…ìe …ói…óo Men wa…óani go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe gese …ói…ói inab Menhunndintini =hurliride …óe tamarooje Men wa…ói hakkunde majje remuru"
  18,33,"∆äen gese …ói…ói kala addi √±aametee majje, …óe too√±aali hay e huunde e …óun, Men seeki hakkunde majje [gese …óen …ói…ói] caangol"
  18,34,"Wonani mo dim…óe, o wi'ani wonndii…óo makko on tawi himo yewtude mo: \"Min mi…óo …ìurumaa jawdi e teddude gorol"
  18,35,"O naati ka ngesa makko tawi ko o too√±u…óo hoore-makko, o wi'i: \"Mi sikkaa mbaa re'ay poomaa\". @Corrected"
  18,36,"Mi sikkaa kdai Darngal ngal daroto, mi woondii si mi artira le ka Joomi an, maa mi tawu sanne, waylitorde …ìurnde mba mo∆¥∆¥ude"
  18,37,"Wonndii…óo makko on wi'ani mo, tawi himo yewtude mo: \"Enee, a yeddii On Tagu…óo ma immorde mbullaari=leydi refti e to…ì…ìere [maniiyu] refti O fonndumaa gorko"
  18,38,"Kono min ko Kanko Alla woni Joomi an, mi kafidataa e Joomi an hay gooto"
  18,39,"Ko haanunoo tuma nde naatu…óaa ka ngesa maa…óa wi'aa: \"Ko Alla muuyi kon doole alaa si wanaa Alla\". Si a yi'ii lan, min mi…óo …ìurumaa fan…óude jawdi e …ìi…ó…ìe"
  18,40,No jortaa nde Joomi an okkoyta lan mo∆¥∆¥ere …ìurnde ngesa maa mban O nula e mabba lepte immorde ka kammu mba wonta boowal …ìowrungal
  18,41,"Maa…óun ndiyan mabba …óan wonta …ìee…ìu…óan, hara a hattantaake …óa…ì…ìugol …óan"
  18,42,"Dim…óe makko …óen bonnaa o weeti himo waylita newe makko …óen e dow ko o nafki kon e mabba, tawi kammba ko fukkiimba e da∆¥∆¥e mabba, himo wi'a: \"Ee jalla min, hara mi kafidaano e Joomi an hay e gooto"
  18,43,"Laatanaaki mo fedde nde no walla mo gaanin Alla, o wonaali foolu…óo"
  18,44,No ton Giggol Alla Goongawol ngol ko Kanngo mo∆¥∆¥i mbarjaari mo∆¥∆¥i battane
  18,45,"Fiyan …ìe misal ngurdan aduna …óan no wa'i wa ndiyan Men jippini…óan immorde ka kammu jillondiri e majjan pu…ói leydi ndin, …ói wonti muncii…ói keneeli no jaroo…ói, Alla wonii ko O Hattan…óo e dow kala huunde"
  18,46,"Jawdi ndin e …ìi…ó…ìe wor…ìe …ìen ko cu…óaari ngurndan aduna, mo∆¥∆¥i heddotoo…ói …óin ko …óin …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude mbarjaari ka Joomi maa…óa e mo∆¥∆¥ude yela"
  18,47,"√ëannde Men na…ìata pelle …óen a yi'ay leydi ndin ko fee√±undi, Men moo…ìa …ìe Men accataa immorde e ma…ì…ìe hay e gooto"
  18,48,"∆Åe holliree ka Joomi maa [ko …ìe] saffewol, [O Daalana …ìe] gom…óii on arii e Amen wano Men tagirnoo on non, ka laawol aranol, ko woni on aa∆¥ino wonnde Men wa…óanaali on fodoore"
  18,49,"Deftere nden wallinee, a yi'ay bom…ìe …ìen ko hul…ìe ko woni kon e mayre, …ìe wi'a: \"Ee bone amen, ko he…ìi ndee deftere nde …óalataa tosokun wanaa njanun si wanaa nde moftii …óun, …ìe tawa ko …ìe golli kon no wee…ìitaa, Joomi maa…óa too√±ataa hay e gooto"
  18,50,"Tuma nde Men wi'annoo Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen: \"Sujjanee Aadama, …ìe sujji si wanaa Ibliisa o laatike jeyaa…óo e jinnaaji …óin o yalti e Yamiroore Joomi makko. E on jogitoto mo e …ìi…ó…ìe makko …ìen yim…ìe gaanin An, hara kam…ìe ko …ìe ay…ìe mo'on, bonanii too√±oo…ìe …ìen battudi"
  18,51,"Mi tawnaali …ìe tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin wanaa tagugol ko'e ma…ì…ìe kadi, Mi wonaali jogitotoo…óo majjinoo…ìe …ìen sembinoo…ìe. @Corrected"
  18,52,"E √±annde O Daalata: \"Noddee kafidaa…ìe An …ìen, …ìen …ìe aa∆¥i…óon, …ìe nodda …ìe, …ìe jaabotaako …ìe Men wa…ói hakkunde ma…ì…ìe halkorde"
  18,53,"Bom…ìe …ìen yi'a Yiite ngen …ìe fellita wonnde kam…ìe ko …ìe ukketee…ìe e magge, …ìe he…ìataa gaayi magge yiltorde"
  18,54,"Gom…óii Men fensitanii yim…ìe …ìen e nder ndee Alqur'aanaare immorde e kala misal, ne…ó…óanke on wonii himo …ìuri kala huunde wennjugol"
  18,55,"Ha…óaali yim…ìe …ìen nde …ìe gom…óinta …ìe insinanoo Joomi ma…ì…ìe tuma nde Peewal ngal arunoo e ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa nde arata e ma…ì…ìe sunna aran…ìe …ìen maa…óun nde arata e ma…ì…ìe lepte …óen ko …óe fee√±u…óe"
  18,56,"Men Nuliraali Nulaa…ìe …ìen si wanaa ko weltinoo…ìe e jertinoo…ìe, …ìen heefer…ìe hi…ìe wennjana meere nden fii yo …ìe fuynir nde Goonga kan, …ìe jogitii Aayeeje An …óen e ko …ìe jertiniraa kon jalnori"
  18,57,"Alaa fotay…óo too√±ude on waajuraa…óo Aayeeje Joomi makko o …óuurii=fali e gaayi majje o yejjiti ko juu…óe makko …óen ardini kon. Menen Men wa…óii e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen cokoo…óe fii wota …ìe faamu nde, ka noppi ma…ì…ìe kadi pahu, hay si a noddii …ìe faade e Peewal …ìe feewataa ontuma haapoomaa"
  18,58,"Ko Joomi mon woni Surroowo ko O Jom Hinnayee on, sinndo O nangitirno …ìe ko …ìe faggitii kon O yaccinanayno …ìe lepte …óen, ko woni, no woodani …ìe fodoore …ìe he…ìataa gaanin mayre fattorde"
  18,59,"∆äen ca'e, Men halkuno …ìe tuma nde …ìe too√±unoo Men wa…óani halkeede ma…ì…ìe nden Fodoore"
  18,60,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo sagataa makko on: \"Mi seerataa haa mi yottoo ka fottirde maaje …óen …ói…ói, maa…óun mi wuloo jamaanu"
  18,61,"Tuma nde …ìe yottoyinoo hakkonde majje …ìe yejjiti linngil ma…ì…ìe ngil, ngil jogitii laawol maggil ka maayo wuddere"
  18,62,"Nde …ìe lummbunoo o [Muusaa] maakani sagataa makko on: \"Anndanii en sojjaari=bottaari men ndin, gom…óii en hawrii e nduu yaadu men …óoo tampere"
  18,63,"O wi'i: \"A yi'ii, nde soruno…óen ka fetere, min mi yejjuno linngil ngil, yejjintinaali lan fii maggil si wanaa Seytaane nde mi anndita ngil, ngil jogitii laawol maggil ka maayo no hawnori"
  18,64,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ko …óon ko won…óen …óa…ì…ìude kon [woni], …ìe ruttii e …ìatteeji ma…ì…ìe fillitagol"
  18,65,"∆Åe tawoyi jeyaa…óo immorde e jeyaa…ìe Amen Men Okki mo Hinnayee immorde ka Amen, Men Anndini mo immorde e Amen Ganndal"
  18,66,"Muusaa maakani mo: \"Enee [a accay] mi jokkete fii yo a anndinan go…ó…óun e ko anndina…óaa kon Peewal"
