  18,72,"[Khadiru] maaki: \"Enee, mi wi'aano ma pellet, an a hattantaake mu√±al wonndugol e am"
  18,73,"[Muusaa] maaki: wata a jogoran ko mi yijjiti kon, wata a hewtinan e fiyaake an on satteende"
  18,74,"∆Åe yahi haa nde …ìe fottunoo e suka o wari mo! O maakani [mo]: \"E a waru wonkii laa…ìuki tanaa [yo…ìtanagol] wonkii, gom…óii a addii huunde a√±iinde"
  18,75,"[Khadiru] wi'i: \"Enee, mi wi'aano ma pellet, an a hattantaake mu√±al wonndugol e an"
  18,76,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Si mi lanndike ma gaayi huunde …ìaawo …óii, haray wata a wonndino e an, gom…óii a timminii nganto e an"
  18,77,"∆Åe yahi haa …ìe yaltiti e yim…ìe saare, …ìe …óa…ì…ìiri …ìe √±aametee …ìe salii wernude …ìe, …ìe tawi e nder mayre maadi faalaa fukkaade [Khadiru] o darnindi , o [Muusaa] maaki: \"Sinno a yi…óuno a ∆¥ettayno njoddi e …óun"
  18,78,"[Khadiru] maaki: \"Ko …óum woni seedigal hakku- nde an e ma'a, aray mi yiito maa firo kon ko a hattananooka mun√±aade e dow mun"
  18,79,"Si ko laana kan, ka laatanike miskinee…ìe gollo- …ìe ka maayo, mi faalaa aybinnde ka, hari laatike …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe lam…óo himo nannga kala laana o ja…ìta"
