  18,99,"Men …óala yoga e ma…ì…ìe nden √±alnde no yolloo e yoga, wuttaa ka allaadu Men moo…ìa …ìe moo…ìudee"
  18,100,Men wee…ìitanay(holliray) Jahannama nden √±annde yeddu…ìe …ìen wee…ìitugol=holllirgol
  18,101,"∆Åen …ìe gite mun laatii e wirngallo gaayi janta An, …ìe laati…ìe hattantaake nanugol"
