  20,53,"On wa…óan…óo on leydi ndin we∆¥∆¥itaandi, o naadani on e nder mayri laawi, O jippini immorde e kammu ngun ndiyam Men yaltiniri …óam nooneeji immorde e pu…ói sertu…ói"
