  20,71,"[Fir'awna] wi'i: Eyoo, on gom…óinii mo ko adii mi du≈ãanaade(sakkitaade) on? Pelet, ko kanko woni maw…óo mo'on on anndin…óo on mbilaaku ngun, mi woondii, maa mi ta∆¥a juu…óe mon …óen e koy…óe mon …óen ta∆¥a luutindira, maa mi feta on e julle tama aray anndon ko hommbo e amen …ìuri lepte sa…ótu…óe e heddotoo…óe"
  20,72,"[Mbilee…ìe …ìen] wi'i: \"Men …ìurnataa ma e dow koo ko ari e amen immorde e …ìannganguyeeji, e On Tagu…óo men, [an Fir'awna] √±aawu ko √±aawataa kon, pellet, ko √±aawataa ko ka ngurndan aduna …óoo"
  20,73,"Menen dey, men gom…óinii Joomi amen fii yo o yawtan men goopi amen e kon ko doolu…óaa men e mu'un immorde e mbilewu ngun, ko Alla woni Mo∆¥∆¥o Heddotoo…óo. @Corrected"
  20,74,"Pellet on mo ari ka Joomi mu'un hara ko o bon…óo; haray pellet, no woodani mo Jahannama o maayataa e nder magge o wuurataa kadi"
  20,75,"mo ari ka Makko ko o gom…óin…óo hara gom…óii o golliino mo∆¥∆¥i …óin, haray …ìen …óon no woodani …ìe Darjaaji Toowu…ói …óin"
  20,76,"Aljannaaji √ëii…ìal no doga e ley majji can…ói …óin, ko …ìe duumotoo…ìe nder ton, ko …óum woni njo…ìdi on la…ì…ìinii…óo. @Corrected"
  20,77,"Gom…óii Men wahaynii faade e Muusaa ro∆¥idu e jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen wa…óan …ìe laawol yooru ngol ka maayo joorngol wata a hulu hewtiteede wata a hulu [yoolagol]"
  20,78,"Fir'awna jokkitiri …ìe koneeli makko …óin, suumi …ìe ka maayo ko suumi …ìe kon"
  20,79,"Fir'awnan majjini yim…ìe makko …ìen, o fewnaali […ìe]"
  20,80,"Ko onon yo …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila gom…óii Men danndiino on e ga√±o mon on, Men fodi on kadi ka ban≈ãe √±aamo [fello] Tuuri ngon, Men jippini e moo…óon Manna= …óacce njumri e doobe"
  20,81,"√ëaamee immorde e laa…ìu…ói ko Men arsiki on kon, wota on bewu e nder mu'un sakko Tikkere Am nden jippo e mo'on, on mo Tikkere Am jippii e mu'un gom…óii haray o halkike"
  20,82,"Pellet, Min ko Mi heewu…óo Yawtanngol wonannde on tuubu…óo o gom…óini o golli ko mo∆¥∆¥i refti o feewi"
  20,83,Ko hon…óun he√±inmaa gaayi yim…ìe maa …ìen an Muusaa
  20,84,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"∆Åee…óoo, hi…ìe iwtiri …ìaawo am, mi he√±ike ka Maa…óa Joomi fii yo A welto"
  20,85,"[Alla] Daali: \"Pellet, Mennen gom…óii Men jarribike=finninii yim…ìe maa…óa …ìen …ìaawo maa…óa, Saamiriiyu majjinii …ìe"
  20,86,"Muusaa ruttii ka yim…ìe makko …ìen ko o tikku…óo sunii…óo; o maaki: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, enee, Joomi mo'on Fodaali on Fodoore Mo∆¥∆¥ere, kaa ko aadi ndin juutani on? Kaa on faandi nde jippotoo e mo'on Tikkere immorde ka Joomi moo…óon si lunndi …óon fodoore am nden"
  20,87,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men lunndaaki fodoore maa…óa nden e sago amen, kono menen men ronndinaama teddeendi e cu…óaaje yim…ìe …ìen men werlii …óe, ko nii Saamiriiyu kadi welirii"
  20,88,"O yaltinani …ìe …ìanndu ngaari marn hito= huunaango, …ìe wi'i: \"Ko ko'ol woni rewetee…óo mon e rewetee…óo Muusaa on, o yejjitu [mo …óoo]"
  20,89,"Enee, …ìee yi'aali wonndema ruttataako e ma…ì…ìe konngol, ndi maranaa …ìe kadi lorra wonaa fii non [poo…óugol] nafa"
  20,90,"Gom…óii Haaruuna maakaniino …ìe ko adii: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, pellet, on jarribora kol, pellet, Joomi moo…óon ko Hinnorante On jokkee lam …óofto…óon yamiroore am nden"
  20,91,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men seerataa ko men √±ii…ìu…ìe e [dewal] makkol haa Muusaa ruttoo e amen"
  20,92,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ko an yo Haaruuna, nde yi'uno…óaa …ìe majjii ko ha…óumaa"
  20,93,nde jokkitataa mi? Kaa a yeddii yamaruyee am on
  20,94,"[Haaruuna] maaki: \"Ko an yo neene-gooto am, wata a nanngu waare am nden wanaa hoore am nden kadi, min dey, mi hulu wata a wi'u: Mi senndii hakkunde …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen, mi he…óaaki konngol maa…óa ngol"
  20,95,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Ko hon…óum woni fiyaake maa…óa on an Saamiriiyu"
  20,96,"[Saamiriiyu] wi'i: \"Mi yi'ii ko …ìe yi'aali …óum, mi nokki nokkannde e batte nulaa…óo on [Jibriila] mi werlii …óum ko nii cu…óirani lam wonkii am"
  20,97,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Yahu, pellet, no woodanmaa ka ngurndam nde wowlataa wanaa meemondiral, pellet, no woodanmaa kadi Fodoore a lunndataako nde, ndaarii faade e rewtee…óo maa, on mo √±allu…óaa ufinaade e hoore mun, mi woondii mi sunnay mo refti mi jaroo mo ka maayo e jaragol"
  20,98,"Pellet, Rewetee…óo mon On ko Alla, On Mo Rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Kanko, Ganndal Makko Yaajanii kala huunde"
  20,99,"Ko wano nii Men filloranay maa immorde e kumpital ko fe∆¥∆¥unoo kon, gom…óii Men addanii ma immorde ka Amen ja≈ãta"
  20,100,"Mo …óuurike e mayre pellet, o ronndoto √ëalnde Darngal teddeele [bakkaatu]"
  20,101,"Ko o luttintee…óo e nder majje, bonanii …ìe donngal √ëalnde Darngal"
  20,102,"√ëalnde wuttoytee ka alaadu Men moo…ìa bon…ìe …ìen nden √ëalnde ko mbulii…ìe [gite]"
  20,103,"Hi…ìe sowndondira hakkunde ma…ì…ìe […ìe wi'a] on √±ii…ìaali si wanaa [bal…óe] sappo"
  20,104,"Ko Menen woni Anndu…ìe ko …ìe wowlata kon, tuma nde koohoo…ìe ma…ì…ìe e laawol wi'ata: \"On √±ii…ìaali si wanaa √±allal"
  20,105,"Hi…ìe lanndaade ma fii pelle …óen, maaku: \"Joomi am jaroto …óe e jaragol"
  20,106,"O acca [leydi] ndin ko ndi boowal …ìowrungal"
  20,107,A yi'ataa e mayri oo√±annde wanaa tintiire
  20,108,"Ko nden √ëalnde …ìe jokkata noddoowo on ko aldaa e selugol mo,, hitooji …óin yankinanoo Hinnorante On hara a nanataa si wanaa nyuumbaango"
  20,109,"Nden √ëalnde tefoore nden nafataa, si wanaa on mo Hinnorante On sakkiti …óum O weltori konngol makko"
  20,110,Himo Anndi ko woni kon hedde yeeso ma…ì…ìe e hedde …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe …ìe hu…ìindortaa …óum ganndal
  20,111,"Geece …óen yankinanii Wuuru…óo Dartii…óo On, gom…óii sooyii on ronndii…óo too√±e"
  20,112,On mo golli immorde e mo∆¥∆¥i …óin hara ko o gom…óin…óo haray o hulaa too√±e wanaa uytaneede kadi
  20,113,Ko nii Men Telliniri nde Alqur'aanaare Aarabuure Men fensiti kadi e nder mayre immorde e kammbaaji …óin bela-jo'o kam…ìe …ìe hulay maa nde fu…ó…óanoo …ìe waaju
  20,114,"Alla Lam…óo Goongu…óo On Toowii, wata a he√±or Alqur'aanaare nden ko adii nde timmintee e maa…óa wahayu mayre, maaku: \"Joomi …ìeydanam Ganndal"
  20,115,Gom…óii Men ahodiino e Aadama ko adii o yejjiti Men he…ìanaali mo pellital
  20,116,"Tuma Nde Men Daalannoo malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen sujjanee Aadama, …ìe sujji si wanaa Ibliisa o salii"
  20,117,"Men Daali: \"Ko an yo Aadama, pellet, oo…óoo ko o ga√±o maa an e sonnaajo maa on, wata o yaltin on dey ka Aljanna sakko tampaa"
  20,118,"Pellet, no woodanmaa nde a weeletaake nder ton a holataa kadi"
  20,119,"Pellet, an a …óom…óetaake nde ton e nguletaake kadi"
  20,120,"Seytaane sonwonsini faade e makko; o wi'i: \"Ko an yo Aadama,hara yo mi tinndine e leggal luttineede ngal e laamu ngu follotaako ngun"
  20,121,"∆Åe √±aami e maggal, fee√±ani …ìe mettefooji ma…ì…ìe …óin, …ìe naati e suddirgol e dow ma…ì…ìe immorde e kaaki Aljanna on, Aadama yeddi Joomi makko o majji"
  20,122,"Refti Joomi makko Su…ìii mo, O Tuubini mo O Fewni [mo]"
  20,123,"O Daali: \"Jippee ton, on fow mo'on, yoga e mo'on ko ay…ìe yoga. Si tawii tun aroyii e mo'on immorde e Am Fewnoowo kala jokku…óo Peewal Am ngal haray o majjataa o malkisataake kadi"
  20,124,"Kala …óurnii…óo gaayi ja≈ãtagol lam, haray pellet, no woodani mo ngurndam …ìillu…óam Men moo…ìoya mo √ëalnde Darngal ko o bun…óo"
  20,125,"O wi'a: \"Joomi, ko fii hon…óum moo…ìan…óaa lam ko mi bun…óo, gom…óii mi laatinoke yi'oowo"
  20,126,"O Daala: \"Ko wano nii arunoo e maa…óa Aayeeje Amen …óen yejjitu…óaa …óe, ko wano nii kadi hannde yejjitirte…óaa"
  20,127,"Ko wano nii Men yo…ìirta on fantin…óo hara o gom…óinaa Aayeeje Joomi makko …óen, pellet, ko Lepte Laakara …óen …ìuri sa…ótude ko …óen kadi heddotoo"
  20,128,"Kaa hara …ìannganaali …ìe no foti hewde ko Men halki ado ma…ì…ìe immorde e gire? Hi…ìe yaha e ko…óooli ma…ì…ìe, pellet, no e …óum Aayeeje wonannde joomiraa…ìe hakkillaaji …ìen"
  20,129,"Sinno wonaano Daalol aditii ngol immorde ka Joomi maa…óa [Lepte] …óen laatotono duumii…óe e lajal innaangal"
  20,130,"Mun√±o e dow ko …ìe wowlata kon, subuhinor yettugol Joomi maa…óa ko adii ∆¥ellitagol naange ngen e ko adii mutugol magge e ka saa'iiji jemma subuhino e ka seraaji √±allal belajo'o a weltoto"
  20,131,"Wata a yawtin dey gite maa …óen faade kon ko Men dekmini …óum nooneeji immorde e ma…ì…ìe, cu…óaari ngurndam aduna fii yo Men jarribor …ìe e …óum, Arsike Joomi maa…óa on …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude ko on kadi heddotoo"
  20,132,"Yamir …ìeynguure maa…óa nden Julde nden mon√±itoraa e …óum, Men lanndaaki ma arsike ko Menen arsikaymaa. Battane [mo∆¥∆¥e] …óen kadi wonanii huloo…ìe Alla …ìen"
  20,133,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko hanno ara e amen Aaya immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Enee, hara araali e ma…ì…ìe …ìanngal ko woni kon e …óeri arani …óin"
  20,134,"Sinndo Menen Men halkirno …ìe Lepte ko adii …óum, …ìe wi'ayno: \"Joomi amen, ko hannoo Nualaa e amen Nulaa…óo men jokka Aayeeje Maa …óen, ko adii nde Men hoyata men hesra"
  20,135,"Maaku: \"Gooto kala [e amen] no habbitii, [onon kadi] habbitee aray anndon ko hommbo woni jom Laawol Focciingol ngol ko hommbo kadi feewi"
  21,1,"∆Åadanike yim…ìe …ìen hasboore ma…ì…ìe nden, te kam…ìe hi…ìe e nder welsindaare ko …ìe …óurnii…ìe"
  21,2,Arataa e ma…ì…ìe waaju immorde ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe ko fu…ó…óaa si wanaa …ìe jentike nde hara kam…ìe hi…ìe fija
  21,3,"∆Åer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen ko welsandii…óe …ìen too√±u…ìe suu…óa cowndi(gunndo) [wi'a] enee, hara oo wonu si wanaa …ìanndinke yeru mo'on, kaa on aray e mbilewu hara onon hi…óon sutii (ndaara)"
  21,4,"O maaki: \"Joomi am no Anndi Konngol ngol ka kammu e ka Leydi Kanko ko O Nanoowo Anndu…óo On"
  21,5,"Ko woni, …ìe wi'u: \"Ko nde jii…ìu-jaa…ìu koy…ói, toode, o fefindi nde, ko woni, kanko ko o yimoowo, awa yo o addan en Aayewal wano aran…ìe …ìen Nuliranoo non"
  21,6,"Gom…óinaali ado ma…ì…ìe immorde e saare Men halki nde. Enee, hara ko kam…ìe goom…óita"
  21,7,"Men Nulaali ado maa…óa si wanaa wor…ìe Men Wahayina e ma…ì…ìe, lanndee yim…ìe defte …ìen si tawii wonii on anndaa. @Corrected"
  21,8,"Men wa…óaali …ìe …ìalli …ìe √±aamataa √±aametee, …ìe laataaki kadi luttintee…ìe"
  21,9,"Refti Men Goonginani …ìe Fodoore nden Men danndi …ìe wonndude e …ìen …ìe Men Muuyi, Men halki fantin…ìe …ìen"
  21,10,Gom…óii Men jippinii faade e moo…óon Deftere no e nder mayre ja≈ãtawol moo…óon. Kaa on hakkiltaa
  21,11,Heewii ko Men halki immorde e saare laatinoonde ko too√±unde Men fu…ó…ói …ìaawo mayre yim…ìe goo
  21,12,"Tuma nde …ìe so'unoo Lepte Amen …óen, tawi kam…ìe hi…ìe doga …óe"
  21,13,"Wata on dogu, ruttee faade e ko neemina…óon kon e mu'un e ko…óan…óe mo'on, belajo'o on lannditoyte"
  21,14,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Eeyoo, bone amen, pellet, menen men laatinoke too√±u…ìe\". @Corrected"
  21,15,"Seerataa ndun noddaandu ma…ì…ìe, haa Men wa…óa …ìe co√±ateeri ko …ìe may…ìe"
  21,16,Men tagaali kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji ko Men fijoo…ìe
  21,17,"Sinndo Men faandino nde Men jogotoo fijindaaru, Men jogitotono …óum immorde ka Amen si tawii Men laatike wa…óoo…ìe"
  21,18,"Ko woni, Me…óen werloo Goonga kan e dow meere nden ka munca nde, tawa kayre ko nde fuuyoore, no woodani on bone kon ko sifoto…óon"
  21,19,"Ko Kanko woodani ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi …ìen wonu…ìe ka Makko kadi …ìe mawnittaako gaayi rewugol Mo, …ìe hasrintaaka kadi"
  21,20,Hi…ìe Subhinoo jemma e √±alorma …ìe aamataa
  21,21,"Kaa …ìe jogiti rewetee…ói ka leydi hara kannji hi…ói immintina [may…ìe …ìen]"
  21,22,"Sinndo laatino e majji [kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin] rewtee…ói ko wonaa Alla …ói bonayno. Senayee wonanii Alla Jom Arsi kin gaayi ko…ìe sifotoo. @Corrected"
  21,23,"O lanndetaake ko O gollata kon, kam…ìe ko …ìe lannditoytee…ìe"
  21,24,"Kaa …ìe jogiti gaanin Makko rewetee…ói? Maaki: \"Addee daliili mon on, ko ndee woni ja≈ãta …ìen wonndu…ìe e am e ja≈ãta …ìen adii…ìe lam\". Ko woni, …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe …ìe anndaa Goonga kan kam…ìe ko …ìe …óurnii…ìe"
  21,25,"Men Nulaali ado maa…óa immorde e Nulaa…óo si wanaa Men wahayinii e makko; pellet, rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Min Rewee Lam"
  21,26,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Hinnorante On jogitike …ìi…ó…óo\". Senayee woodanii Mo, ko woni, […ìen ko …ìe] jeyaa…ìe teddinaa…ìe"
  21,27,"∆Åe adortaa Mo konngol ngol, kam…ìe ko Yamiroore Makko nden …ìe gollata"
  21,28,"Himo Anndi ko woni kon hedde yeeso ma…ì…ìe e ko woni kon hedde …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe, …ìe tefanoytaa si wanaa on mo O Weltanii, kam…ìe immorde e kulol Makko ko …ìe jootu…ìe"
  21,29,"Kala e ma…ì…ìe kadi wi'u…óo: \"Min ko mi rewetee…óo gaanin Makko\". On …óon Men Yo…ìay mo Jahanna- ma ko wano nii Men Yo…ìirta too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  21,30,"Enee, hara …ìen yeddu…ìe yi'aali wonndema kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin …ói laatinoke hippondir…ói, Men Udditi …ói Men wa…ói immorde e ndiyam …óam kala huunde wuuru nde. Kaa …ìe gom…óintaa"
  21,31,"Men wa…ói ka leydi pelle fii wata nde oo√±odo e ma…ì…ìe, Men wa…ói e mayri …óate yaaju…óe, belajo'o kam…ìe …ìe feeway"
  21,32,"Men wa…ói kammu ngun kippudi reenaandi, kam…ìe ko …ìe …óurnii…ìe gaayi Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  21,33,Ko Kanko woni On Tagu…óo jemma on e √±alorma on e naange ngen e lewru ndun kala majji hi…ói fubboo(lummboo) ka fuluku
  21,34,"Men wa…óanaali …ìanndunke ado maa…óa luttineede, enee, hara si a maayii ko kam…ìe woni luttintee…ìe …ìen"
  21,35,"Kala wonkii meedat may…óe nden, Men jarribora on bone on e mo∆¥∆¥ere nden jarrabagol, ko ka Amen kadi ruttoto…óon"
  21,36,"Si …ìen yeddu…ìe yi'ii ma, …ìe jogitortaa ma si wanaa jalkitde […ìe wi‚Äôa:] \"Enee, hara ko oo woni on ja≈ãtotoo…óo rewetee…ói mo'on …óin?\" hara kam…ìe ko …ìe yeddu…ìe jantagol Hinnorante On"
  21,37,"Ne…ó…óake on Tagaama immorde e hawjere, aray Mi holla on Aayeeje Am …óen wata on hawju"
  21,38,"Hi…ìe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si tawii ko on goongu…ìe"
  21,39,"Sinndo …ìen yeddu…ìe anndiino tuma tawi …ìe ittataa Yiite ngen ka geece ma…ì…ìe wanaa kadi ka …ìabbe ma…ì…ìe kadi, kam…ìe …ìe wonaali walloytee…ìe"
  21,40,"Ko woni, nge aray e ma…ì…ìe e juhayee nge muga …ìe, hara …ìe hattantaake ruttugol nge, …ìe wonaali kadi nennanoytee…ìe"
  21,41,"Gom…óii Nulaa…ìe goo jalkitanooma ado maa…óa, jippii e …ìen jalkitu…ìe ko …ìe laatinoo hi…ìe jalkita"
  21,42,"Maaku: \"Ko hommbo reenata on jemma e √±alorma immorde e Hinnorante On, ko woni, kam…ìe gaayi ja≈ãta Joomi ma…ì…ìe ko …ìe …óurnii…ìe"
  21,43,"Kaa no woodani …ìe reewetee…ìe …ìe no dannda …ìe gaanin Amen? ∆Åe hattantaake wallude hay wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe, wanaa kam…ìe woni wondatee…ìe immorde e Amen"
  21,44,"Ko woni, Men dakmitii …ìee e baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen haa ngurndam …óam juutani …ìe. Enee, hara …ìee yi'aali wonnde Menen Me…óen ara e leydi ndin Men ustira ndi immorde e seraaji mayri? Kaa ko kam…ìe woni fooloo…ìe …ìen"
  21,45,"Maaku: \"Anndu ko mi woni jertinirde on ko Wahyu on, [kono] paho on nanataa noddaandu ndun, si …ìe jertinaama"
  21,46,"Mi woondii si meemii …ìe see…óa immorde e Lepte Joomi maa …óen, maa …ìe wi'a: \"Ee-yoo, bone amen pellet, menen men laatinoke too√±u…ìe"
  21,47,"Men wa…óa manndikir…óe(peesir…óe) Nun…óal ngal fii √ëalnde Darngal hara wonkii woo to√±iroytaake hay e huunde, hay si laatii ko yeru gabbun pamarun Men adday kun Men yonii Hasboo…ìe"
  21,48,Gom…óii Men Okkii Muusaa e Haaruuna Serndoore nden e ndayngu e ja≈ãta wonannde huloo…ìe …ìen
  21,49,∆Åen hulay…ìe Joomi ma…ì…ìe ka wirnii hara kam…ìe immorde e Darngal ngal ko …ìe huli
  21,50,"Ndee [Alqur‚Äôaanaare] ko nde Ja≈ãta, ko nde barkinaande Men Jippiniinde. Kaa onon ko on yedday…ìe nde"
  21,51,"Gom…óii Men Okkii Ibraahiima Peewal makko ngal ko adii, Men laatike kadi Anndu…ìe mo"
  21,52,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko e yim…ìe makko …ìen: \"Ko hon…óum woni …óii nanndonlaaji nate mahii…óe, …óin …ói ufini…óon e [dewal] mu'un"
  21,53,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men taw baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen no rewde …ói"
  21,54,"O maaki: \"Gom…óii on laatike onon e baabiraa…ìe mon …ìen e nder majjere …ìanngunde won…óon"
  21,55,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Enee, ko Goonga kan addan…óaa men, kaa an ko e fijoo…ìe …ìen jeya…óaa"
  21,56,"Maaku: \"Ko woni, Joomi mo'on ko Jooma kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin On Tagu…óo…ói, min komi jeyaa…óo e seedii…ìe …ìen e dow …óum"
  21,57,"Mi woondirii Alla, maa mi fewja fii …óii sanamuuji mo'on …ìaawo huccitugol mo'on ko on ru≈ãii …ìe"
  21,58,"O wa…ói …ói kunte, si wanaa mawndu majji ndun, belajo'o kam…ìe …ìe ruttoto e mayru"
  21,59,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko hommbo wa…ói …óu'un e rewetee…ói amen …óin? Pellet, on ko o jeyaa…óo e too√±u…ìe …ìen"
