  21,103,"Suninoytaa…ìe …óen∆¥ere mawnde nden, Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen no ja…ì…ìoo…ìe […ìe wi'a:] \"Ko ndee woni √ëalaande mo'on, nden nde laatino…óon hi…óon fodee"
  21,104,"√ëalnde Men taggoyta kammu ngun wano taggugol …óerol defte. Ko wano Men fu…ó…óori non ka arannde tagu Men ruttirta ngu, […óum] ko Fodoore e dow Amen, pellet, Menen Men laatike golloo…ìe"
