  22,5,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, si tawii on laatike e sikke immorde e immital ngal, pellet, Menen Men Tagii on immorde e mbullaari refti e to…ì…ìere maniiyu, refti e he…ó…óere refti e huyre timmunde tagu e nde wonaa timmunde tagu fii yo Men …ìannginan on, Me…óen √ëii…ìina ka renngaaji ko Men Muuyi kon haa e happu innaa…óo, refti Men yaltini on ko on booboo…ìe, refti fii yo on yotto sagatalaaku mo'on no e mo'on …ìen …ìe no maaya no e mo'on kadi …ìen …ìe no ruttee faade ka …ìuri jaasude e ngurndan …óam fii wata …ìe anndu …ìaawo ganndal hay e huunde. A yi'ay leydi ndin ko yoorunde si Men jippinii e dow mayri ndiyam …óan ndi dilla ndi ∆¥ura ndi fu…óina immorde e kala noone woo…óu…óo"
  22,6,"∆äum, ko tawde pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga kan, pellet, O wurnitay may…ìe …ìen, tawde pellet, ko O Hattan…óo e dow kala huunde. @Corrected"
  22,7,"Pellet, Darngal ngal ko aray ngal sikke alaa e maggal, wonnde pellet, Alla immintinay …ìen won…ìe ka genaale"
  22,8,No e yim…ìe …ìen on mo no wennja e fii Alla ko aldaa e ganndal wanaa peewal wanaa deftere nur…óunde(jalbunde)
  22,9,"Hofu…óo balaaji mu'un [mawnintinii…óo] fii yo o majjin gaayi Laawol Alla ngol, no woodani mo ka aduna oyeere Men mee…óinoyay mo kadi √ëalnde Darngal Lepte sumoowe ngen"
  22,10,"∆äum ko sabu ko juu…óe maa…óa …óen ardini kon. E wonnde pellet, Alla wonaali Too√±oowo jeyaa…ìe …ìen"
  22,11,"No e yim…ìe …ìen on mo no rewa Alla e dow selindaare; si mo∆¥∆¥ere he…ìii mo o tabitira sabu …óum si jarrabuyee kadi he…ìii mo o waylitoo e yeeso makko, o hayrii aduna on e Laakara on ko …óum tigi woni hayrere …ìanngunde nden"
  22,12,"Himo rewa gaanin Alla kon ko lorrataa mo e kon ko nafataa mo kadi. ∆äum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo], ko …óum woni majjere wo…ó…óunde nden"
  22,13,"Himo rewa on mo lorra muu…óum no …ìuri …ìadaade diini nafa muu…óum kan, bonii welddi…óo bonii kadi wuuridaa…óo"
  22,14,"Pellet, Alla hiMo naada …ìen gom…óin…ìe …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin Aljannaaji no ila sengo ley majji can…ói …óin, pellet, Alla hiMo wa…óa ko O faandii kon. @Corrected"
  22,15,On won…óo no sikka wonnde Alla wallataa mo ka aduna e ka Laakara; haray yo o fontu …ìoggol faade ka kammu refti o ta∆¥a ngol yo o ndaaru taw si pewje makko …óen ittay ko tikkini kon
  22,16,"Ko wano nii Men Jippiniri nde Aayeeje …ìanngu…óe. Pellet, Alla hiMo Fewna on Mo O faandii"
