  22,22,"Tuma kala …ìe faandii yaltugol nder ton immorde e suno, …ìe ruttee e nder magge, […ìe wi‚Äôanee:] mee…óee Lette sumoowe ngen"
  22,23,"Pellet, Alla naada …ìen gom…óin…ìe …ìe golle mo∆¥∆¥i …óin Aljannaaji no ila e ley majji can…ói …óin, …ìe cu…óiree nder ton immorde jawe kan≈ãe e lu'ulu'uuje koltu ma…ì…ìe on nder ton ko hariire. @Corrected"
  22,24,"∆Åe fewnaama faade e ko laa…ìi immorde e konngol ngol, …ìe fewnaa kadi faade e Laawol Yettiniingol ngol"
  22,25,"Pellet, …ìen yeddu…ìe hi…ìe faddaade gaayi Laawol Alla ngol e Juulirde Horminnde nden, nden nde Men wa…óani …óum yim…ìe …ìen, no fota ter √±ii…ìu…óo on e mayre e liigotoo…óo on. Kala faalaa…óo oo√±orde e mayre too√±e, Men mee…óinay mo immorde e Lepte muusu…óe"
  22,26,"E tuma nde Men Jippinnoo Ibraahiima nokku Suudu ndun, [Men Daali:] Wata a kafidu e Am hay e huunde, la…ì…ìin Suudu Am ndun fii wanngotoo…ìe …ìen e darotoo…ìe …ìen [juula] e ru∆¥∆¥oo…ìe sujja …ìen"
  22,27,"Noddin e yim…ìe …ìen fii Hajju ngun, …ìe aray e maa…óa ko …ìe seppoo…ìe e dow kala …óehiimba reedu, …ìe aray immorde e kala laawol wo…ó…óungol"
  22,28,"Fii yo …ìe seedo nafoore ma…ì…ìe, …ìe ja≈ãtoo Innde Alla e nder √±al…ói anndaa…ói e dow ko O arsiki …ìe kon immorde e muumi neemoraa…ói, √±aamee e majji, √±amminon kadi baaso …ìillii…óo on"
