  23,109,"Pellet, laatinoke fedde e jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen hi…ìe wi'a: \"Joomi amen, men gom…óinii haforan men Yurme∆äaa men ko An …ìuri Mo∆¥∆¥ude Yurmetee…ìe …ìen"
  23,110,"Jogiti…óon …ìe jalnori(jalkigol), haa …ìe yejjintini on ja≈ãta Am, laati…óon hi…óon jala …ìe"
  23,111,"Min Mi yo…ìii …ìe hannde sabu ko …ìe mu√±√±inoo kon, pellet, kam…ìe ko kam…ìe woni malaa…ìe …ìen"
  23,112,"O Daali: \"No foti heewde ko √±ii…ìu…óon ka leydi, limoore duu…ìi"
  23,113,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men √±ii…ìii √±allal maa…óum yoga e √±allal, lanndo limoo…ìe …ìen"
  23,114,"O Daali: \"On √±ii…ìaali si wonaa see…óa, sinndo onon on laatino hi…óon anndi"
  23,115,"Enee, on sikku wonndema ko Men Tagiri on ko puyndan, hara onon on ruttetaake faade ka Amen"
  23,116,"Alla Toowii Laam…óo Goongu…óo On, Rewetee- …óo alah si wanaa Kanko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin. @Corrected"
  23,117,"Kala noddu…óo wonndude e Alla rewetee…óo goo, daliil alanah mo e …óum, anndu pellet, hasboo- re makko ko ka Joomi makko, pellet Kanko, O malnatah heefer…ìe …ìen"
  23,118,"Maaku: \"Jooma am, Yaafo Yurmo ko An ∆Åuri Mo∆¥∆¥ude Yurmetee…ìe …ìen"
  24,1,"Simoore, Men jippinii nde Men farlii nde, Men jippini e nder mayre Aayeeje …ìanngu…óe belajo'o onon on waajitoto"
  24,2,"Debbo jinoowo on e gorko jeenoowo on foccee gooto kala e ma…ì…ìe paatawol(looci) teemedere, wata yurmeende ma…ì…ìe nanngu on e fii Diina Alla kan, si tawii on laatike hi…óon gom…óini Alla e √ëalaande Laakara nden. Yo seedo foccugol …ìe ngol jamaa immorde e gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  24,3,"Gorko jinoowo on o resataa si wonaa debbo jeenoowo maa…óum sirkoowo, debbo jinoowo on resatah mo si wanaa gorko jinoowo maa…óum sirkoowo, …óum harminaama e dow gom…óin…ìe …ìen"
  24,4,"E …ìen …ìe no tukka rew…ìe sa≈ãii…ìe …ìen refti hara …ìe addaali seedee…ìe nayo, haray piyee …ìe paatawol(looci) cappan…óe jeetati. Wata on ja…ìan …ìe seedagol poomaa. ∆Åen …óon, ko kam…ìe woni Faasiqii…ìe …ìen"
  24,5,"Si wanaa …ìen tuubu…ìe …ìaawo …óum …ìe mo∆¥∆¥ini. Pellet, Alla ko O Surroowo Yurmetee…óo"
  24,6,"E …ìen …ìe no tukka sonnaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen hara laatanaaki …ìe seedee…ìe si wanaa wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe …óin, ko yo go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe seedo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla pellet, kanko ko e goongu…ìe …ìen o jeyaa"
  24,7,"Jowa…ìun …óum, wonndema yo kuddi Alla wonu e dow makko si o laatike jeyaa…óo e fenoo…ìe …ìen"
  24,8,"∆Åe dunyira e [sonnaajo on] lepte …óen, nde o seedotoo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla, pellet [gorko on] ko e fenoo…ìe …ìen o jeyaa"
  24,9,"Jowa…ìun …óum, ko nde Alla tikkata e dow makko si [gorko on] laatike ko e goongu…ìe …ìen o jeyaa"
  24,10,"Sinndo wanaano ∆Åural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden, e wonndema Alla ko O ja…ìoowo tuubuubuye √ëee√±u…óo"
  24,11,"Pellet, …ìen addu…ìe penaale …óen ko …ìe jamaa jeyaa…óo e moo…óon, wata on sikku …óum ko bone mo'on; ko woni …óum ko mo∆¥∆¥ere mo'on. No woodani kala ne…ó…óo immorde e ma…ì…ìe ko o faggitii kon e junuubu, on fawtii…óo maw…óum [junuubu on] immorde e ma…ì…ìe, no woodani mo Lepte maw…óe"
  24,12,"Ko haanunoo tuma nde nanu…óon …óum, wor…ìe gom…óin…ìe …ìen e rew…ìe gom…óin…ìe …ìen …ìe yananee ka wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe ko mo∆¥∆¥i, …ìe wi'a: \"∆äum ko penaale …ìanngu…óe nii"
  24,13,"Ko haanunoo ko nde …ìe addata e …óum seedee…ìe nayo, si …ìe addaali seedee…ìe …ìen; haray …ìen …óon, ka Alla ko kam…ìe woni fenoo…ìe …ìen"
  24,14,Sinndo wonaano ∆Åural Alla ngal e Yurmeende Makko nden e dow moo…óon ka aduna e ka laakara Lepte maw…óe meemayno on fii kon ko ukki…óon e muu…óum
  24,15,"Tuma nde werlorayno…óon …óum …óenn…óe moo…óon, wowliron kunndu…óe moo…óon kon ko ganndal alanah on e muu…óum sikkon …óum kadi ko newii…óum, hara non …óum ko mawnu…óom ka Alla"
  24,16,"Ko haanunoo tuma nanu…óon nde, wi'on: \"Haanaa men nde men wowlata e dum, Senayee woodanii Ma, …óum ko fenaande mawnde nii"
  24,17,"Alla no waajaade on fii wata on fillo sugu [ndee fenaande] poomaa, si tawii on laatike gom…óin…ìe"
  24,18,Alla no …ìannginannde on Aayeeje …óen Alla ko O Anndu…óo √ëee√±u…óo
  24,19,"Pellet, …ìen yi…óu…ìe yo bone …óen saako e [hoore] …ìen gom…óin…ìe; no woodani …ìe Lepte muusu…óe ka aduna e ka Laakara. Alla no Anndi, onon on anndah"
  24,20,"Sinndo wanaano ∆Åural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden e tawde pellet, Alla ko O Newii…óo Hinndotooao"
  24,21,"Ko onon …ìen gom…óin…ìe, wata on jokku …óate Seytaane …óen, kala jokku…óo …óate Seytaane …óen, pellet, o yamiray [mo] ko boni kon e ko a√±aa kon. Sinndo wonaano ∆Åural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden; hay e gooto e moo…óon laa…ìataano poomaa, kono Alla hiMo la…ì…ìina on mo O Muuyi. Alla ko O Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  24,22,"Wata joomiraa…ìe …ìural ngal e yaajeende nden e moo…óon woondu wonndema …ìe okkortaa …ìadondiraa…ìe …ìen e …ìillii…ìe …ìen e feru…ìe …ìen ka Laawol Alla, yo …ìe yaafo. Kaa on yi…óaa yo Alla yawtan on? Alla ko O Yawtoowo Yurmetee…óo"
  24,23,"Pellet, …ìen wonu…ìe tukkude [sonnaa…ìe] sa≈ãii…ìe welsindii…ìe gom…óin…ìe, …ìe hu…óaama ka aduna e ka Laakara no woodani …ìe Lepte maw…óe"
  24,24,"√ëalnde seedoytoo e dow ma…ì…ìe …óen…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen e juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen e koy…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, ko …ìe laatinoo kon hi…ìe golla"
  24,25,"Nden √ëalnde Alla huu…ìinanay …ìe [njo…ìdi] Diina ma…ì…ìe Goongaha kan, …ìe annda pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni Goonga ∆Åannguka kan"
  24,26,"Rew…ìe so…ìu…ìe …ìen ko fii wor…ìe so…ìu…ìe …ìen. Wor…ìe so…ìu…ìe …ìen ko fii rew…ìe so…ìu…ìe …ìen. Rew…ìe laa…ìu…ìe …ìen ko fii wor…ìe laa…ìu…ìe …ìen, wor…ìe laa…ìu…ìe …ìen ko fii rew…ìe laa…ìu…ìe …ìen. ∆Åee …óoo ko hisnaa…ìe e kon ko …ìe wowlata, no woodani …ìe haforaneede e arsike teddu…óo"
  24,27,"Ko onon yo gom…óin…ìe, wata on naatu e cuu…ói tanaa cuu…ói mo'on …óin haa du≈ãino…óon salminon e dow yim…ìe majji …ìen, ko …óum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde on. Bela jo'o onon on waajitoto"
  24,28,"Si on tawaali nder ton go…ó…óo, wata on naatu ton haa du≈ãane…óon, si on wi'aama: \"Yiltee\" haray yiltee, ko …óum …ìuri laa…ìannde on. Alla non hiMo Anndi ko golloton kon"
  24,29,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde naatoton e cuu…ói …ói ho…óiraaka hara no e nder majji miranhoy mo'on, Alla non hiMo Anndi ko won…óon e fe√±√±inde e ko won…óon e suu…óude"
  24,30,"Maakan wor…ìe gom…óin…ìe …ìen yo …ìe heltu ndar…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen …ìe reena farjuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin, ko …óum …ìurata la…ì…ìinnde …ìe. Pellet, Alla ko O Humpitii…óo ko …ìe huuwata"
  24,31,"Maakan rew…ìe gom…óin…ìe …ìen yo …ìe heltu ndar…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe reena farjuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin, wata …ìe fe√±√±in cu…óaari ma…ì…ìe ndin si wanaa ko fee√±i kon e mayri. Yo …ìe fawu tiggaaje ma…ì…ìe …óen ka becce ma…ì…ìe, wata …ìe fe√±√±inan cu…óaari ma…ì…ìe ndin si wanaa genndiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen maa…óum baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe maa…óum baabiraa…ìe genndiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe maa…óum …ìi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe, maa…óum …ìi…ó…ìe genndiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe maa…óum musi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe, maa…óum …ìi…ó…ìe musi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe, maa…óum …ìi…ó…ìe banndiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe, maa…óum sonnaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe, maa…óum …ìen …ìe …ìe jeyiri √±aame ma…ì…ìe maa…óum …ìen wor…ìe jokkoo…ìe …ìe haaju mun alaa e rew…ìe, maa…óum boobo mo ∆¥ellitaaki e awraaji sonnaa…ìe …ìen. Wata …ìe tappindir koy…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen fii yo Annde ko …ìe suu…ói kon immorde e cu…óaari ma…ì…ìe. Tuubee rutto…óon ka Alla on fow mo'on, ko onon yo gom…óin…ìe bela jo'o on malete"
  24,32,"Resinee …ìe resaali …ìen e moo…óon e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen immorde e muccu…ìe moo…óon e hor…ìe moo…óon, si …ìe laatike waasu…ìe Alla al…óinay …ìe immorde e ∆Åural Makko ngal, Alla ko O Yaaju…óo Anndu…óo"
  24,33,"∆Åe he…ìaali feere resugol …ìen yo …ìe habbo haa Alla al…óinira …ìe ∆Åural Makko ngal. ∆Åen wonu…ìe …óa…ì…ìude soottaade e …ìen …ìe √±aame moo…óon jeyi, soottaadede …ìe si on anndii e ma…ì…ìe mo∆¥∆¥ere, jonnee …ìe immorde e jawdi Alla ndin, ndin ndi O jonni on, wata on waawnu hor…ìe moo…óon …ìen e fii jeeno, si …ìe faandike sa≈ãaade, wata on …óa…ì…ìu jawkal ngurndam aduna, kala waawnuu…óo …ìe pellet, Alla …ìaawo baawnugol …ìe ko O Surroowo Yurmitee…óo"
  24,34,"Gom…óii Men jippinii e moo…óon Aayeeje …ìanngu…óe e misal immorde e …ìeya wulinoo…ìe ko adii on e waaju wonannde huloo…ìe [Alla] …ìen"
  24,35,"Ko Alla woni Ndaygu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, sifa Ndaygu Makko ngun ko wano tu…ó…óere hara no e mayre pitilol(lampu), pitilol ngol wona e nder biiniiri, biiniiri ndin hara hindi wa'i wa hoodere jalbunde hinde hu…ì…ìa immorde e leggal barkinaangal nebbantewal ngal wonaa funnaangeyankowal ngal wonaa hirnaangeyankowal nebban maggal …óan no …ìadoo jalbude, hay si yiite meemaali …óan, ndaygu e hoore ndaygu, Alla no fewnira ndaygu Makko ngun on mo O Muuyi, Alla no piyana yim…ìe …ìen mise, Alla ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde. @Corrected"
  24,36,E nder cuu…ói …ói Alla du≈ãii(sakkiti) yo darne Innde Makko jantee e nder majji Subunhinanee Mo nder majji ka bimmbi e ka kiikii…óe
  24,37,"Wor…ìe …ìe njulaaku e ngeyngu maapintaa …óum gaayi ja≈ãtagol Alla e √±imnugol Julde nden e tottu- gol Jakka on, hi…ìe huli √ëalaande nde waylitoytoo e muu…óum …ìer…óe …óen e gii…óe …óen"
  24,38,"Fii yo Alla yo…ìoy…ìe ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude ko …ìe gollunoo kon, O …ìeydana …ìe e ∆Åural Makko ngal. Alla no arsika on mo O Muuyi ko Aldaa hasboore"
  24,39,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe, golle ma…ì…ìe …óen no wa'i wa merere wonunde e boowal, …óon…óaa…óo on no sikka ko nde ndiyam, haa si o arii e mayre o tawataa hay e huunde, o tawa Alla ka Makko O huu…ìinana mo hasboore makko nden, Alla ko O Yaawu…óo Hasboore. @Corrected"
  24,40,"Maa…óum ko wano ni…ìe e maayo luggungo, no suddi ngo benpe∆¥∆¥e no dow maggo benpe∆¥∆¥e no dow majje duule, ni…ìe yoga e majje no e dow yoga, si o yaltinii junngo makko ngon o …ìadotaako yi'ugol ngo. On mo Alla wa…óanaali ndaygu hara o alaa ndaygu"
  24,41,"Enee, a yi'aali wonndema Alla no subuhinanaade Mo …ìen wonu…ìe ka kammuuli e ka leydi e colli …óin kadi ko saffinii…ói? Gooto kala e …óii gom…óii anndii julde mu'un nden e subuhinaali mu'un …óin, Alla ko O Anndu…óo ko …ìe Huuwata"
  24,42,"Ko Alla heeranii Laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, ko faade ka Alla woni wa…ótinirde nden"
  24,43,"Enee, a yi'aali wonndema Alla hiMo sogga duulere, refti O hawtindira nde, refti O wa…óa nde fawondirnde hi…óa yi'a to…ìo ngon no yalta e nder mayre, ngo jippoo immorde ka kammu, immorde e pelle no e nder mayre marmalle hiMo hewtina …óe on mo O Muuyi, hiMo pottina …óe on mo O Muuyi? Ndaneeri ma∆¥e mayre no do'a na…ìude gii…óe …óen"
  24,44,"Alla hiMo waylita jemma on e √±alorma on, pellet, na wonii e …óum tasakuyee wonannde joomiraa…ìe gii…óe …ìen"
  24,45,"Ko Alla tagii kala daabe hun immorde e ndiyam, no e majji yaarooji reedu muu…óum, no e majji yaarooji koy…óe muu…óm no e majji kadi yaarooji [koy…óe] nayi. Alla hiMo Taga ko O Muuyi, pellet, Alla ko O hattan…óo kala huunde"
  24,46,"Gom…óii Men jippinii Aayeeje …ìanngu…óe, Alla no fewna on mo O muuyii faade e Laawol foccii ngol"
  24,47,"Hi…ìe wi'a: \"Men gom…óinii Alla e Nulaa…óo on, men …óoftike, refti huccita fedde goo e ma…ì…ìe, …ìaawo …óum, …ìen wonaali gom…óin…ìe"
  24,48,"Si …ìe noddaama faade ka Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on fii yo o √±aawu hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, tawa fedde goo e ma…ì…ìe ko …ìe …óuurnii…ìe"
  24,49,"Si tawii ko kam…ìe mari goonga kan, …ìe aray ka makko ko …ìe …óoftii…ìe"
  24,50,"Enee, ko nawnaare woni ka …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe, kaa …ìe sikkiti, kaa …ìe hulu wata Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on too√±u …ìe? Ko woni, …ìee ko kam…ìe woni too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  24,51,"Anndu ko woni konngol gom…óin…ìe …ìen si …ìe noddaama faade ka Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on fii yo o √±aawu hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, ko nde …ìe wi'ata: \"Men nanii men …óoftike.\" ∆Åen …óon ko kam…ìe woni malaa…ìe …ìen"
  24,52,"Kala …óoftii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on o huli Alla o rentii [e Lepte Makko …óen] haray …ìen …óon ko kam…ìe woni malaa…ìe …ìen"
  24,53,"∆Åe woondiri Alla, e hattirde goondooje ma…ì…ìe, si a yamirii …ìe ma …ìe yaltu sanne. Maaku: \"wata on woondu, …óoftaare no anndaa, pellet, Alla ko humpitii…óo ko golloton"
  24,54,"Maaku: \"∆äoftee Alla …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on\". Si …ìe huccitii(runtiima) anndu ko fawii mo ko, ko o roondaa kon, no fawii on ko roonda …óon kon, si on …óoftike mo on feeway, fawaaki Nulaa…óo on si wanaa yottinngol …ìanngungol"
  24,55,"Alla Fodii …ìen gom…óin…ìe e moo…óon …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin O lontinay …ìe ka leydi wano O lontinirnoo non …ìen adii…ìe …ìe, ma O wee…ìinan …ìe diina ma…ì…ìe ka O welanaa …ìe, ma O wattitan …ìe …ìaawo kulol ma…ì…ìe ngol hoolaare, Yo …ìe rewam wata …ìe sirkanam hay e huunde. Kala yeddu…óo …ìaawo …óum haray …ìen …óon ko kam…ìe woni faasiqii…ìe …ìen"
  24,56,"√ëii…ìee e Julde totton Jakka on …óofto…óon kadi Nulaa…óo on, bela jo'o on Yurmete"
  24,57,"Wata a sikku …ìeen yeddu…ìe …ìe laawoto ka leydi, jaa∆¥orde ma…ì…ìe nden ko ka Yiite, pellet, bonii wattnde"
  24,58,"Ko onon yo gom…óin…ìe, yo sakkintino e moo…óon …ìen …ìe √±aame moo…óon jeyi, e …ìen …ìe yottaaki koy…óol immorde e moo…óon, laabi tati ko adii Julde Peeral nden, e tuma wallinton conci moo…óon ka njolloro e ka …ìaawo Julde gee∆¥e ko awraaji moo…óon tati non. Bakkaatu fawaaki on fawaaki …ìe …ìaawo majji, jinndoo…ìe hakkunde moo…óon, yoga e moo…óon e dow yoga. Ko wano nii Alla …ìanngini- rani on Aayeeje …óen Alla ko O Anndu…óo √ëee√±u…óo"
  24,59,"Si sukaa…ìe moo…óon yottike kellefuyee, yo …ìe sakkitinono wano du≈ãinornoo non …ìen adii…ìe …ìe, ko wano nii Alla …ìannginiranta on Aayeeje Makko …óen, Alla ko O Anndu…óo √ëee√±u…óo"
  24,60,"E sonnaa…ìe jottii…ìe …ìen, …ìen …ìe jortaaki desal bakkaatu fawaaki …ìe nde …ìe wallinta conci ma…ì…ìe …óin hara …ìe wonaa fe√±√±in…ìe cu…óaari, ko nde …ìe nantotoo …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde …ìe, Alla ko O Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  24,61,"Bakkaatu fawaaki bun…óu on, bakkaatu fawaaki la∆¥u…óo on, bakkaatu fawaaki nawnu…óo on, fawaaki e wonkiiji moo…óon nde √±aamoton ka cuu…ói moo…óon maa…óum ka cuu…ói baabiraa…ìe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói neeniraa…ìe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói musi…ó…ìe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói banndiraa…ìe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói bappiraa…ìe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói yaayiraa…ìe moo…óon, maa…óom ka cuu…ói kaawiraa…ìe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói neeniraa…ìe moo…óon ka dewol, maa…óum …óin …ói jogi…óon cottir…óe muu…óum, maa…óum gi…óo moo…óon. Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde hawtoton √±aamon maa…óum √±aamon ko on sertu…ìe. Si on naatay e cuu…ói salminee e dow wonkiiji moo…óon, hiwraango immorde ka Alla barkinaango laa…ìungo, ko wano nii Alla …ìannguniranta on Aayeeje …óen belajo'o onon on haqqilay"
  24,62,"Anndu gom…óin…ìe …ìen ko …ìen gom…óin…ìe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, si …ìe laatike hi…ìe wonndi e makko e dow fiyaake moftu…óo, …ìe yahatah haa …ìe du≈ãinoo e makko, pellet, …ìen …óa…ì…ìiray…ìe ma du≈ãayee ko …ìen …óon woni gom…óin…ìe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, si …ìe …óa…ì…ìirii ma du≈ãayee fii yoga e fiyaake ma…ì…ìe, du≈ãano on mo yi…óu…óaa [du≈ãanaade] e ma…ì…ìe, insinano…óaa …ìe ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko O Surroowo Yurmetee…óo"
  24,63,"Wata on wa…óu noddugol Nulaa…óo on hakkunde moo…óon wano noddugol yoga e moo…óon yoga. Gom…óii Alla no Anndi …ìen sortotoo…ìe e moo…óon e moltagol, …ìen wonu…ìe lunndaade yamaruyee makko on, yo …ìe rento fii wata fitina hi…ìu …ìe maa…óum Lempte muusu…óe he…ìa …ìe"
  24,64,"Ko non woniri, pellet, ko Alla heeranii ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi gom…óii hiMo Anndi ko wonu…óon e hoore mu'un kon, √ëalnde …ìe ruttetee faade ka Makko O yeetoo …ìe ko …ìe gollunoo kon. Alla ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  25,1,Mawnii On Jippin…óo Serndoore nden e dow jeyaa…óo Makko on fii yo wonan winndire nden jertinoowo
  25,2,"On Mo woodanii …óum Laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, o jogitaaki …ìi…ó…óo laatanaaki Mo kadi kafidaa…óo ka Laamu. O tagii kala huunde O e…ì…ìindiinde e e…ì…ìugol"
  25,3,"∆Åe jogitii gaanin Makko rewetee…ói …ói tagaani huunde kannji ko …ói tagaa…ói, …ói maranah ko'e majji lorra wanaa nafa …ói marah mayde wanaa ngurndan wanaa Immital"
  25,4,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe wi'i: \"Ndee [Alqur'aanaare] wonaali si wonah pene …ói o fefindii …óum, walli mo e hoore majje yim…ìe goo\". Gom…óii …ìe addii too√±e e bagamma"
  25,5,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko nde tinndi adinoo…ìe o winnditi …ói hi…ói fidanee mo bimmbi e kiikii…óe"
  25,6,"Maaku: \"Jippinii nde On Anndu…óo ngunndoo on ka kammuuli e ka leydi, pellet, Kanko O Laatike Surroowo Yurmetee…óo"
  25,7,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko he…ìi oo Nulaa…óo, himo √±aama √±aametee himo yaha kadi ka lokooji(jeereeji)¬∞? Ko haanunoo ko nde jippintee e makko Maalaa'ikaajo o laatoo wonndude e makko jertinoowo"
  25,8,"Maa…óum werlee e makko ngalu, maa…óum laatanoo mo ngesa o √±aama e mabba. Too√±oo…ìe …ìen wi'i: \"On jokkaali si wonaa gorko mbil…óaa…óo"
  25,9,"Ndaarii [yo Nulaa…óo] ko honno …ìe piyiranay maa mise, …ìe majjii …ìe hattantaake [he…ìude] laawol"
  25,10,"Mawnii On taw…óo si O Muuyii O wa…óane mo∆¥∆¥ere, no e …óum gese no ila ley majje can…óe …óen, O wa…óane kadi ku…ìeeje"
  25,11,"Ko woni, …ìe fennu Darngo ngo, Men heblorani …ìen fennu…ìe Darngal ngal Yiite ooyunge"
  25,12,Si nge yi'ii …ìe immorde e nokkuure wo…ó…óunde nananee nge tikkere e faraango
  25,13,"Si …ìe werlaama e nder magge e nokkuure …ìittunde ko …ìe sinndindiraa…ìe, …ìe nodda ton halakuyee"
  25,14,"Wata on noddu hannde halakuyee gooto, noddee halakuyeeji buy"
  25,15,"Maaku: \"Enee, ko …óum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude, kaa ko Aljanna luttoowo on, on mo huloo…ìe Alla …ìen fodaa? O laatanike …ìe njo…ìdi e wattinirde"
  25,16,"No woodani …ìe nder ton ko …ìe welaa, ko …ìe √±ii…ìoo…ìe, …óum laatike e dow Joomi maa…óa Fodoore lannditeteende"
  25,17,"√ëalnde O moo…ìidoyta …ìe e ko …ìe rewaynoo kon gaanin Alla, O Daala: \"Enee, ko onon majjini …ìee jeyaa…ìe Am, kaa ko kam…ìe majji Laawol ngol"
  25,18,"∆äi wi'a: \"Senayee wonanii Ma, haananah men nde men jogitotoo gaanin Maa…óa immorde e rewetee…ìe, kono, A dakmintinii …ìe e baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen haa …ìe yejjiti waaju ngun …ìe laatii yim…ìe halkii…ìe"
  25,19,"Gom…óii …ìe fennii on, sabu ko wi'oton kon, …ìe hattantah yiltugol [Lepte …óen] wanaa wallude, kala too√±u…óo e moo…óon Men mee…óinay mo Lepte maw…óe"
  25,20,"Men Nulaali ado maa…óa immorde e Nulaa…ìe si wanaa kam…ìe hi…ìe nafoo √±aametee hi…ìe seenoo kadi ka luumaaji, Men wa…ói yoga e moo…óon fitina yoga, fii yo on mu√±√±o. Joomi maa…óa laatike ko O Yi'oowo"
  25,21,"∆Åen …ìe jortaaki hawroyde e Amen wi'i: \"Ko hannoo jippinee e makko Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen, maa…óum men yi'a Joomi amen?\" Gom…óii …ìee mawnintinike ka wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe, …ìe townitii townitaare mawnunde"
  25,22,"√ëalnde …ìe yi'oyta Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen weltaare alanaa bom…ìe …ìen nden √ëalnde, …ìe wi'a: \"Heedo heedaango"
  25,23,"Men ardini faade e ko …ìe gollunoo kon immorde e gollal, Men wa…ói ngal punndi caraandi"
  25,24,Yim…ìe Aljanna …ìen nden √ëalnde …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude √±ii…ìirde …ìuri labeede kadi √±allirde
  25,25,E √ëalnde nde kummu ngun seekorta duule …óen Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen jippinee jippineede
  25,26,"Laamu GoongAawu ngun nden √ëalnde ko Hinnorante On ngu woodani, laatoo √ëalnde sa…ótunde e dow yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  25,27,"E √ëalnde too√±u…óo on ≈ãatoyta junngo makko ngon, o wi'a: \"Eeh jalla min, mi jogitino wonndude e Nulaa…óo on Laawol"
  25,28,"Eeh bone am haaniino min, mi jogitanooki kaariijo sehilaajo"
  25,29,"Gom…óii o majjinii lam gaayi Deftere nden …ìaawo nde arii a am, Seytaane laatike ko o jaasinoowo ne…ó…óanke on"
  25,30,"Nulaa…óo on maaka: \"Ko ann yo Jooma pellet, yim…ìe am …ìen …ìe jogitike ndee Alqur'aanaare wikkaande(accaande)"
  25,31,"Ko wano nii, Men wa…óirani kala Annabaajo ga√±o immorde e bon…ìe …ìen, Joomi maa…óa yonii Fewnoowo e Ballo"
  25,32,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe wi'i: \"Ko hanno Alqur'aanaare nden jippinee e makko e jumla gooto?\" ∆äum ko wano nii, fii yo Men tabintinir nde …ìernde maa…óa nden Men rewnindira nde rewnindirgol"
  25,33,"∆Åe addantaa ma misal, si wanaa Men addanii ma Goonga kan e ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude firo"
  25,34,"∆Åen moo…ìoytee…ìe e dow geece muu…óum faade ka Jahannama, ko …ìen …óon woni …ìuru…ìe bonde nokkuure e …ìuru…ìe majjude kade laawol"
  25,35,"Gom…óii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, Men wa…ói wonndude e makko Musi…ó…óo makko on Haaruuna ballo"
  25,36,"Men Daali: \"Yahee ka …ìen yim…ìe fennu…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen, Men yirbini …ìe yirbinndee"
  25,37,"E yim…ìe Nuuhu tuma nde …ìe fennunoo Nulaa…ìe …ìen, Men yooli …ìe Men wa…ói …ìe maande fii yim…ìe …ìen, Men heblani too√±oo…ìe …ìen Lepte muusu…óe"
  25,38,E Aadinkoo…ìe …ìen e Samuudinkoo…ìe …ìen e yim…ìe …ìunndu ndun e gire …óuu…óu…óe hakkunde …óum
  25,39,"Gooto kala e ma…ìe Men piyani …óum mise, gooto kala e ma…ì…ìe men halki …óum halkugol"
  25,40,"Gom…óii …ìe arii e nden saare to…ìaande to…ìo bonngo. Kaa …ìe laataaki hi…ìe yi'a …óe? Ko woni, …ìe laatinoke …ìe jortaaki Immotal"
  25,41,"Si …ìe yi'ii ma, …ìe jogitotaako ma si wanaa jalnori. Enee, ko oo Alla Immini Nulaa…óo"
  25,42,Fii kala hari o …ìadike(…óesi) majjinnde en gaayi rewetee…ói me'en …óin si tawiino wanaa ko mu√±√±i …óen kon e dow majji. Aray …ìe anndoyat tuma …ìe yi'ata Lepte …óen ko hommbo …ìur…óo majjude laawol
  25,43,"Enee, a tinii on jogitii…óo rewetee…óo makko on belee…óe makko …óen. E hara ko an laatotoo e dow makko fawtii…óo"
  25,44,"Kaa a sikku wonnde ko …ìuri heewude e ma…ì…ìe hi…ìe nana maa…óum hi…ìe hakkila? Anndu kam…ìe …ìe wonaali si wanaa wano neemoraa…ói, toode, ko kam…ìe …ìuri majjude laawol"
  25,45,"Kaa a tinaali faade e Joomi maa…óa honno O fontiri …óowdi ndin? Sinndo O Muuyuno O wa…óayno ndi dee∆¥undi, refti Men wa…ói naange ngen tinndinaynge e mayri"
  25,46,Refti Men tami ndi ka Amen tamannde newiinde
  25,47,"Ko Kanko woni On wa…óan…óo on jemma on koltu e …óoyngol ngol fowtere, O wa…ói √±alorma on ngal saakor…óo"
  25,48,"Ko Kanko woni On accitu…óo keni …óin ko …ói weltinooji hakkunde Yurmeende Makko nden, Men jippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam laa…ìu…óam"
  25,49,"Fii yo Men wurnitir …óam leydi maayundi, Men yarna…óam kadi kon ko Men tagi neemoraa…ói e yim…ìe …óuu…óu…ìe"
  25,50,"Gom…óii Men fensitii nde hakkunde ma…ì…ìe fii yo …ìe waajito, salii …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen si wanaa yeddugol"
  25,51,Sinndo Men Muuyuno Men Nulayno e kala saare jertinoowo
  25,52,Wata a …óofto yeddu…ìe …ìen ha…ì e ma…ì…ìe hare jihaadi mawnde
  25,53,"Ko Kanko woni On jillindir…óo maaje …óen …ói…ói, ngoo…óoo ko welungo ∆¥em ngoo…óoo kadi ko lam…óamwo haa…óungo tak, O wa…ói wirngallo hakkunde majje, e heedo heedaango"
  25,54,"Ko Kanko woni on Tagu…óo …ìanndunke immorde e ndiyam …óam, O wa…ói mo dammbe e esiraawo, Joomi maa…óa laatike ko O Hattan…óo"
  25,55,"Hi…ìe rewa gaanin Alla kon ko nafataa …ìe lorrataa …ìe, yeddu…óo on laatike ko o tee…óii…óo Joomi makko"
  25,56,Men Nuliraali ma si wanaa ko a weltinoowo e jartinoowo
  25,57,"Maaku: \"Mi naamaaki on e dow …óum njo…ìdi si wanaa on yi…óu…óo jogitaade faade ka Joomi makko Laawol"
  25,58,"Wakkilo e On Wuuru…óo Mo maayataa subuhino…óaa wonndunde e yettugol Mo, O yonii e …óum Humpitii…óo junubaaji jeyaa…ìe Makko"
  25,59,"On Tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, e nder bal…óe jeego'o refti O fotondiri ka dow Arsi, Hinnorante On lanndo Mo ko O Humpitii…óo. @Corrected"
  25,60,"Si wi'anaama …ìe: \"Sujjanee Hinnorante On\" ∆Åe wi\"a: \"Ko hommbo woni Hinnorante On? Enee, hara men sujjanay kon ko yamir…óaa men?\" ∆äum …ìeydi …ìe fo…ó…óitaare"
  25,61,Mawnii On wa…óu…óo ka kammu burjuuji(buurti) o wa…ói e nder majji pitilol e leelewal jalbungal
  25,62,Ko Kanko woni On wa…óu…óo jemma on e √±alorma on lontondiray…ói fii on faandii…óo annditugol maa…óum o faandii jarnugol
  25,63,"E jeyaa…ìe Hinnorante On, …ìen yahoo…ìe ka leydi ko no newiri, si majju…ìe …ìen ewnike …ìe, …ìe wi'a: \"Kisiyee\". @Corrected"
  25,64,"E …ìen waaloo…ìe sujjannde Joomi ma…ì…ìe e daragol [juula]"
  25,65,"E …ìen wi'oo…ìe: \"Joomi amen wo…ó…óintinan men Lepte Jahannama …óen, pellet, Lepte magge …óen ko duumii…óe"
  25,66,"Pellet, …óen bonii √±ii…ìirde e darorde"
  25,67,"E …ìen taw…ìe si …ìe nafkii …ìe fantintaa …ìe …ìittintaa kadi, […ìe] woni √±ii…ìu…ìe hakkunde …óum"
  25,68,"E …ìen …ìe rewaali wonndude e Alla rewetee…óo goo, …ìe waraali fittaandu ki Alla harmini kin si wanaa sabu goonga, hara …ìe jeenataa. Mo wa…óii …óum o hawray e junuubu"
  25,69,"Sowanoyte mo Lepte …óen √ëalnde Darngal, o luttinoyee e nder majje ko o hoynaa…óo"
  25,70,"Si wanaa …ìen tuubu…ìe …ìe gom…óini …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, haray …ìen …óon Allalomtinay bon…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin mo∆¥∆¥i. Alla wonii ko O Surroowo Yurmetee…óo"
  25,71,"Kala tuubu…óo o golli ko mo∆¥∆¥i haray pellet, kanko o ruttoto ka Alla ko o ja…ìanaa…óo tuubuubuyee"
  25,72,"E …ìen …ìe seeditotaako penaale …óen si …ìe rewii ka rayrayti …óin [wowletee] …ìe fe∆¥∆¥ay ko teddu…ìe @Corrected"
  25,73,E …ìen taw…ìe si …ìe waajoraama Aayeeje Joomi ma…ì…ìe …óen …ìe hippotaako e dow majje ko …ìe faa…óu…ìe e wumu…ìe
  25,74,"E …ìen wi'oo…ìe: \"Joomi amen, okku men immorde e sonnaa…ìe amen e ge…óal…ìe amen …ìuu…ìendan gite, wa…óaa men wonannde huloo…ìe Alla …ìen √±entintee…ìe"
  25,75,"∆Åen…óon …ìe yo…ìoyte hu…ìeere nden sabu ko …ìe mu√±√±ii kon, …ìe hawroya nder ton e hiwraango e salminaango"
  25,76,Ko …ìe √±ii…ìoo…ìe nder ton mo∆¥∆¥ii √±ii…ìirde e darorde
  25,77,"Maaku: \"Jey…óo lam On haajaaka e moo…óon sinndo wanaano du'aaji mo'on …óin, gom…óii on fenniino aray …óe laatoo duumii…óe [Lepte laakara]"
  26,1,"Taa, Siin, Miim"
  26,2,∆äen ko Aayeeje Deftere …ìanngunde nden
  26,3,Belajo'o an a tampiniray hoore maa…óa kin fii …ìe laataaki gom…óin…ìe
  26,4,Si Men Muuyii Men jippinay e ma…ì…ìe immorde ka kammu Aaya daa…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen √±alla ko …óe yankinanii…óe mo
  26,5,Arataa e ma…ì…ìe waaju immorde ka Hinnorante On fu…ó…óaangu si wanaa …ìe laatike …óuurii…ìe ngu
  26,6,Gom…óii …ìe fennii aroyay e ma…ì…ìe kabaruuji ko …ìe laatinoo ko…ìe jalkitano
  26,7,"Enee, …ìe yi'aali faade e leydi ndin, no foti hewde ko Men fu…óini e mayri immorde e kala noone teddu…óo"
