  38,22,"Nde …ìe naatuoo ka Daawuuda, o …óen∆¥ii …ìe. ∆Åe wi'i: \"Wata a hulu ! Ko wennju…ìe …ói…óo; go…ó…óo e amen too√±ii oya. √ëaawir goonga hakkunde amen, wata a too√±u, tinndinaa men e laawol focciingol ngol"
  38,23,"Oo ko musi…ó…óo am: himo jogii baali cappan…óe jeenay e jeenay, min mi…óo jogii baalii gootii. O wi'i: \"Henndinam ngii\"; o foolimi e yewtere"
  38,24,"O maaki: \"Pellet, o too√±irii ma lamndagol baalii maa ngii, wa…ótugol e baali makko …óin\". ∆äuu…óii ko hawtu…ìe too√±indirta hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa …ìen gom…óim…ìe, …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói - …ìen non no fan…ói. - Daawuuda felliti, wonnde Men jarribike mo. O insinanii Joomi makko, o suuyiri sujjugol, o tuubi"
  38,25,"Men yaafanii mo …óum. Pellet non, hino woodani mo ko Amen, …ìadal e mo∆¥∆¥ude ruttorde"
