  38,35,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, haforanam, ye…óaa lam laamu, ngu heertantaako go…ó…óo goo, …ìaawo am. Pellet, ko An woni ye…óoowo On"
  38,36,"Men eltani mo henndu ndun, tawi hindu wifira e sago makko, neweende, nokku kala ko o yi…ói"
  38,37,"E seytanuuji …óin, mahaynoo…ói e mutaynoo…ói"
  38,38,"Go…ó…ói …óin, ko dummbaa…ói e pen…óe"
  38,39,"∆äum ko dokkal Amen. Okkitir, maa jogitoraa ko aldaa e lamnditoreede"
  38,40,"Ko pellet, hino woodani mo ka Amen, …ìadal e mo∆¥∆¥ude ruttorde"
  38,41,"Janto kadi jeyaa…óo Amen on Ayyuuba, nde o noddunoo Joomi makko, wonnde : \"Seytaane memirii lam tampere e muuseendi"
  38,42,"[Allah wi'ani mo]: \"Latir tunndawal maa ngal [ka leydi]: ∆äam …óoo, ko lootor…óam, …ìuu…ìu…óal e njaram"
  38,43,"Men ye…ói mo …ìeynguure makko nden, e yeru ma…ì…ìe tawti …ìe, yurmeende immorde e Amen, e waaju wonannde mar…ìe haqqille …ìen"
  38,44,"Nanngir sookewo maa ngon, tamere hu…óo, piyiraa …óum [suddii…óo maa on], fii wata a firtu (woondoore nden)\". Men tawu mo, mu√±√±ii…óo. O mo∆¥∆¥ii jeyaa…óo. Pellet, ko o …óuu…óu…óo tuubugol-ruttoo"
  38,45,"Janto kadi, jeyaa…ìe Amen …ìen, Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba, joomiraa…ìe cemmbe e yi'an…óe"
  38,46,"Men heertinanii …ìe heertinannde, annditugol galle (laakara) …óen"
  38,47,"E kadi …ìee ka Amen, ko jeyaa…ìe e su…ìaa…ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe su…ìaa…ìe"
  38,48,"Janto kadi Ismaa'iila, e Yuusa'u, e Zal-Kifli, kala ma…ì…ìe, ko jeyaa…ìe e su…ìaa…ìe"
  38,49,"∆äum ko waaju. Ko pellet, hino woodani gom…óu…ìe …ìen, ruttorde mo∆¥∆¥unde"
  38,50,"∆äum ko Aljannaaji √±ii…ìal, …ói …ìe udditanaa dame mun"
  38,51,"hara ko …ìe so…ì…ìindii …ìe ton, hi…ìe nodda ton muuyantee…ói …óuu…óu…ói e njaram"
  38,52,"Hino woodani …ìe (ton): ra…ì…ìidu…ìe ndaar…óe, goree…ìe"
  38,53,"Ko …óum woni ko foda…óon, fii √ëalaande hasboore nden"
  38,54,"Pellet, …óum ko arsike Amen, gasugol alanaa mo"
  38,55,"∆äum, [ko njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe]. Pellet, hino woodani kadi bew…ìe …ìen, ko …ìuri bonnde e ruttorde"
  38,56,"woni Jahannama, nge …ìe naatoyta. Nge bonii nda…ó…óudi"
  38,57,"∆äum, ko yo …ìe mee…óu: ko fatata, e ∆¥e∆¥∆¥iri"
  38,58,"go…ó…óe …óen, nanndu…óe e majje, ko nooneeji"
  38,59,"E hino dental naatiroyay ngal doole e mon, toolii alanaa …ìe; tawde ko …ìe naatoo…ìe Yiite"
  38,60,"∆Åen wi'a: bismilla alanaa mon, ko onon defi men …óum\". Nge bonii √±ii…ìirde"
  38,61,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Joomi amen, defu…óo men …óum on, …ìeydan mo leptte cowalle ka Yiite"
  38,62,"∆Åeya wi'i: \"Ko ha…ói men yi'ugol wor…ìe, …ìe men limtaynoo e bom…ìe …ìen"
  38,63,"Hara men jogitorno …ìe ton jalnori, kaa ko gite (amen) yawti …ìe"
  38,64,"Pellet, ka goonga, ko …óum woni yeddondiral yim…ìe Yiite …ìen"
  38,65,"Maaku: \"Anndee ko mi jertinoowo. Rewetee…óo woo alaa, si wanaa Allah Gooto, Foolu…óo On"
  38,66,"Jey…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde …óin …ói…ói, Foolu…óo, Haforoowo On"
  38,67,"Maaku: \"(Ndee Alqur'aanaare), ko nde kabaaru maw…óo"
  38,68,kono hi…óon …óuurnii …óum
  38,69,"Ganndal alanaano lam, e fii mbatu ngun dowrowu, tuma nde …ìe wennjaynoo"
  38,70,"Wahayinaaka e am, si wanaa wonnde min on, ko mi jertinoowo …ìanngina"
  38,71,"Janto nde Joomi maa daalannoo Malaa'ika'en: \"Min ko Mi tagiroowo …ìanndinke, immorde loopal"
  38,72,"si Mi fotindirii mo, Mi wuttii e makko ruuhu Am on, haray suuyanee mo sujjon"
  38,73,Malaa'ika'en fow sujji …ìe denndaangal
  38,74,"si wanaa Ibuliisa, o mawnintinii, o woni jeyaa…óo e yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  38,75,"(Allah) daali: \"Ko an yo Ibuliisa, ko ha…óu maa sujjangol ko Mi tagiri juu…óe Am? A mawnintini kaa a jeya e townitii…ìe …ìen?\" @Corrected"
  38,76,"O wi'i: \"Ko min …ìuri mo mo∆¥∆¥ude. A tagirii lam e yiite, A tagirii mo kanko e loopal"
  38,77,"O daali: \"Yaltu ton, an on, ko a riiwaa…óo"
  38,78,"pellet, kuddi Am ndin fawike ma haa √ëalnde njo…ìdi diina"
  38,79,"(Ibuliisa) wi'i : \"Joomi am, nennitanam, haa √±alnde nde …ìe immintintee"
  38,80,"O daali: \"A jeyaama e nennitantee…ìe …ìen"
  38,81,haa e √±alaande happu anndaa…óo
  38,82,"O wi'i: \"Mi woondirii mawngu Maa ngun ! Ma mi bewnu…ìe fow ma…ì…ìe"
  38,83,"si wanaa jeyaa…ìe Maa, la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen e ma…ì…ìe"
  38,84,"(Allah) daali: \"Mi woondirii goonga, ko goonga mi wowlata"
  38,85,"ma Mi hebbinire Jahannama, e …ìen jokku…ìe ma fow e ma…ì…ìe"
  38,86,"Maaku: \"Mi lamndaaki on njo…ìdi e fii …óum; mi wonaali jeyaa…óo e sincoo…ìe(deftatoobe)"
  38,87,"Ndee [Alqur‚Äôaanaare] wonaali, si wanaa waaju tageefo ngon"
  38,88,"Ma on anndu (fii) kabaaru mayre, ko nee…ìaa"
  39,1,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  39,2,"Men jippiniirii Deftere nden e maa…óa, e hoore goonga. rewu Allah, la…ì…ìinanaa Mo diina kan"
  39,3,"Anndee, ko Allah woodani diina laa…ìuka kan. ∆Åen non …ìe …ìeya jogitori yi…ó…ìe gaanin Makko (hara hi…ìe wi'a): \"Men alaa rewirde …ói, si wanaa tun no …ói …ìannira men ka Allah, …ìadal\". Pellet, Allah √±aawoyay hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, e kon ko …ìe woni lurrude e mun. Pellet, Allah fewnataa on won…óo fewnoowo, …óuu…óu…óo yeddugol"
  39,4,"Sinno Allah yi…óuno, nde O siforta …ìi…ó…óo, O su…ìayno ko O yi…ói woo, e ko O tagi kon. Senayee woodanii Mo ! Ko Kanko woni Allah, Bajjo, Foolu…óo On"
  39,5,"O tagirii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, goonga.Himo suddira jemma on √±alorma on, O suddira √±alorma on jemma on. O elti naange ngen e lewru ndun, kala majji no doga haa e lajal ta∆¥aangal. Anndee, ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, Haforoowo On"
  39,6,"O tagii on e fittaandu wooturu, refi O wa…ói e ndun, genndo mayru. O jippinani on e neemoraa…ói …óin, nooneeji jeetati. Himo taga on ka teege yumma mon en, tagu …ìaawo tagu, e nder ni…ìe tati. Ko On moo…óon Allah, woni Joomi mon ! Ko Kanko laamu woodani. Rewetee…óo alaa, si wanaa Allah. Ko honno ferlitora…óon [e rewugol Mo]"
  39,7,"Si on yeddii, anndon Allah, ko yondinii…óo e mon. O ja…ìantaa jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, keeferaaku. Si on yettii Mo non, O weltanoo on …óum.Hay gooto roondantaako go…ó…óo woo donngal mum. Refti ko ka Joomi mon, woni ruttorde mon; O yeetitoo on, fii kon ko gollayno…óon. Pellet, ko O anndu…óo, ko woni e …ìer…óe"
  39,8,"Si loraa memii ne…ó…óo on, o noddira Joomi makko, ruttagol e Makko. Refti si O okkii mo mo∆¥∆¥ere, immorde ka Makko, o yejjita ko o noddaynoo kon ado …óum, o wa…óana Allah kafidii…ói, fii no o majjinira (yim…ìe …ìen) e laawol Makko ngol. MaAku: \"Dakmitor keeferaaku maa ngun, see…óa. Pellet, ko a jeyaa…óo e yim…ìe Yiite …ìen"
  39,9,"Kaa ko on yankinotoo…óo tummbo jemma, ko o sujjoowo, darotoo…óo (naafe), hara himo laakara, himo jortii yurmeende Joomi makko nden... Maaku: \"Hara anndu…ìe …ìen fotay e …ìe anndaa …ìen?\" Anndu ko waajitotoo, ko joomiraa…ìe haqqille …ìen"
  39,10,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo jeyaa…ìe Am gom…óim…ìe, hulee Joomi mon\". Hino woodani mo∆¥∆¥im…ìe (golle) …ìen e oo aduna, mbarjaari. Leydi Allah ndin ko yaajundi. Anndee mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìen timminirante njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndin, ko aldaa e limoore"
  39,11,"Maaku: \"Min mi yamiraama rewugol Allah, la…ì…ìinana Mo diina kan"
  39,12,"Mi yamiraa kadi, wonugol arano e jebbilii…ìe …ìen"
  39,13,"Maaku : \"Min mi…óo huli, si mi yeddii Joomi am, lepte √ëalaande Mawnde"
  39,14,"Maaku: \"Ko Allah mi rewata, mi la…ì…ìinan Mo diina am"
  39,15,"rewee ko yi…óu…óon onon, hara wanaa Kanko. Maaku: \"Ko woni hayru…ìe …ìen, ko …ìen …ìe tawata √ëalnde Darngal, …ìe hayrinii ko'e ma…ì…ìe, e …ìeynguureeji ma…ì…ìe\". Anndee ko nden woni hayrere …ìanngunde nden"
  39,16,"Hino woodirani …ìe senngo dow ma…ì…ìe, kippoodi Yiite, e kippoodi senngo ley ma…ì…ìe. Ko …óum woni ko Allah hul…ìinirta jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Ko onon yo jeyaa…ìe Am, kori hulee Lam"
  39,17,"∆Åen wo…ó…óitor…ìe rewugol bewnooji …ói, …ìe ruttii e Allah, welo-welo no woodani …ìe. Wewlinir jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen"
  39,18,"nanoo…ìe Konngol …ìen, …ìe jokka ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e maggol. Ko …ìen woni …ìe Allah fewni …ìen, ko …ìen woni joomiraa…ìe haqqille …ìen"
  39,19,E ko on mo konngol lepte jojji e mun... E ko an da…óndata won…óo ka Yiite
  39,20,"Si ko …ìen hulu…ìe Joomi mun, hino woodani …ìe ku…ìeeje [ka Aljanna] e ku…ìeeje mahaa…óe dow majje, hara can…ói no ila ley majje. Ko fodoore Allah ! Allah non firtataa fodoore. @Corrected"
  39,21,"E a yi'aali, wonnde Allah saa∆¥inirii ndiyam ka kammu, o naadi …óam e nder …ìulli ka leydi; refti O yaltinira …óam remuru seedundu noone, refti ndu …óay…óa, yi'aa hindu soy…ói; refti O wa…óa …óum ko muncaa. Pellet, wonii e …óum, waaju, wonannde joomiraa…ìe haqqille …ìen"
  39,22,"E ko on mo Allah ya√±√±ani …ìendre mun nden, fii lislaamu, hara himo e ndaygu immorde ka Joomi makko... Bone woodanii …ìen yooru…ìe …ìer…óe mun, e jantagol Allah. ∆Åen wonii e majjere …ìanngunde"
  39,23,"Allah jippinii ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e yewtere, Deftere nanndunde [√±aawooje], …óimmitunde. Nde guri …ìen huloo…ìe Joomi mun ri…ìirta (nanugol nde), refti guri e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe dee∆¥ira jantoore Allah nden. Ko …óum woni peewal Allah ngal O fewnirta on Mo muuyani. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo mo alaa"
  39,24,"E ko on reentarii…óo yeeso mun ngon, e lepte bon…óe …óen √ëalnde Darngal... Too√±u…ìe …ìen wi'anee ontuma: \"Mee…óee kon ko wonuno…óon faggitanaade"
  39,25,"Adinoo…ìe …ìen fenniino, lepte …óen ardirani …ìe, ka …ìe so'aa-anndude"
  39,26,"Allah mee…óiniri …ìe koyeera, ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet non, ko lepte laakara …óen non, …ìuri mawnude, si tawno hi…ìe anndunoo"
  39,27,"Gom…óii Men piyanii yim…ìe …ìen, e ndee Alqur'aanaare, kala misal, belajo'o, …ìe waajitora"
  39,28,"Alqur'aanaare (janngeteende) e haala Aarabu, nde aldaa e oo√±aare, fii no …ìe gom…óira"
  39,29,"Allah wa…óii misal, gorko mo lurru…ìe hawti …óum, hi…ìe poo…óondira mo, e gorko laa…ìan…óo gorko [goo]: Hara …ìen …ói…óo fotay e misal? Yettoore woodanii Allah! Kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe anndaa"
  39,30,"Pellet, ko a maayoowo, kam…ìe kadi ko …ìe maayoo…ìe"
  39,31,"refti onon, √ëalnde Darngal, ko ka Joomi mon, yeddondiroyton"
  39,32,"E ko hommbo …ìuri too√±de wa on fenu…óo e hoore Allah, maa o fenni goonga kan nde ka arunoo e makko? E wonaa Jahannama woni jaa∆¥orde yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  39,33,"On non ardu…óo e goonga, o goongini …óum, ko …ìen woni gom…óu…ìe …ìen"
  39,34,"Hino woodani kala ko …ìe faaletee, ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe; ko …óum njo…ìdi mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  39,35,"fii no Allah yawtirana …ìe, ko …ìuri bonnde e ko …ìe golli kon, O yo…ìitira …ìe njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndin, ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e ko …ìe gollaynoo kon"
  39,36,"Allah siforaali yonugol jeyaa…óo Makko on? Hi…ìe hul…ìinire …óin …ói wonaa Mo. Kala mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo alanaa mo"
  39,37,"Kala non mo Allah fewni, majjinoowo mo alaa. Allah siforaali wonnde Foolu…óo, Jom lepte"
  39,38,"Pellet, si a lamndike …ìe: \"Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin?\", ma …ìe wi'u: \"Ko Allah\". Maaku: \"Yeetee lam fii …óin …ói rewoton gaanin Allah, si Allah faandanike lam lorra, hara …ói huncanay lam lorra Makko kan? Maa si O faandanike lam yurmeende, taw si …ói ha…óay lam yurmeende Makko nden? Maaku: \"Allah yonii lam, ko e Makko hoolnotoo…ìe …ìen tuuginotoo"
  39,39,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, gollee e laawol mon, min ko e [laawol am] mi gollirta. Aray ka anndon"
  39,40,"ko hommbo lepte hoynay…óe aroyat e muu…óum, lepte duumii…óe jippoo e makko"
  39,41,"Men jippinirii Deftere nden e maa…óa, fii yim…ìe …ìen, e hoore goonga. Kala feewu…óo, ko hoore makko [o feewani]; kala kadi majju…óo, ko hoore makko o majjani. A wonaali wakiil e dow ma…ì…ìe"
  39,42,"Allah hino ∆¥ettita pittaali …óin, saanga maayde majji, e …óin …ói maayaali, ka …óoyngol majji. O jogitoo …óin …ói √±aawani maayde, O accita …óiya, haa e lajal ta∆¥aangal. Pellet, maandeeji woni e …óum, wonannde yim…ìe miijitotoo…ìe"
  39,43,"Kaa …ìe jogiti tefooji, gaanin Allah? Maaku: \"Hay si tawii …ói jeyaa huunde, …ói haqqiltaa kadi"
  39,44,"Maaku: \"Tefoore nden fow, ko Allah heeranii. Ko Kanko woodani laamagol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Refti ko ka Makko ruttete…óon"
  39,45,"Si fii Allah tun jantaama, …ìer…ìe …ìen …ìe gom…óinaa laakara …ìen, tamoo. Si fii …óiya, …ói wonaa Mo [Kanko Allah] jantaama, e jaka yoo, hi…ìe wewla"
  39,46,"Maaku: \"Yaa Allah, Fu…ó…óu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, Anndu…óo wirnii…ói e fee√±u…ói, ko An √±aawata hakkunde jeyaa…ìe Maa …ìen, kon ko …ìe luutondiraynoo e mun"
  39,47,"Si tawno no woodanno too√±u…ìe …ìen, ko woni kon ka leydi fow, e yeru mun, wonndude e mum, …ìe sottorayno …óum, bone lepte …óen, √ëalnde Darngal; fee√±irana …ìe ka Allah, kon ko …ìe tijjanooki"
  39,48,"boneeji …ói …ìe faggitinoo …óin fe√±ana …ìe, ko …ìe jalkitaynoo kon huu…ìita …ìe"
  39,49,"Si lorra he…ìii ne…ó…óo on, o nodda Men. Refti si Men okkii mo neema, immorde ka Amen, o wi'a: \"Anndee ko e ganndal [am] mi okkiira …óum\". ∆äum ko jarrabuyee kan; kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe anndaa"
  39,50,"Gom…óii …ìen adinoo…ìe …ìe wi'iino …óum. Kono kon ko …ìe faggitotonoo, nafaani …ìe"
  39,51,"boneeji …ói …ìe faggitotonoo …óin memi …ìe. Too√±u…ìe …ìen e ma…ì…ìe, kon ko …ìe wonunoo e faggitagol, memoyay …ìe, …ìe wonaali laawotoo…ìe"
  39,52,"E …ìe anndaa wonnde Allah no ya√±√±ana arsike on mo O muuyani, O …ìillina [mo O muuyani]? Pellet, maandeeji wonii e …óum, wonannde yim…ìe gom…óinoo…ìe"
  39,53,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo jeyaa…ìe Am fantim…ìe e hoore mun, wata on ta∆¥o yurmeende Allah nden. Pellet, Allah ko haforoowo junubaajo …óin fow. Ko Kanko woni Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  39,54,"Tuubee rutto…óon ka Joomi mon, jebbilano…óon Mo, ado lepte …óen arde e mon, hara on faabetaake"
  39,55,"Jokkee ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e ko jippinaa e mon, immorde ka Joomi, ado lepte …óen ardude on, juhal, hara on so'aa anndude"
  39,56,"fii wata wonkii wi'oy: \"Ee nimse am, e ko mi welsindii e fii Allah. Pellet, mi jeyano e …ìen jalkitoo…ìe"
  39,57,"maa ki wi'a: \"Si Alah fewnuno lam, mi wonanyno jeyaa…óo e gom…óu…ìe …ìen"
  39,58,"Maa ki wi'a, tuma ki yi'ata lepte …óen: \"Si feere ruttagol no woodannoo lam, mi jeyee e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  39,59,"Gasataa ! Tawde Aayeeje Am …óen aruno e maa…óa, fennu…óaa …óe, mawnintini…óaa, laati…óaa jeyaa…óo e yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  39,60,"√ëalnde Darngal, a yi'oya fennonoo…ìe e hoore Allah …ìen, hino …ìawli geece. Wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaa∆¥orde mawnintinii…ìe …ìen"
  39,61,"Allah na da…óndira gom…óu…ìe …ìen, sabu maloore ma…ì…ìe nden. Bone memataa …ìen, wanaa kam…ìe woni sunoytoo…ìe"
  39,62,"Ko Allah woni Tagu…óo kala huunde, ko Kanko kadi woni Fawtii…óo kala huunde"
  39,63,"Ko Kanko sottir…óe kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin woodani. Yeddu…ìe Aayeeje Allah …ìen non, ko …ìen woni hayru…ìe(pertu…ìe) …ìen"
  39,64,"Maaku: \"E ko woori Allah, yamirton mi, yo mi rewu, onon …ìee majju…ìe"
  39,65,"Gom…óii wahayinaama e maa…óa, e …ìen adinoo…ìe ma: \"Si a sirkii, pellet, golle maa …óen bonay jeye…óaa e hayru…ìe …ìen"
  39,66,"Alah rew Allah, jeye…óaa e yettoo…ìe (Mo) …ìen"
  39,67,"∆Åe mawniniraali Allah, no O foti maninireede, hara le, leydi ndin fow, ko tamannde Makko, √ëalnde Darngal, kammuuli …óin kadi taggiree √±aamo Makko. Senayee woodanii Mo ! O toowii e kon ko …ìe sirkanta Mo"
  39,68,"Wuttee ka Allaandu, kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi kon fa…ó…óee, si wanaa …ìen …ìe Allah muuyani [da…óugol]. Refti wuttee e mayru …ói…óa…ìol, tawa ko …ìe darii…ìe habbitii"
  39,69,"Leydi ndin jalbira ndaygo Jeydo ndi On; taalkuru ndun wallinee, Annabaa…ìe e seedee…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen addee; goonga √±aawiree hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, wanaa …ìe too√±etee…ìe"
  39,70,"wonki kala yo…ìee ko golli kon. Ko Kanko [Allah] …ìuri anndude ko …ìe gollata"
  39,71,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen soggiroyee ka Jahannama dente-dente. Haa si …ìe hewtii nge, dame magge udditee, reenu…ìe nge …ìen wi'ana …ìe: \"E Nulaa…ìe jeyaa…ìe e mo'on hewtaano on, janngaynoo…ìe Aayeeje Joomi mon, e moo…óon, …ìe rentina on hawrugol e ndee √±alaande mon?\" ∆Åe wi'a: \"Ko non tigiri, kono Konngol lepte ngol, jojjiino e yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  39,72,"[∆Åe] wi'anee: \"Naatiree dame Jahannama …óen lutton ton. Nge bonii jaa∆¥orde mawnintinii…ìe …ìen"
  39,73,"Huloo…ìe Joomi mun …ìen kadi …óowitiree ka Aljanna, dente-dente. Haa si …ìe hewtii mo, dame makko udditee, reenu…ìe mo …ìen wi'ana …ìe: \"Kisiyee wonii e mon, on laa…ìii, naatiree mo, duumagol"
  39,74,"∆Åe wi'a ontuma: \"Yettoore woodanii Allah, laatinan…óo men fodoore Mun, O ronini men leydi [Aljanna] ndin, me…óen weerira e Aljanna on, kala ka men yi…ói\". Mbarjaari gollunoo…ìe mo∆¥∆¥ere …ìen mo∆¥∆¥ii"
  39,75,"Yi'oyaa Malaa'ikaen, hi…ìe taarii Arsi kin, hi…ìe subbunhinora yettugol Joomi ma…ì…ìe. Goonga √±aawiree hakkunde ma…ì…ìe. Wi'ee ontuma: \"Yettoore woodanii Allah, Jey…óo tegeefo ngon"
  40,1,"Haa, Miim"
  40,2,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, Foolu…óo, Anndu…óo On"
  40,3,"Haforoowo junubaaji …óin, Ja…ìoowo tuubuubuyee, Sa…ótu…óo lepte, Jom yaajeende. Rewetee…óo alaa, si wanaa kanko. Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde nden"
  40,4,"Alaa ko wennjata e Aayeeje Allah …óen, si wanaa yeddu…ìe …ìen. Wata a hoditor ko …ìe dillirta kon ka leydi"
  40,5,"Ado ma…ì…ìe, yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen e feddeeji …óin …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe, fennuno (Nulaa…ìe mun …ìen), mofte kala himmiri nanngugol Nulaa…óo mun on. ∆Åe wennjiri meere, fii no bonnitira (goonga) kan. Kono Mi nanngi …ìe. Taskii no nanngal Am ngal wa…ótinirnoo"
  40,6,"Ko wano nii Konngol Joomi maa ngol, jojjiri e yeddu…ìe …ìen : \"Wonnde pellet, ko …ìe yim…ìe Yiite"
  40,7,"∆Åen (Malaa'ikaa…ìe) roondii…ìe Arsiki kin, e won…ìe bannge makki …ìen, hi…ìe subbunhinora yettugol Joomi ma…ì…ìe, …ìe gom…óina Mo, …ìe insinorana gom…óim…ìe …ìen (wiide): \"Joomi amen, A ya√±√±irii kala huunde, yurmeende e ganndal. Yawtan …ìen tuubu…ìe, …ìe jokki laawol Maa ngol, da…óndaa …ìe kadi lepte Dul…ìoowe ngen"
  40,8,"Joomi amen, naadu…ìe ka Aljannaaji √±ii…ìal, …óin …ói fodu…óaa …ìe, e kala mo∆¥∆¥u…óo e baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe, e genndiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe, e geyngol ma…ì…ìe. Pellet, ko An woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo On"
  40,9,"Da…óndaa…ìe [kuu…óe] e bon…óe …óen. Kala mo da…óndu…óaa [kuu…óe] mun bon…óe …óen nden √ëalnde, haray pellet, A yurmiii mo\". Ko …óum woni maloore mawnunde nden"
  40,10,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen noddiroyte: \"Ko tikkere Allah nden …ìuri mawnude, e dii ko tikkan…óon ko'e mon kon, tuma noddeteno…óon e gom…óinal, yeddon"
  40,11,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Joomi amen, A warii men laawi …ói…ói, wuurnitu…óaa men laawi …ói…ói: men qirrike junuubi amen …óin. Taw si laawol yaltirngol hino woodi"
  40,12,"∆äum moo…óon, ko tawde si Allah tun noddanooma, on yeddon; si O kafidaama, gom…óinon. √ëaawoore nden ko Allah heeranii, Toowu…óo, Maw…óo On"
  40,13,"Ko Kanko woni holloowo on maandeeji Makko …óin, O jippinirana on to…ìo ka kammu. Kono taskotaako, si wanaa ruttotoo…óo [e Allah]"
  40,14,"Rewiree Allah, la…ì…ìinirangol Mo diina kan, hay si heefer…ìe …ìen yi…óaa"
  40,15,"Ko o toowu…óo darjaaji, Jey…óo Arsi kin. Himo jippiniria wahayu on, yamiroore Makko, e on mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, no o jertinira √±alnde Kawral ngal, @Corrected"
  40,16,"√±alnde …ìe fee√±oyta. Huunde suu…óotaako Allah, e fee ma…ì…ìe. Ko hommbo laamu woodani hannde? Ko Allah Bajjo, Foolu…óo On"
  40,17,"Hannde, wonkii kala yo…ìete ko faggitii. Too√±e woo alaa hannde, pellet, Allah ko yaawu…óo √±aawoore"
  40,18,"Jertnirt…ìe, √±alaande dillere nden, tuma …ìer…óe …óen ∆¥awtirta ka konondi, hara hi…ìe (heewu…ìe) ngo∆¥o. Gi…óo woo alanaa too√±oo…ìe …ìen, wanaa tefoowo ja…ìantee…óo"
  40,19,"Himo anndi janfa gite, e ko …ìer…óe …óen suu…ói"
  40,20,"Allah ko goonga √±aawirta. ∆äi …ìe rewata …óin non, gaanin Makko, hay huunde …ói √±aawirtaa. Pellet, ko kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi'oowo On"
  40,21,"Hara …ìee yiilaaki ka leydi, …ìe ndaara no battane ado mabbe …ìen wa'unoo? ∆Åen le no …ìurunoo tii…óude doole e batteeji, ka leydi. Allah nanngitiri …ìe junuubi ma…ì…ìe …óin, …ìe he…ìaano da…óndoowo …ìe e (lepte) Allah …óen"
  40,22,"Ko wa…ói …óum, ko tawde Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen addayno …ìe …ìanngannduyeeji, …ìe yedda. Allah halki …ìe. Pellet, ko O Doolnu…óo, Sa…ótu…óo lepte"
  40,23,"Gom…óii Men nulirii Muusaa Aayeeje Amen …óen, e hujja …ìanngu…óo"
  40,24,"haa e Fir'awna, e Haamaana, e Qaaruuna. Kono …ìe wi'i: \"Ko mbileejo, …óuu…óu…óo fenaande"
  40,25,"Nde o addannoo …ìe goonga kan, immorde e Amen, …ìe wi'iti: \"Waree …ìi…ó…ìe wor…ìe gom…óimdim…ìe …ìen e makko, accon rew…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen\". Pewje heefer…ìe …ìen wonaali, si wanaa e majjere"
  40,26,"Fir'awna wi'i: \"Accee mi wara Muusaa. Yo o noddu Joomi makko ! Mi…óo huli nde o waylata diina mon kan, maa o fe√±√±ina bonnere ka leydi"
  40,27,"Muusa maaki: \"Mi moolorii Jey…óo lam On, jeyi on, e bone kala mawnintinii…óo, mo gom…óinaa √±alaande hasboore"
  40,28,"Gorko gom…óino…óo goo, jeyaa…óo e yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen - suu…óunoo…óo gom…óinal mun - :\"E on waray gorko, fii o wi'i: \"Joomi am ko Allah?\" Hara le o addanii on …ìanngannduyeeji, immorde ka Joomi mon. Si tawii o fenu, haray fenaande makko ko kanko fawii; si tawii kadi o goongu, haray yoga e kon ko kammbirani on, he…ìay on\". Pellet, Allah fewnataa on fantinoowo fennoowo"
  40,29,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, laamu no woodani on hanndi, ko on foolu…ìe ka leydi. Kono ko hommbo wallata en, e lepte Allah …óen, si …óe arii e men?\" Fir'awna wi'i: \"Mi hollataa on, si wanaa ko mi yi'i kon. Mi tindintaa on kadi, si wanaa e laawol peewal ngol"
  40,30,"Gom…óin…óo on wi'iti: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, min on mi…óo hulani on, sugu √±alaande he…ìunoonde feddeeji …óin"
  40,31,"Sugu mbowka yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen, e Aadi'en, e Samuuda'en, e arnoo…ìe …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe …ìen\". Allah faandanaaki too√±ude jeyaa…ìe …ìen"
  40,32,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, min mi…óo hulani on, √ëalaande noddindirton"
  40,33,"√ëalnde huccitiroyton, ho…óon ndoga, hara da…óndoowo on alanaa on e Allah\". Kala mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo alanaa mo"
  40,34,"Gom…óii Yuusufu ardanii on e …ìannganduyeeji, ko adii, on seeraali e sikkitagol kon ko o addani on. Haa nde o faatinoo, wi'u…óon: \"Allah nultataa Nulaa…óo goo, …ìaawo makko\". Ko non majjinirta kala wono…óo fantinoowo sikkitii…óo"
  40,35,"∆Åen wenjiroo…ìe e Aayeeje Allah …óen ko aldaa e hujja ar…óo …ìe, [kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen] mawnii tikkere ka Allah, e ka gom…óim…ìe …ìen. Ko wano non Allah notirta e …ìernde kala mawnintinii…óo dundarankeejo"
  40,36,"Fir'awna wi'i: \" Ko an yo Haamaana, mahanam sooro, no gasa mi yottoo …óate …óen"
  40,37,"…óate kammuuli …óin, mi ∆¥eewoya Rewetee…óo Muusaa On; sabu mi sikki mo fenoowo\". Ko wano non Fir'awna cu…óiranaa, golle makko bon…óe …óen; o sakkaa e laawol (peewal) ngol. Feere Fir'awna nden wonaano, si wanaa e hayrere"
  40,38,"[Gorko] gom…óin…óo on wi'i: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, jokkee lam, mi fewna on e laawol peewal ngol"
  40,39,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, anndee …óam nguurndam aduna, ko dakamme-hun tun, ko laakara on woni, galle √±ii…ìal …óen"
  40,40,"Mo gollii bone, o yo…ìitetaake, si wanaa yeru makko; mo gollii kadi mo∆¥∆¥ere, foti ko gorko maa debbo, hara ko o gom…óin…óo, …ìen …óon naatay Aljanna, …ìe arsikoyee ton, ko aldaa e limoore"
  40,41,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, ko wa…ói si mi…óo nodda on e da…óal, hi…óon nodda lam e Yiite"
  40,42,"Hi…óon nodda lam e yeddugol Allah, sirkana Mo e ko mi alanaa …óum ganndal, hara non, min mi…óo nodda on e Foolu…óo, Suuroowo bakkaatu On"
  40,43,"Sikke alaa, wonnde ko noddoton lam e mun kon, dewal alanaa …óum aduna, wanaa laakara. E wonnde ruttorde men nden, ko ka Allah, e wonnde ko fantim…ìe …ìen, woni Yiite ngen"
  40,44,"Aray nde anndoton, ko mi yewtata on kon; mi fawa fiyaaku am on e Allah. Pellet, Allah ko Reenu…óo jeyaa…ìe …ìen"
  40,45,"Allah da…óndi mo, boneeji …ói …ìe fewjunoo, O fiiltii yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen, ko …ìuri bonnde e lepte"
  40,46,"Yiite ngen, …ìe wee…ìitoyte e magge, bimmbi e kiikii…óe. √ëalnde Darngal daroytoo (wi'oyte): \"Naatee yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen, ka …ìuri sa…ótude e lepte"
  40,47,"Janto tuma …ìe yeddondiroyta ka Yiite, lo'unoo…ìe …ìen wi'ana townitinoo…ìe …ìen: \"Menen, ko onon men jokkuunoo, taw si on du√±anay men ge…ìal e Yiite ngen"
  40,48,"Townitinoo…ìe …ìen wi'a: \"En fow, hi…óen e magge. Gom…óii Allah √±aawii hakkunde jeyaa…ìe …ìen"
  40,49,"Won…ìe ka Yiite …ìen kadi wi'ana ayninaa…ìe Jahannama …ìen: \"Toranee men Joomi mon, O hoynana men, √±alaande (wootere) e lepte …óen"
  40,50,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Nulaa…ìe mon …ìen ardanaano on e …ìanngannduyeeji?\" ∆Åe wi'a: \"Oo'owoye !\" [Ayninaa…ìe] …ìen wi'a: \"Awa toree, onon tigiri !\" Kono toraare heefer…ìe …ìen wonaali, si wanaa e majjere"
  40,51,"Pellet, Men wallay Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen, e gom…óim…ìe …ìen, ka nguurndam aduna, e √ëalnde seedee…ìe …ìen daroytoo"
  40,52,"√±alnde de ngantinagol nafoytaa too√±unoo…ìe …ìen, hara kuddi hino woodani …ìe, e galle bon…óe"
  40,53,"Gom…óii Men okkii Muusaa ganndal [Tawreeta] ngal, Men ronini …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen, Deftere nden"
  40,54,"ko nde peewal e waaju, wonannde joomiraa…ìe haqqille …ìen"
  40,55,"Mu√±√±o tun, pellet, fodoore Allah nden ko goonga, insinano junuubi maa …óin, subbunhinano…óaa Joomi maa, kiikii…óe e bimmbi"
  40,56,"Pellet, wennjiroo…ìe e Aayeeje Allah …óen, ko aldaa e dalil ar…óo e ma…ì…ìe, alaa e …ìer…óe …óen, si wanaa mawnintinagol. ∆Åe yottotaako non, e …óum. Moolor Allah, Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi'oowo On"
  40,57,"Pellet, ko tagde kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, …ìuri mawnude e dii tageendi yim…ìe …ìen. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe anndaa"
  40,58,"Bun…óo e yi'oowo fotataa, gom…óim…ìe …ìen kadi golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói, fotataa e bonnu…óo. Fan…óii ko waajitorton"
  40,59,"Pellet, Darngal, ko ko arata, sikke alaa e mu'un. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe gom…óinaa"
  40,60,"Joomi mon daali: \"Toree Lam, Mi jaabinana on. Mawtinantoo…ìe rewugol Lam …ìen, ko pellet, …ìe naatoyay Jahannama, ko …ìe hoy…ìe"
  40,61,"Ko Allah wa…óirani on jemma on, ka fowto…óon e mun, e √±alorma on, yi'inoowo. Pellet, Allah ko Jom …ìural e yim…ìe …ìen, kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe yettataa (neema)"
  40,62,"Ko On moo…óon Allah Joomi mon, woni Tagu…óo kala huunde. Rewetee…óo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Ko honno firlitorta…óon (e …óum)"
  40,63,"Ko non …ìeya yeddaynoo…ìe Aayeeje Allah …óen, ferlisortenoo"
  40,64,"Ko Allah woni wa…óiran…óo on leydi ndin, √±ii…ìirde, kammu ngun, kippoodi, O mbaadini on - O mo∆¥∆¥ini mbaadiiji mon -, O arsiki on e laa…ìu…ói. Ko On moo…óon woni Allah Joomi mon; senaare woodanii Allah, Jey…óo winndere nden"
  40,65,"Ko Kanko woni wuur…óo On. Rewetee…óo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Rewee Mo kisan; la…ì…ìinano Mo diina kan. Yettoore woodanii Allah, Jey…óo winndere nden"
  40,66,"Maaku: \"Min mi ha…óaama rewugol …óin …ói noddoton gaanin Allah, tuma nde …ìannganduyeeji …óin ari e am, immorde e Joomi am, mi yamiraama kadi, nde mi jebbilantoo, Jey…óo winndere nden"
  40,67,"Ko Kanko woni tagu…óo on e mbumbuldi, refti e to…ì…ìere (maniiyu), refti e he…ó…óere, refti O yaltiniri on penuu…ìe fii no yottoron cemmbe mon, e no laatoron nayee…ìe, - no e mo'on, ∆¥ettitetee…ìe ado …óum, - haa no yottoron lajal happaangal, belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  40,68,"Ko Kanko woni wuurnoowo e waroowo. Si O haajii e fiyaaku, ko O wi'anay mo tun: \"Laato\", o laatoo"
  40,69,"E a tinaali, …ìen yeddondirtee…ìe e Aayeeje Allah …óen, ko honno …ìe firlitoraa"
  40,70,"∆Åen fennu…ìe Deftere nden, e kon ko Men nuliri Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen; …ìe aray anndude"
  40,71,"tuma kolombooje …óen wa…óoyaa e daa…óe ma…ì…ìe, e jolokooje(callalle) …óen, hara hi…ìe daasiree"
  40,72,ka nder wul…óam; refti …ìe hu…ì…ìoyee ka nder Yiite
  40,73,"Refti …ìe wi'anee: \"Ko honto woni …óin …ói kafidayno…óon"
  40,74,"Ko aldah e Allah?\" ∆Åe wi'a: \"∆äi majjitike men. Wurin, men wonaano ko adii, e rewugol hay huunde\". Ko hona nih Allah majjinirta heefer…ìe …ìen"
  40,75,"Ko wa…ói on …óum, ko ko weltorayno…óon kon ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e ko wewlirayno…óon kon"
  40,76,"Naatiree dame Jahannama …óen, luttugol ton. Nge bonii jaa∆¥orde wonande mawnintinii…ìe …ìen"
  40,77,"Mu√±√±o. Pellet, fodoore Allah nden, ko goonga. Ko si Men hollete yoga e ko Men fodi …ìe kon, maa hara Men ∆¥ettite (ado mun) ko ka Amen …ìe ruttirtee"
  40,78,"Gom…óii Men imminii Nulaa…ìe ado maa. Hino e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe Men sifani maa fii mun; hino ma…ì…ìe, …ìe Men sifanaaki ma fii mun. Haananaa Nulaa…óo, addugol Aaya, si wanaa e du≈ãayee Allah. Si yamiroore Allah nden arii, goonga √±aawirte meerente'en sooya nden √±alnde"
  40,79,"Ko Allah woni wa…óiran…óo On neemoraa…ói …óin ko wa…ó…óoron, √±aamon kadi e majji"
  40,80,"nafooje kadi hino woodani on e majji, e no yottoron e majji, haaju hittu…óo e berde mon. Ko e hoore majji e hoore laa…óe …óen, woni ko ronndete…óon"
  40,81,"Himo holla on maandeeji Makko …óin. Ko hon…óum e maandeeji Allah …óin, woni ko yeddoton"
  40,82,"E …ìee yiilaaki ka leydi, …ìe ndaara ko honno battane …ìeya ado ma…ì…ìe wattinirnoo? ∆Åen no …ìurunoo …ìe …óuude e sa…ótude doole e batteeji [wa…óaa…ói] ka leydi. Kono kon ko …ìe faggotonoo, duncanaano …ìe"
  40,83,"Nde Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen addannoo…ìe …ìanngannduyeeji …óin, …ìe wewliri ganndal ko woni ka ma…ì…ìe kon. ∆Åe huu…ìitiraa kon ko …ìe jalkitaynoo"
  40,84,"Nde …ìe yi'unoo lepte Amen …óen, …ìe wi'i: \"Men gom…óinii Allah tun, men yeddii kon ko men wonunoo e sirkannde"
  40,85,"Kono gom…óinal ma…ì…ìe wonaano ko nafata …ìe, fewndo …ìe yi'unoo lepte Amen …óen; …óum ko laawol Allah non, gom…óii …óun yawtiino e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Yeddu…ìe …ìen sooyi …óon nden √±alnde"
  41,1,"Haa, Miim"
  41,2,"Ko jipporiinde immorde ka Yurmetee…óo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  41,3,"Deftere fensitaande Aayeeje mun, janngeteende e …óemngal aarabu, wonannde yim…ìe anndoo…ìe"
  41,4,"wewlinaynde jertina. Kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude …ìen e ma…ì…ìe, …óuurnii, …ìen …ìe nanataa"
  41,5,"∆Åe wi'i: \"∆Åer…óe amen no ommbanii ko noddataa men e mun kon, noto hino e noppi amen, heedo kadi hino hakkunde amen e maa. Haray wonu e golle maa ; menen kadi me…óen e golle amen"
  41,6,"Maaku: \"Anndee ko ne…ó…óanke yeruujo mon. Wahayinaama e am, wonnde Rewetee…óo mon on, ko Rewetee…óo gooto. √ëii…ìee e …óum, insinano…óon Mo\". Bone woodanii sirkoo…ìe …ìen"
  41,7,"…ìe jonnataa …ìen zakka, hara kadi hi…ìe yeddi fii laakara"
  41,8,"Pellet, …ìen gom…óim…ìe …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin, hino woodani …ìe njo…ìdi ndi ta∆¥ondirtaa"
  41,9,"Maaku: \"E onon on yedday On tagu…óo leydi ndin nder bal…óe …ói…ói, wa…óanon Mo goree…ìe? Awa ko On woni Jey…óo winndere nden. @Corrected"
  41,10,"O wa…ói pelle e dow mayri, O hebbini barki e mayri, O e…ì…ìi nguureeji mayri …óin e nder bal…óe nayi timmu…óe, wonannde lamndotoo…ìe …ìen. @Corrected"
  41,11,"Refti O fotondiri ka kammu, fewndo ka ngu curkinnoo, O daalidani ngun kanngu e leydi ndin: \"Ardiree …óoftaare, maa karheede\". ∆äi wi'idi: \"Men arii ko men …óoftii …ìe\". @Corrected"
  41,12,"O timminiri …ói kammuuli jee…ói…ói nder bal…óe …ói…ói, O yamiri kala kammu, fiyaaku maggu. Men cu…óiniri kammu aduna ngun, koode e reenir…óum. ∆äum ko e…ì…ìoore Foolu…óo, Anndu…óo On. @Corrected"
  41,13,"Si …ìe …óuurnike, haray wi'u …ìe: \"Men jertinirii on haacaangu, sugu haacaango Aadi'en e Samuuda'en"
  41,14,"nde Nulaa…ìe …ìen ardirannoo…ìe, yeeso ma…ì…ìe e …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe, wonnde: \"Wata on rewu dey, si wanaa Allah\", …ìe wi'i: \"Si Joomi amen haajuno, ko Malaa'ika O jippinaynoo. Awa menen, ko men yeddu…ìe ko nula…óon mun kon"
  41,15,"Aadii'en kan, …ìe mawnintini ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, …ìe wi'i: \"Hara ko hommbo …ìuri men doole?\" E …ìee yi'aali, wonnde Allah tagu…óo …ìe On no …ìuri …ìe tii…óude doole? ∆Åe woni e yeddugol Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  41,16,"Men wurti henndu …ìuu…ìundu e ma…ì…ìe e √±alaa…óe hiitaa…óe, fii no Men mee…óinira …ìe lepte koyeera …óen ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet, ko lepte laakara …óen …ìuri wonnde koyeera, kadi …ìe faaboytaake"
  41,17,"Samuuda'en kan, Men …ìannginanno …ìe; kono …ìe su…ìii bum…óam …óam e dow peewal ngal. Dillere lepte hoynooje …óen nanngiri …ìe, sabu ko …ìe faggitotonoo kon"
  41,18,Men da…óndi gom…óim…ìe …ìe woniina hulnoo…ìe …ìen
  41,19,√ëalnde non ay…ìe Allah …ìen moo…ìiroytee faade ka Yiite... Hara hi…ìe √±o∆¥∆¥indiree
  41,20,"Haa si …ìe hewtii nge, nann…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, e gii…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, e guri …ìalli ma…ì…ìe …óin seeditoo e dow ma…ì…ìe, kon ko …ìe gollaynoo"
  41,21,"∆Åe wi'ana guri ma…ì…ìe …óen: \"Ko fii honn…óum seeditani…óon e amen?\" ∆äe wi'a: \"Ko Allah wowlin…óo kala huunde On, wowlini men. Ko Kanko tagunoo on gila ka laawol aranol, ko ka Makko kadi ruttete…óon"
  41,22,"On wonaali hi…óon suu…óora, fii wata nan…óe mon, e gii…óe mon, e guri mon seedito e mon. Kono on sikkuno, wonnde Allah anndaa ko …óuu…ói e ko huuwoton"
  41,23,"Ko …óum moo…óon, wonunoo ko sikkuno…óon Joomi mon, …óum halki on. Wa…ótin…óon jeyaa…ìe e pertu…ìe …ìen"
  41,24,"Hay si …ìe mu√±√±ike, ko Yiite ngen wonata jaa∆¥orde ma…ì…ìe; si …ìe …óa…ì…ìii feleede accitee, …ìe wonaali feletee…ìe accitee"
  41,25,"Men wurtani …ìe wondii…ìe, …ìen cu…óinani …ìe ko woni yeeso ma…ì…ìe, e ko woni …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe. Konngol [lepte] ngol jojji e ma…ì…ìe, wondude e mofte yawtunoo…óe ado ma…ì…ìe, immorde e jinna e yim…ìe. Pellet, …ìe laatino hayru…ìe"
  41,26,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen wi'i: \"Wata on jentito ndee Alqur'aanaare, sonkee e mayre (tuma nde janngetee) belajo'o, on foolay"
  41,27,"Ma Men mee…óiniroy yeddu…ìe …ìen, lepte sa…ótu…óe, Men yo…ìira ko …ìuri bonde e ko …ìe huuwaynoo kon"
  41,28,"Ko …óum woni njo…ìdi ay…ìe Allah …ìen: Ko Yiite ngen. Ko galle luttugol woodani …ìe ton, njo…ìdi kon ko …ìe yeddiraynoo Aayeeje Amen …óen"
  41,29,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen wi'a: \"Joomi amen, hollii men majjinnoo…ìe men …ìen ka jinna e ka yim…ìe, men yaa…ìa …ìe men fuga, haa …ìe wona e …ìur…ìe joltude …ìen"
  41,30,"Pellet, wi'u…ìe …ìen : \"Joomi amen ko Allah\", refti …ìe tabiti; Malaa'ika'en hino jippoo e ma…ì…ìe (wiide): \"Wata on hulu, wata on suno; wewliree Aljanna, on mo wonano…óon fodeede"
  41,31,"Ko menen woni walloo…ìe on …ìen ka nguurndam aduna e ka laakara. Hino woodani on ton, kala ko wonkiiji mon woo…óetee, hino woodani ton, kala ko noddoton"
  41,32,"ko maraari, immorde e Haforoore, Hinnotoo…óo"
  41,33,"Hara ko hommbo …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude konngol, wano on noddu…óo e fii Allah, o golli mo∆¥∆¥ere, o wi'i: \"Min, ko e juul…ìe …ìen mi jeyaa"
  41,34,"Mo∆¥∆¥ere nden fotataa e bone on. Du√±ir (golle bon…óe …óen) kon ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude; e jaka yoo, on mo ngayngu woni hakkunde maa e mun, himo wa'ita wa gi…óo sa…ótu…óo giggol"
  41,35,"Kono hawrataa e …óum, si wanaa mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìen; hawrataa e …óum, si wanaa jom ge…ìal mawnungal"
  41,36,"Si sowinsinoore arii he…ìude ma immorde e seytaane, moolor Allah. Kanko ko O Nanoowo, Anndu…óo"
  41,37,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin, jemma on e √±alorama on, e naange ngen e lewru ndun. Wata on sujjan naange ngen wanaa kadi lewru ndun. Sujjanee Allah, tagu…óo …ói On, si wonii ko Kanko rewoton"
  41,38,"Si …ìe townitike, …ìen won…ìe ka Joomi maa kan, hi…ìe subbunhinorana Mo jemma e √±alorma, hara …ìe haa…ìataa"
  41,39,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin, tawde a yi'ay leydi ndin no yoori. Si wonii Men jippinii ndiyam to…ìo e mayri, ndi dilla ndi fontoo. Awa wuurnitu…óo ndi On, pellet, ko wuurnitoowo maay…ìe …ìen, tawde pellet, ko O hattan…óo haka huunde"
  41,40,"Pellet, oo√±otoo…ìe …ìen e Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ìe suu…óotaako Men. E ko feroytee…óo on ka Yiite …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude kaa ko aroyoowo on √ëalnde Darngal hino hoolii? Gollee ko faala…óon, ko pellet, Himo reeni ko golloton kon"
  41,41,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen Alqur'aana tuma nde arunoo e ma…ì…ìe, pellet non, ko nde Deftere teddunde [foolunde]"
  41,42,"meere iwrantaa nde yeeso mayre, wanaa …ìaawo mayre. Ko jipporiinde immorde ka √ëeenyo, Yettinii…óo On"
  41,43,"A wi'aaka si wanaa ko Nulaa…ìe adinoo…ìe ma …ìen wi'anoo. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko O Jom yaafuyee, e Jom lepte muusu…óe"
  41,44,"Si Men wa…óuno nde janngeteende e haala ajami, …ìe wi'ayno: \"Ko ha…óno Aayeeje mayre …óen fensitee? E nde wonay e haala ajami, [Nulaa…óo] on wona aarabuujo?\" Maaku: \"Kayre wonannde gom…óim…ìe …ìen, ko nde peewal e cellal\". ∆Åe gom…óinaa …ìen kan, noto hino e noppi ma…ì…ìe …óin, kayre ko nde ni…ìe e dow ma…ì…ìe; …ìen hino noddiree e nokku wo…ó…óu…óo"
  41,45,"Gom…óii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, nde luutondira e mayre. Si wanaano Konngol ardinoongol immorde ka Joomi maa, hakkunde ma…ì…ìe √±aaweteno. Kam…ìe kan, pellet, hi…ìe e sikke sikkitii…óo nde"
  41,46,"Kala gollu…óo ko mo∆¥∆¥i, ko fii hoore-makko; kala kadi bonnu…óo, yantay e makko. Joomi maa siforaali wonnde, too√±oowo jeyaa…ìe …ìen"
  41,47,"Ko ka Makko woni ko ganndal Darngal ruttetee. Dim…óe yaltataa e coom…ói mun, deyel (woo) saawataa,ngel jibintaa si wanaa e ganndal Makko.√ëalnde O noddiroyta …ìe:\"Ko honto woni kafidaa…ói Am …óin?\", …ìe wi'a:\"Men anndinii Ma, alah e amen seedotoo…óo […óum]"
  41,48,∆Åe majjira e kon ko …ìe rewaynoo ko adii; …ìe yananee wonnde da…óirgal alanaa …ìe
  41,49,"Ne…ó…óanke on haa…ìataa toragol mo∆¥∆¥ere. Si bone memii mo, ko o ta∆¥otoo…óo, yonndinii…óo"
  41,50,"Si Men mee…óinir mo mo∆¥∆¥ere immorde ka Amen, …ìaawo nde lorra memi mo, ko pellet o wi'ay: \"∆äum …óoo ko min ! Mi fellitaani si Darngal daroto. Si mi ruttaama ka Joomi am, ko pellet, mo∆¥∆¥ere hino woodani lam ka Makko\". Ma Men humpitu yeddu…ìe …ìen, fii ko …ìe huuwi kon, ko ma Men mee…óinoy …ìe lepte sa…ótu…óe"
  41,51,"Si Men neeminii e ne…ó…óanke on, o …óuurnoo o toowna balaaje makko; si bone non he…ìii mo, o wona jom toraare yaajunde"
  41,52,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, si wonii le ko ka Allah nde iwri, refti yeddu…óon nde; haray ko hommbo …ìuri majjude on won…óo e lurral wo…ó…óungal"
  41,53,"Aray Men holla …ìe maandeeji Amen …óin ka tatteeji e ma…ì…ìe tigi, haa …ìanngana …ìe wonnde ko nde goonga. E yonaali wonnde Joomi maa, ko O seedii…óo kala huunde"
  41,54,"Anndee hi…ìe e sikke fii hawroygol e Joomi ma…ì…ìe. Anndee non, ko O hu…ìindii…óo kala huunde"
  42,1,"Haa, Miim"
  42,2,"Ain, Siin, Qaaf"
  42,3,"Ko wano nii woni ko Allah Te…ó…óu…óo, √ëee√±o On wahayiniri e maa, e …ìen adinoo…ìe ma"
  42,4,"Ko Kanko woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ko Kanko kadi woni Toowu…óo, Maw…óo On"
  42,5,"Kammuuli …óin no e…ì…ìa seekorgol dow majji, hara Malaa'ika'en no subbunhinanora yettugol Joomi ma…ì…ìe, …ìe insinanoo won…ìe ka leydi …ìen. Anndee pellet, ko Allah woni Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  42,6,"∆Åen non jogitii…ìe yi…ó…ìe goo gaanin Makko, Allah ko reenu…óo …ìe. A wonaali reenoowo …ìe"
  42,7,"Ko wano non Men wahayniri e maa…óa, janngeteende e aarabu, fii yo a jertin yim…ìe neene ca'e …óen e won…ìe takko mayre …ìen, jertinaa fii √±alnde dental nden, - nde sikke alaa e mu'un - Fedde goo ka Aljnna, fedde goo kadi ka Yiite"
  42,8,"Si Allah haajuno, O wa…óayno …ìe mofte goote. Kono himo On mo O muuyi ka Yurmeende Makko. Too√±oo…ìe …ìen non, gi…óo alanaa …ìe, wanaa ballo"
  42,9,"Kaa …ìe jogiti yi…ó…ìe goo gaanin Makko? Awa ko Allah woni Gi…óo On, ko Kanko wuurnitata maay…ìe …ìen; ko Kanko kadi woni ka…ótan…óo kala huunde"
  42,10,"Kala ko luutondir…óon e fii mun, haray √±aawoore mun nden ko ka Allah woni. Ko On moo…óon Allah, woni Joomi am; ko e Makko mi fawii, ko ka Makko kadi mi ruttorta [tuubugol]"
  42,11,"Fu…ó…óu…óo kamuuli …óin e leydi ndin. O wa…óiranii on e pittaali mon …óin genndoo…ìe, ka neemoraa…ói kadi nooneeji; Himo …óu…ó…óinira on …óum. Hay huunde yerondiraa e Makko; ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi'oowo On"
  42,12,"Ko Kanko heerori soktir…óe kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Himo wertana arsike on mo O muuyani, O …ìi…ótinana (mo O muuyani). Pellet, ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  42,13,"O sar'inanii on e diina kan, konko ko O yamirnoo Nuuhu, e kon ko Men wahayini e maa…óa, e kon ko Men yamirnoo Ibraahiima, e Muusaa e Iisaa, wonnde: \"√ëi…ìnee diina kan; hara on seertaali e makka\". Kono Ko noddotaa sirkoo…ìe …ìen e mun kon, mawnii e dow ma…ì…ìe. Allah non hino su…ìanoo …óum, mo O muuyani, O fewna e Makko, kala tuuboowo"
  42,14,"∆Åe seertaano, si wanaa …ìaawo nde ganndal ngal arde e ma…ì…ìe, sabu bewre hakkunde ma…ì…ìe. Si wanaano fii Konngol ardinoongol, immorde ka Joomi maa, haa e lajal ta∆¥aangal, √±aaweteno hakkunde ma…ì…ìe. Ko pellet, roninaaa…ìe Deftere nden …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe, hino e sikke fii mayre sikkitii…ìe"
  42,15,"Noddu (yim…ìe …ìen) kisan; √±ii…ìiraa no yamira…óaa non, wata a jokku mbelee…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, maakaa: \"Mi gom…óinii ko Allah jippini kon (fow) e Defte, mi yamiraama kadi, nun…óugol hakkunde mon. Allah woni Joomi amen e Joomi mon. Ko menen golle amen woodani, ko onon kadi golle mon woodani. Yeddondiral woo alaa hakkunde amen e mon. Allah moo…ìoyay e denndaandal. Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde nden"
  42,16,"∆Åen wennjiroo…ìe e diina Allah kan, …ìaawo ka ja…ìaneede, hujja ma…ì…ìe on ko meere, tikkere no fawii e ma…ì…ìe, hino woodani …ìe kadi lepte sa…ótu…óe"
  42,17,"Ko Allah woni jippiniri Deftere nden goonga, e manndakke …óen. E ko anndin maa? Hino gasa hara Darngal ngal ko ko …ìadii"
  42,18,"∆Åeya …ìe gom…óinaali ngal …ìen, hi…ìe he√±oringal; gom…óim…ìe …ìen kan, ko …ìe hulu fii maggal, e hoore hi…ìe felliti wonnde ko ngal goonga. Awa anndee won…ìe yeddondireede …ìen fii Darngal, ko pellet, …ìe wonii e nder majjere wo…ó…óunde"
  42,19,"Allah ko newanii…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Himo arsike on mo O muuyani. Ko Kanko woni Doolnu…óo, Foolu…óo On"
  42,20,"Kala taw…óo ko baraaje ndun laakara o faalaa, Men …ìeydanay mo mbarjaari makko ndin; kala kadi taw…óo ko jayru ndun aduna o yi…ói, Men okkay mo …óum, hara non o alaa ka kaalara (ton) ge…ìal"
  42,21,"Kaa hara denndaaaa…ói hino woodani …ìe, sar'inan…ói …ìe e diina kan, kon ko Allah du≈ãaaki fii mun? Si wanaano fii Konngol [happunoongol] ngol fii senndugol [hakkunde ma…ì…ìe], √±aaweteno hakkunde ma…ì…ìe. Ko pellet, hino woodani too√±u…ìe …ìen, lepte muusu…óe"
  42,22,"A yi'ay too√±u…ìe …ìen hino huli e ko …ìe fggitii kon, …óum le ko yantay…óum e ma…ì…ìe. Gom…óim…ìe …ìen, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, hi…ìe e dinngire naakooji, hara hino woodani …ìe ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe, kala ko …ìe faaletee. Ko …óum tigiri, woni …ìural mawnungal ngal"
  42,23,"Ko …óum woni ko Allah wewlinirta jeyaa…ìe Makko gom…óim…ìe …ìen, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e. Maaku: \"Mi lamndaaki on njo…ìdi e …óum, si wanaa tun giggol en…óam …óam\". Kala faggitii…óo mo∆¥∆¥ere, Men …ìeydanay mo mo∆¥∆¥ere e hoore mayre. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo, mantoowo"
  42,24,"Kaa …ìe wi'ay o fefindor nde e hoore Allah fenaande. Si Allah haajuno, O notayno e …ìernda maa nden. Alla no meha meere nden, O tabintinira goonga kan Daalol Makko ngol. Pellet, ko O Anndu…óo gunndooji …ìer…óe …óen"
  42,25,"Ko Kanko woni ja…ìanoowo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen tuubuubuyee, O yaafoo bon…ói …óin, e hoore Himo anndi ko golloton kon"
  42,26,"Himo jaabinana gom…óim…ìe …ìen, …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói, O …ìeydana …ìe e …ìural Makko ngal. Heefer…ìe …ìen non, hino woodani …ìe lepte sa…ótu…óe"
  42,27,"Si tawno Allah ya√±√±anno jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen [fow] arsike, pellet, …ìe bewayno ka leydi; kono Himo jippinira emmbere ko O muuyi. Pellet, ko O Hummpitii…óo, yi*oowo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen"
  42,28,"Ko Kano woni jippinoowo to…ìo ngon …ìaawo …ìe ta∆¥aade, O saaka yurmeende Makko nden. Ko Kanko kadi woni Gi…óo, Yettinii…óo On"
  42,29,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin: tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e ruugay…ói …ói O saaki …óin hakkunde majji. Kanko e fii moo…ìindiroygol …ìe ngol, si O haajii, ko O hattan…óo"
  42,30,"Kala ko he…ìi on e masiibo, ko sabu ko juu…óe mon …óen faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non, ko …óuu…ói"
  42,31,"On wonaali laawotoo…ìe ka leydi ; alanaa on gaanin Allah, gi…óo, wanaa ballo"
  42,32,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin: dogay…óe …óen ka maayo, wa'u…óe wa pelle"
  42,33,"Si O haajii, O dee∆¥inay henndu ndun, ndu wa…ótinira tabitndu e hoore maggo. Wonii e …óum, maandeeji, wonannde kala mu√±√±otoo…óo, yettoowo"
  42,34,Maa yoolira…óe sabu ko …ìe faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non ko …óuu…ói
  42,35,"Wennjoo…ìe …ìen e Aayeeje Amen …óen, hino anndi …ìe alaa laaworde"
  42,36,"Kala ko okka…óon e huunde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna; ko ko woni ka Allah kon, …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude woni kadi ko heddotoo wonannde gom…óim…ìe …ìen fawotoo…ìe e Joomi ma…ì…ìe"
  42,37,"wo…ó…óitotoo…ìe bakkaatuuji maw…ói …óin e pankare …óen, si wonii …ìe tikkii, hara …ìe yaafoto"
  42,38,"…ìen nootii…ìe Joomi ma…ì…ìe, …ìe √±i…ìni julde nden, …ìe tawata fiyaaku ma…ì…ìe on ko diisondiral hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, nafqoo…ìe e kon ko Men arsiki …ìe"
  42,39,"e …ìen taw…ìe si bewre he…ìii …ìe, …ìe yottoto"
  42,40,"Njo…ìdi bonnere, ko bone yeru mun. Kala non yaafii…óo o mo∆¥∆¥intini, haray njo…ìdi makko ndin ko ka Allah woni. Pellet non, O yi…óaa too√±oo…ìe …ìen"
  42,41,"Kala non yottii…ìe …ìaawo …ìe too√±eede, ko …ìen woni …ìe laawol [nanngitireede] fawaaki e mun"
  42,42,"Ko laawol [nanngitireede] fawii e mun, ko too√±oo…ìe yim…ìe …ìen, hara hi…ìe bewira e leydi ndin ko aldaa e goonga: …ìe …óon, hino woodani lepte muusu…óe"
  42,43,"Mu√±√±ii…óo on kadi o yaafii, ko pellet, …óum no jeyaa e pellital fiyakuujI"
  42,44,"Kala mo Allah majjini, haray gi…óo (goo) alanaa mo …ìaawo …óum. A tinay too√±u…ìe …ìen, tuma …ìe yi'i lepte …óen, hi…ìe wi'a: \"Hara laawol ruttorde no woodi"
  42,45,"A tinay …ìe kadi, hi…ìe wee…ìitee e magge, hara hi…ìe yankinii koyeera on, hi…ìe ndaarira ndaar…óe leppagol. Gom…óim…ìe …ìen wi'aya: \"Ko woni hayru …ìe …ìen, ko …ìen hayrim…ìe ko'e mun e …ìeynguureeji ma…ì…ìe …óin √ëalnde Darngal\". Anndee pellet, too√±u…ìe …ìen no e lepte duumii…óe"
  42,46,"Yi…ó…ìe alanaa …ìe, ko wallitoo …ìe, hara wanaa Allah. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray laawol alanaa mo"
  42,47,"Nootee Joomi mon, ado √±alaande arde, nde ruttoowo alaa …óum ka Allah. Nden √±alnde, faaborde alanaa on, yeddugol kadi alanaa on"
  42,48,"Si …ìe …óuurnike non, haray Men nuliraali ma, aynoowo …ìe: fawaaki ma, si wanaa yottingol. Si wonii Men mee…óiniri ne…ó…óanke on neema immorde e Amen, o wewlira mo; si ko bone non he…ìi …ìe, sabu kon ko juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen ardiniri, a taway pellet, ne…ó…óo on ko jeddu…óo sanne"
  42,49,"Ko Allah woodani laamagol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Himo taga ko O muuyi. Himo ye…óa mo O muuyani …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe, O ye…óa kadi mo O muuyani …ìi…ó…ìe wor…ìe"
  42,50,"maa O jillira …ìe wor…ìe e rew…ìe; Himo wa…óa dimaro, on mo O muuyani. Pellet, ko O Anndu…óo, Ha…ótan…óo"
  42,51,"Sellantaa ne…ó…óanke, nde Allah yewtata mo, si wanaa wahayu, maa e …ìaawo heedo, maa O immina Nulaa…óo (Malaa'ikaajo), on wayahina e du≈ãayee(sakkitoore) Makko, kon ko O haaji. Pellet, ko O Toowu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo"
  42,52,"Ko wano non Men wayayinir e maa…óa, ruuhu on [Alqur'aana] e yamiroore Amen. A anndaano ko woni Deftere, maa gom…óinal; si ko woni, Men wa…óunde ndaygu, ngu Men fewnirta on mo Men muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Amen …ìen. Pellet, ko a fewnoowo e laawol focciingol"
  42,53,"laawol Allah, On jey…óo ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Anndee, ko ka Allah, fiyakuuji …óin ruttotoo"
  43,1,"Haa, Miim"
