  57,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  57,2,"Ko Kanko heeranii laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Himo wuurna Himo wara, Kanko ko O hattan…óo kala huunde"
  57,3,"Ko Kanko woni Arano e Sakkitii…óo, Fee√±u…óo e Wirnii…óo, Kanko ko O anndu…óo kala huunde"
  57,4,"Ko Kanko tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin nder bal…óe jeegoo, refti O fotondiri ka dow \"Arsi\"; Himo anndi ko mutata kon ka leydi, e ko ∆¥awata e mayri, e ko jipporta ka kammu e ko ∆¥awata e maggu. Himo wonndi e mon kala ka won…óon. Allah no reeni ko golloton kon. @Corrected"
  57,5,Ko Kanko heeranii laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Ko ka Allah fiyakuuji …óin ruttirtee
  57,6,"Himo naadia jemma on e nder √±alorma on, O naadira √±alorma on kadi e nder jemma on. Kanko ko O anndu…óo ko woni e nder …ìer…óe"
  57,7,"Gom…óinee Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, nafqon kon ko O wa…óiri on lomtinaa…ìe e mun. Gom…óim…ìe …ìen e mon, …ìe nafqi [jawle ma…ì…ìe …óen], hino woodani …ìen njo…ìdi mawnundi"
  57,8,"E ko he…ìi on, on gom…óintaa Allah? E hino Nulaa…óo on hino nodda on e gom…óingol Joomi mon. Gom…óii [Allah] ∆¥ettii e mon ahadi, si on laatike gom…óim…ìe"
  57,9,"Ko Kanko jippinta e jeyaa…óo Makko on Aayeeje …ìanngu…óe, fii no o yaltinira on e ni…ìe faade e ndaygu. Pellet, Allah ko Yuminoowo on, Hinnotoo…óo"
  57,10,"E ko he…ìi on, on sakkotaako fii laawol Allah ngol, e hino le ko Allah woodani ronugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin? Fotataa e mon, …ìen sakkinoo…ìe ado uddital ngal …ìe ha…ìidaa; ko …ìen …ìuri mawnude darja e dii …ìen sakkii…ìe …ìaawo …óum …ìe ha…ìidaa. ∆Åe fow ma…ì…ìe non, Allah fodii …ìe mo∆¥∆¥ere. Allah no humpitii ko golloton kon"
  57,11,"Ko hommbo √±awlirta Allah √±amaande labaande, O sowana mo nde, hara no woodani mo njo…ìdi teddundi"
  57,12,"√ëalnde yi'oytaa gom…óim…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, hara annoora ma…ì…ìe yaara yeeso ma…ì…ìe e √±aamo ma…ì…ìe (…ìe wi'anee): \"Weltaare mon hannde ko Aljannaaji, …ói can…ói ilata senngo ley mun, ko on duumotoo…ìe nder ton\". Ko …óum woni malal mawngal ngal"
  57,13,"√ëalnde naafiqii…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e naafiqii…ìe rew…ìe …ìen wi'anoyta gom…óim…ìe …ìen: \"Habbee men, men jalbinora annoora mon on\". ∆Åe wi'anee : \"Yiltoree …ìaawo mon, …óa…ì…ìoyon annoora\". Heedo wa…óee hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, ngo damal ngal yurmeende woni e nder mun, …ìaawo maggal noon, ko lepte woni e bannge mun"
  57,14,"Hi…ìe nodda …ìe : \"E men wondaano e mon?\" ∆Åe wi'a : \"Ko non woniri. Ko woni tun, on fitinno ko'e mon, habbitani…óon [gom…óim…ìe …ìen bone], sikkiti…óon, yelaaji hodi on haa yamiroore Allah nden ari. Hodoowo on hodi on e mo∆¥∆¥ere Allah nden"
  57,15,"Hannde on, on ja…ìantaake soktor…óum wanaa e …ìen yeddu…ìe. Depporde mon nden ko ka Yiite : ko ngen woni ko hanndu…óon. Nge bonii ruttorde"
  57,16,"E yontaani gom…óim…ìe …ìen nde …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen dee∆¥irta jantoore Allah nden e kon ko jippii immorde e goonga? Hara …ìe wa'aali wa …ìen okkanoo…ìe Defte …ìen ko adii, dumunna on juutani …ìen, …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen yoori, ko …óuu…óunoo e ma…ì…ìe kon ko faasiqii…ìe"
  57,17,"Anndee pellet, Allah wuurnitay leydi ndin …ìaawo ndi yoorii. Gom…óii Men …ìannginiranii on Aayeeje …óen, fii no haqqiliron"
  57,18,"Pellet, sakkotoo…ìe (jawle mun …ìen) ka wor…ìe e ka rew…ìe …ìe √±awli Allah √±amaande labaande, …ìe sowanoyte (mbarjaari) hara no woodani …ìe njo…ìdi mawndi"
  57,19,"∆Åen gom…óim…ìe Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, ko …ìen woni goongiya≈ãke en. Sahodin…ìe …ìen ka Joomi mun, hino woodani …ìen njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe e annoora ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åen non yeddu…ìe …ìe fenni Aayeeje Amen …óen, ko …ìen woni yim…ìe Jahiimi ngen"
  57,20,"Anndee wonnde nguurndam aduna …óam ko fijindaaru, e mbelee…óe, e cu…óaari, e …ìurondiro hakkunde mon e jawle e …ìi…ó…ìe. Wano to…ìo haawnungo remoo…ìe …ìen pu…ói mun, refti ngo yoora, yi'aa hingo soy…ói; refti ngo wonta muncii…óum. Hino ka laakara, lette sa…ótu…óe, e yaafuyee immorde e Allah e yarluyee. Nguurndam aduna …óam wonaali, si wanaa dakammehoy hodo"
  57,21,"Adondiree e (golle) yaafaawuya ka Joomi mon, e Aljanna mo yaajeendi mun wa'i yaajeendi kammu ngun e leydi ndin, on maranaama …ìen gom…óim…ìe Allah e Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen. ∆äum ko …ìural Allah ngal O okkata on mo O muuyani. Allah ko Jom …ìural mawnungal"
  57,22,"Bone woo he…ìataa [on] e leydi ndin maa e pittaali mon …óin, si wanaa …óum woniino e deftere ado Men tagude ndee [tagoore]. Pellet, …óum ko ko newanii Allah"
  57,23,"Ko fii wata on suno e ko laawii on kon, wanaa kadi weltorgol ko O okki on kon. Allah yi…óaa kala √±aa∆¥oowo, mantii…óo"
  57,24,"∆Åen wuddoo…ìe …ìe yamira yim…ìe …ìen nguddam... kala …óuurnii…óo, pellet, Allah kan ko Galo, Yettinii…óo"
  57,25,"Gom…óii Men nulirii Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen …ìanngannduyeeji, Men jippindinani …ìe Defte e sariyaare, fii no yim…ìe …ìen √±ii…ìira e nun…óal. Men jippini kadi njamndi ndin, ndi doole tii…óu…óe woni e mun e nafooje wonannde yim…ìe …ìen, e no Allah fe√±√±inira …ìen walloo…ìe Mo e Nulaa…óo Makko on ka wirnii. Pellet, Allah ko Jom cemmbe, Foolu…óo. @Corrected"
  57,26,"Gom…óii Men nulii Nuuhu e Ibraahiima, Men wa…ói e geyngol ma…ì…ìe ngol Annabaaku e Defte. Hino e ma…ì…ìe feewu…ìe, ko …óuu…ói kon e ma…ì…ìe ko faasiqii…ìe"
  57,27,"Refti Men jokkindini e batteeji ma…ì…ìe …óin, Nulaa…ìe Amen [goo], Men jokkintiniri […ìe] Iisaa ge…óal Maryama on, Men okki mo Linjiila, Men wa…ói e …ìer…óe jokku…ìe mo …ìen : yurmeende e giggol. Labbeyaagal ngal …ìe sinci ngal, Menen Men wa…ó…óinaa ngal e ma…ì…ìe. [Men lamndaaki] si wanaa …óa…ì…ìugol welayee Allah. Kono …ìe ayniraali …óum no haani aynireede. Men okki njo…ìdi gom…óim…ìe …ìen e ma…ì…ìe. Ko …óuu…óunoo kon e ma…ì…ìe ko faasiqii…ìe"
  57,28,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ìe! Hulee Allah, gom…óinon Nulaa…óo Makko on; O ye…óay on ge…óe …ói…ói e mbarjaari Makko ndin, O wa…óana on annoora mo ndayginorton, O haforana on. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  57,29,"Fii no yim…ìe Defte …ìen anndira wonnde …ìe hattanaa hay huunde e …ìural Allah ngal, e wonnde …ìural ngal ko e juu…óe Allah woni; Himo ye…óa ngal mo O muuyani. Pellet, Allah ko Jom …ìural mawngal"
  58,1,Ko goonga Alla nani konngol oon duttondiroowo e ma haala ko faati e jom galle makko hombo wullito faade e Alla; Alla na nana yeewtere mon nde pellet Alla ko nanoowo ji*oowo
  58,2,"…ìeen nanndinoo…ìe suddii…ìe mum en e yummiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe, …ìeen …ìe ngonah yummiraa…ìe ma…ì…ì∆¥e, woni yummiraa…ìe mum en ko …ìeen jibin…ìe …ìe pellet ho…ìe haala pankare e fenaande e pellet Alla ko jaafatoo…óo jarlotoo…óo bakkatuuji"
  58,3,"…ìeen nanndinoo…ìe rew…ìe mum en refti …ìe ndutto ko …ìe mbiino ko yo…ìe ndim…óin daande ko adi nde…ìe memandirta ko …óum woni ko mbaajete …óon ko, Alla na humpati ko ngollaton ko"
  58,4,"Kala mbo da√±aani yo o hoor lebbi …ói…ói dewandir…ói ko adii nde…ìe mandirta kala mbo hattanaani yo o √±ammin miskinee…ìe capan…óe njeegom, …óuum ko ngam ngoon…óinon Alla e nelaa…óo makko ko …óuum woni keerol Alla woodanii heefer…ìe lepte cattu…óe"
  58,5,"Pellet …ìeen luundotoo…ìe Alla e Nelaa…óo Makko …ìe hoynaama hono no adii…ìe …ìe koynirano, Min tellinii aayeeje pee√±…óe, woodani heefer…ìe lepte koynooje"
  58,6,"√ëande O ummini …ìe kam…óe fof O holla …ìe ko…ìe golluno ko, O tonngii …óuum …ìe njejji …óum Alla na seedii kala huunde"
  58,7,"Mbela a anndah wonde Alla na anndi ko woni e nder kammuuli e ko woni e nder leydi, gunndo wonatah hakkunde tata si wonah O nay…ìita…ìe ngo wonatah hakkunde noyo si wonah O wona jeego…ìo ngo wonatah ko jaasi …óuum si wonah O wonda e mum en to…ìe mbaawi wonde fof, refti O habra…ìe ko …ìe golli √±ande darnga, pellet Alla na anndi kala huunde"
  58,8,"Mbela a yiyaani …ìeen ha…óaa…ìe ndeeyu refti …ìe nduttoo ko…ìe kada ko …ìe ndeeyandira e bakkatuuji e a√±anaagal e woopde nelaa…óo, si…ìi ngarii e ma …ìe calmanir ma na Alla salminiraani ma nih …ìe wiya e pittaali mum en ko ha…ói Alla leptira min ko min kaalata ko, yonii…ìe jahannama ho…ìe naatne heen bonii wattannde"
  58,9,"Eehey mon goo…óin…ìe si on ndeeydii e nelaa…óo wotee ndeeyde e makko e bakkaat e a√±anaagal e woopde nelaa…óo, ndeeydee e …óiggere e kulol Alla Mbo moo…ìoyte…óon to Makko"
  58,10,"Pellet gunndo ko e seytaane ngam o sunina …ìeen goon…óin…ìe o lorotaa…ìe hay ndiga si wonah e sakkitoore Alla, e dow Alla woni ko goon…ói…ìe wakkilto"
  58,11,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ìe si on wiyaama yaacne e jolle yaacne Alla yaajnana mon, si on wiyaama umme, umm…óon Alla …ìamta …ìeen goon…óin …ìe e mon e joman en ganndal darajaaji, Alla na humpatii ko golloton ko"
  58,12,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ìe si on ndeeydii e nelaa…óo tottire e ndeeyu mon sadak, ko …óuum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e mon ko …óuum …ìuri laa…ìde, si on ke…ìaani Alla de ko jaafatoo…óo jurmotoo…óo"
  58,13,"Mbela on kul tottirde sadaka saanga ndeeydaton e nelaa…óo, si on tottiraani Alla ja…ìani on tuubuubuya, ndarnee juulde toottiron askal …óofto…óon Alla e nelaa…óo makko, Alla na humpatii ko golloton ko"
  58,14,"Mbela a yi*aani …ìeen heednin…ìe aade en …ìe Alla tikkani …ìe njeyaaka e mon …ìe njeyaako e ma…ì…ìe, ho…ìe ngoondira penaale te ho…ìe nganndi"
  58,15,Alla heblanii…ìe lepte cattu…óe pellet bonii ko…ìe golluno ko
  58,16,"…ìe nanngarii goondooje mum en …óe heedo, …ìe palii laawol Alla ngol, woodanii…ìe lepte koynooje"
  58,17,"Pellet, …ìeen yeddu…ìe, jawle ma…ì…ìe …óen e …ìi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen duncantaa…ìe e lepte Alla …óen hay huunde. Ko …ìeen …óon woni yim…ìe yiite …ìen, kam…ìe ko …ìe luttoo…ìe ton"
  58,18,"√ëande Alla ummini…ìe kam…ìe fof, …ìe ngoondana Mbo hono no…ìe woondaranta mon nih, ho…ìe sikka won ko…ìe ngoni e dow mum, …ìe tigi ngoni fenoo…ìe …ìe"
  58,19,"Seytaane tehrii…ìe o yejjitini …ìe jantaade Alla ko …ìee tigi ngoni fedde seytaane, pellet ko fedde seytaane woni pertu…ìe"
  58,20,"…ìeen ha…ìatoo…ìe Alla e nelaa…óo Makko,ko …ìeen …ìuri hoyde"
  58,21,"Alla √±aawi ma Mi fool Miin e nelaa…ìe am, pellet Alla ko cemmbu…óo teddu…óo"
  58,22,"A he…ìatah yim…ìe goon…óin…ìe e √±alawma cakkatii…óo na nji…óandira e luundii…ìe Alla e nelaa…óo makko haysi …ìe ngonii baabiraa…ìe mum en wolla …ìi…ì…ìe wolla musi…ì…ìe, wolla gorol mum en, ko …ìe …ìer…óe mum en mbinnda iimaan O semmbini…ìe e ruuhu ummade e Makko, O naatna…ìe aljannaaji na dogo ley majji caatli …ìe duumo toon haa pooma, Alla welee…ìe …ìe mbele Alla, ko …ìeen ngoni fedde Alla, ko fedde Alla tigi woni malaa…ìe. @Corrected"
  59,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  59,2,"Ko kanko yaltini …ìeen heefeee…ìe jom en defte en e galleeji mum en e moo…ìdu adanuru ndu, on cikkaana ma…ìe njaltu, …ìe cikki galli mum en …ói ndeenat…ìe e Alla, O ardi…ìe …óo…ìe cikkaana, O werlii e …ìer…óe mum en kulol, ho…ìe njirbinira galleeji ma…ì…ìe juu…óe mum en e juu…óe goon…óin…ìe, teskee onon joman en hakkillaaji"
  59,3,Si Alla farlaana e mum en yaltineede ma O leptu…ìe e aduna woodana…ìe lepte yiite
  59,4,"∆äum, ko fii kam…ìe …ìe lunndike Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on. \"Kala non lunndii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, pellet, Alla ko Ca…ótu…óo lepte"
  59,5,"Kala ko ta∆¥…óon e tamaroowi wolla accu…óonki hoki dari e poo…ìe makki, ko e yamiroore Alla ngam O hoyna faasiqee…ìe"
  59,6,"Ko Alla rutti faade e nelaa…óo Makko ummaade e mum en, on ke√±araaki e mum pucci wolla geloobi, kono Alla na wuurta nelaa…ìe makko e dow mbo o wela, Alla na hattani kala huunde"
  59,7,"Ko Alla neemini e nelaa…óo Mum e yim…ìe gure dow, na woodani Alla e nelaa…óo makko e …ìadii…ìe nelaado e alyatitm en e miskinee…ìe e …ìiy laawol ngam …óum waasa yiilaade hakkunde al…óu…ìe mon, ko nelaa…óo totti on …ìame ko o ha…ói on ngacce, ndeene Alla, pellet Alla ko cattu…óo lepte"
  59,8,"Woodani waas…óe yaltinaa…ìe galleeji mum en e jaw…óeele mum en ho…ìe …óa…ì…ìa …ìural ummaade e Alla e weluya ho…ìe mballa Alla e nelaa…óo makko, ko …ìeen de ngoni goon…óu…ìe tigi"
  59,9,"E …ìeen tellii…ìe e madiina e iimaan ko adii …ìe, ho…ìe nji…ói oon per…óo faade e ma…ì…ìe …ìe ke…ìatah e …ìer…óe mum en tikkere ko…ìe totta ko, ho…ìe …ìurna e dow ko*e mum en haysi ho…ìe wondi e baasal, kala mbo Alla reeni fittaandu mum e …óawre, ko …ìeen de ngoni malaa…ìe"
  59,10,"E …ìeen ar…ìe caggal mum en na mbi*a joomo amen yaafa amen minen e musi…ì…ìe amen adii…ìe amen e iimaan wotah wa…ó e …ìer…óe amen cokotaagal wonande …ìeen goon…óin…ìe,joomi amen ko Aan woni en…óii…óo jurmotoo…óo"
  59,11,"Mbela a yi*aani …ìeen naafaqin…ìe wii…ìe musibbe mum en yeddu…ìe jeyaa…ìe e yim…ìe defte, si on yaltii pellet ma min yaltid e mon, min …óototaako e dow mon hay gooto, si on ka…ìaama ma min mballu mon Alla na seedo ko…ìe fenoo…ìe"
  59,12,Si…ìe yaltinaama …ìe yaltidtah e mum en si …ìe ka…ìaama …ìe wallataa …ìe si…ìe wallii…ìe ma…ìe runta refti …ìe walletaake
  59,13,"Ko onon …ìuri sattu kulo e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe gaa nih e Alla, wa…ói noon ko…ìe yim…ìe …ìe paamatah"
  59,14,…ìe ha…ìatah e mon si wonah ho…ìe e gure taartinaa…óe galli wolla caggal mahdeele bone ma…ì…ìe hakkunde mum en na satti ha…óa sikka ko…ìe gootum kono …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe na ceerti wa…ói noon ko…ìe yim…ìe …ìe kakkiltah
  59,15,Hona yeru …ìeen adii…ìe …ìe ko …ìadii …ìe mee…ói lepte fiyaaku mum en woodanii…ìe lepte cattu…óe
  59,16,"Ko hono seytaane nde wi*i ne…ó…óanke o yeddu, nde o yeddi o wi*i miin komi kis…óo e ma, miin mbe…óo huli Alla jom binnde O"
  59,17,"Laati batte mum en kan…ìe …ói…óa ko yiite saasoo…ìe toon, …óuum ko njo…ìdi too√±oo…ìe"
  59,18,"Eehey mon goon…óibe ndeente Alla, yo fittaandu ndaar kondu ardinani jannga kule Alla pellet Alla ko kumpatii…óo ko ngolloton ko"
  59,19,"Wote ngone hono …ìeen yejjit…ìe Alla, O yejjitini …ìe pittaali mum en ko …ìeen ngoni faasiqee…ìe"
  59,20,"Yim…ìe yiite e yim…ìe aljanna potatah, ko yim…ìe aljanna ngoni fool…ìe"
  59,21,Si min tellinna o quraana e dow hooseere ma a yiinde honde huli honde fetta ngam hulde Alla …ói tinndi emin piyani…ói yim…ìe ko ngam …ìe miijo
  59,22,"Ko kanko woni dewetee…óo dewetee…óo e goonga alah si wonah kanko, ganndo ko wirni e ka wirnaaki kank woni jom yurmeende huftadinnde e yurmeende heeriinde"
